#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:10
#, no-c-format
msgid "Working with Plugins"
msgstr "Delo z vtičniki"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:12
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enable the individual plugins in the <link linkend=\"configuring-"
"kate-configdialog\">configuration dialog</link>, which also provides access "
"to additional configuration options for plugins that require it."
msgstr ""
"Posamezne vtičnike lahko omogočite v <link linkend=\"configuring-kate-"
"configdialog\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>, ki omogoča tudi "
"dostop do dodatnih konfiguracijskih možnosti za vtičnike, ki to potrebujejo."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:18
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; Application Plugins"
msgstr "&kate; Vtičniki aplikacij"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:21
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; plugins are additional functions for the &kate; editor. They can add "
"extra menus and shortcuts, and extend &kate;'s features. You can install as "
"many or as few as you like, from within &kate;. Open &kate;'s configuration "
"dialog with <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure "
"&kate;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Select "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Application</guimenu><guimenuitem>Plugins</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> to choose the wanted plugins."
msgstr ""
"&kate; vtičniki so dodatne funkcije za &kate; urednik. Dodajo lahko dodatne "
"menije in bližnjice ter razširijo funkcije &kate;. Iz &kate; lahko namestite "
"poljubno ali poljubno malo. Odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno &kate; z "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kate;..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice> Izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>Aplikacijo</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem >Vtičniki</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da izberete "
"želene vtičnike."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:31
#, no-c-format
msgid "The available application plugins are:"
msgstr "Razpoložljivi vtičniki aplikacij so:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:36
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-external-tools\">External Tools</"
"link> - Run external tools and applications"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-external-tools\">Zunanja orodja</"
"link> - zaženite zunanja orodja in aplikacije"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-backtracebrowser\">Backtrace "
"Browser</link> - C/C++ Backtrace navigation tool view"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-backtracebrowser\">Brskalnik "
"Backtrace</link> – pogled navigacijskega orodja C/C++ Backtrace"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:44
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-build\">Build Plugin</link> - "
"Compile or Make and parse error messages"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-build\">Vtičnik za Gradnjo</link> - "
"Prevedi ali ustvari in razčleni sporočila o napakah"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-closeexceptlike\">Close Except/Like</"
"link> - Close group of documents based on a common path or file extension"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-closeexceptlike\">Zapri razen/Všeč "
"mi je</link> – Zapri skupino dokumentov na podlagi skupne poti ali končnice "
"datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-colorpicker\">Color Picker</link> - "
"Show preview for known color names"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-colorpicker\">Izbirnik barv</link> – "
"Prikaži predogled za znana imena barv"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:55
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-colored-brackets\">Colored Brackets</"
"link> - Colored brackets for readability"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-colored-brackets\">Barvni oklepaji</"
"link> - Barvni oklepaji za berljivost"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-ctags\">CTags</link> - Look up "
"definitions/declarations with CTags"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-ctags\">CTags</link> – poiščite "
"definicije/deklaracije s CTags"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:63
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-preview\">Document preview</link> - "
"Preview the document in the target format."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-preview\">Predogled dokumenta</link> "
"– Predogled dokumenta v ciljni obliki."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-documentswitcher\">Document "
"switcher</link> - Quick document switching with <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;&Tab;</keycombo> behavior"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-documentswitcher\">Preklopnik med "
"dokumenti</link> - hitro preklapljanje med dokumenti z obnašanjem <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Tab;</keycombo>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-fsbrowser\">File System Browser</"
"link> - File system browser tool view"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-fsbrowser\">Brskalnik po datotečnem "
"sistemu</link> – pogled orodja za brskanje po datotečnem sistemu"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-documents\">Document Tree View</"
"link> - Displays the open files in a file tree"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-documents\">Pogled drevesa "
"dokumentov</link> – prikaže odprte datoteke v drevesu datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:78
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-gdb\">&gdb;</link> - Provides a "
"simple &gdb; frontend"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-gdb\">&gdb;</link> – Zagotavlja "
"preprost &gdb; čelni del"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-projects\">Project Plugin</link> - "
"Integration with &git; and other source control systems"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-projects\">Projektni vtičnik</link> "
"– integracija z &git; in drugi sistemi za nadzor vira"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:85
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replicode - Constructivist AI language and runtime"
msgstr "Replicode – konstruktivistični jezik in čas izvajanja AI"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:88
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-lspclient\">LSP Client</link> - LSP "
"client providing code navigation and code completion for many languages"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-lspclient\">Odjemalec LSP</link> - "
"odjemalec LSP, ki omogoča krmarjenje po kodi in dokončanje kode za številne "
"jezike"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:92
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-searchinfiles\">Search &amp; "
"Replace</link> - Search and replace in documents, folders, or projects"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-searchinfiles\">Iskanje &amp; "
"Zamenjaj</link> – Iskanje in zamenjava v dokumentih, mapah ali projektih"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:96
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-snippets\">Scripts &amp; Snippets "
"tool view</link> - Create or download code snippets and editor scripts"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-snippets\">Pogled orodja Skripti in "
"delčki kode</link> – Ustvarjanje ali prenos delčkov kode in skriptov "
"urejevalnika"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-keyboardmacros\">Keyboard Macros</"
"link> - Record and play keyboard macros (i.e., keyboard action sequences)"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-keyboardmacros\">Makro tipkovnice</"
"link> - Posnemite in predvajajte makre tipkovnice (tj. zaporedja dejanj "
"tipkovnice)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:103
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-sql\">SQL Plugin</link> - Execute "
"query on SQL databases"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-sql\">Vtičnik SQL</link> - Izvedite "
"poizvedbo v bazah podatkov SQL"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-symbolviewer\">Symbol Viewer</link> "
"- Extract and show reference symbols from source"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-symbolviewer\">Pregledovalnik "
"simbolov</link> - Izvlecite in prikažite referenčne simbole iz vira"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:111
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-konsole\">Terminal tool view</link> "
"- Have a terminal at the ready, using &kde;'s &konsole; widget"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-konsole\">Pogled terminalskega "
"orodja</link> - imejte pripravljen terminal z uporabo &konsole; &kde; "
"pripomoček"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-textfilter\">Text Filter</link> - "
"Process text using terminal commands"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-textfilter\">Besedilni filter</link> "
"- Obdelajte besedilo s terminalskimi ukazi"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-xmltools\">&XML; Completion</link> - "
"Lists &XML; elements, attributes, attribute values and entities allowed by "
"DTD"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-xmltools\">&XML;Dokončanje</link> - "
"seznami &XML; elementov, atributov, atributov vrednosti in entitete, ki jih "
"dovoljuje DTD"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:121
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-xmlcheck\">&XML; Validation</link>- "
"Validates &XML; files using xmllint"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-xmlcheck\">&XML; Preverjanje</link>– "
"Preveri &XML; datotek z uporabo xmllint"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-compilerexplorer\">Compiler "
"Explorer</link>- Interface to compiler explorer tool"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-compilerexplorer\">Compiler "
"Explorer</link>- Vmesnik na orodje compiler explorer"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-formatting\">Formatting</link>- Code "
"formatting plugin"
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-formatting\">Formatiranje</link>- "
"Vtičnik za formatiranje kode"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid "External Tools"
msgstr "Zunanja orodja"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>External Tools</guilabel> plugin allows to invoke external "
"applications with data related to the current document, for example its URL, "
"directory, text or selection. Once enabled, a config page appears as "
"depicted below that allows to change or remove existing tools. Similarly, "
"new tools can be added to your liking. The tools will then appear in the "
"<guisubmenu>External Tools</guisubmenu> submenu of the <guimenu>Tools</"
"guimenu> menu of the application."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik <guilabel>Zunanja orodja</guilabel> omogoča priklic zunanjih "
"aplikacij s podatki, povezanimi s trenutnim dokumentom, na primer njegov "
"URL, imenik, besedilo ali izbor. Ko je omogočeno, se prikaže konfiguracijska "
"stran, kot je prikazano spodaj, ki omogoča spreminjanje ali odstranjevanje "
"obstoječih orodij. Podobno lahko dodajate nova orodja po svojih željah. "
"Orodja se nato prikažejo v podmeniju <guisubmenu>Zunanja orodja</guisubmenu> "
"v meniju <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> aplikacije."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:150
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The config page allows to add new external tools by clicking on the "
"<guilabel>Add</guilabel> button. In this case, a popup menu appears where "
"one can either add a new external tool, add an existing tool from a "
"predefined list, or add a new category to organize the external tools into "
"categories. Similarly, the existing tools can be modified either by double-"
"click or by invoking <guilabel>Edit...</guilabel>, and <guilabel>Remove</"
"guilabel> removes the selected tools."
msgstr ""
"Nastavitvena stran omogoča dodajanje novih zunanjih orodij s klikom na gumb "
"<guilabel>Dodaj</guilabel>. V tem primeru se prikaže pojavni meni, kjer "
"lahko dodate novo zunanje orodje, dodate obstoječe orodje s predhodno "
"določenega seznama ali dodate novo kategorijo, da zunanja orodja "
"organizirate v kategorije. Podobno lahko obstoječa orodja spremenite z "
"dvoklikom ali s klicem <guilabel>Uredi ...</guilabel> in <guilabel>Odstrani</"
"guilabel> odstrani izbrana orodja."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:161
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring External Tools"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje zunanjih orodij"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:163
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Editing a tool opens a config dialog that allows fine-grained configuration "
"of the tool:"
msgstr ""
"Urejanje orodja odpre pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo, ki omogoča natančno "
"konfiguracijo orodja:"

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:174
#, no-c-format
msgid "As can be seen, many details can be defined, namely:"
msgstr "Kot je razvidno, je mogoče opredeliti veliko podrobnosti, in sicer:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Name</userinput>, the name of the tool, which will later appear "
"in the menu."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Ime</userinput>, ime orodja, ki se bo kasneje pojavilo v meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:177
#, no-c-format
msgid "<userinput>Icon</userinput>, optional icon that is visible in the menu."
msgstr "<userinput>Ikona</userinput>, neobvezna ikona, ki je vidna v meniju."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Executable</userinput>, executable including either a full path, "
"or your executable must be in the <envar>PATH</envar> environment variable."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Izvršljiva datoteka</userinput>, izvedljiva datoteka, ki "
"vključuje celotno pot ali pa mora biti vaša izvršljiva datoteka v "
"spremenljivki okolja <envar>PATH</envar>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:179
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Arguments</userinput>, optional arguments that are passed to the "
"executable."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Argumenti</userinput>, neobvezni argumenti, ki se posredujejo "
"izvršljivi datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:180
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Input</userinput>, optional input that is passed to the process "
"via stdin."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Vnos</userinput>, izbirni vnos, ki je posredovan procesu prek "
"stdin."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:181
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Working directory</userinput>, the working directory the tool "
"will be started in. If empty, the working directory is set to the current "
"document’s path."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Delovni imenik</userinput>, delovni imenik, v katerem se bo "
"orodje zagnalo. Če je prazen, je delovni imenik nastavljen na pot trenutnega "
"dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:182
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Mime types</userinput>, if set, the tool is active only if the "
"current document’s mime type matches."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Vrste mime</userinput>, če je nastavljeno, je orodje aktivno le, "
"če se ujema vrsta mime trenutnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Save</userinput>, when invoked, saves none, the current document, "
"or all documents."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Shrani</userinput>, ko je priklican, ne shrani nobenega, "
"trenutnega dokumenta ali vseh dokumentov."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:184
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Trigger</userinput>, a trigger to execute this tool. A trigger "
"will only affect the currently active document and will only execute if the "
"mimetype of current active document matches the mimetype of the external "
"tool."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Sprožilec</userinput>, sprožilec za izvajanje tega orodja. "
"Sprožilec bo vplival samo na trenutno aktiven dokument in se bo izvedel le, "
"če se vrsta mime trenutnega aktivnega dokumenta ujema z vrsto mime zunanjega "
"orodja."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:186
#, no-c-format
msgid "Following triggers are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednji sprožilci:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:188
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>None</userinput>, this is the default, it means the tool has no "
"trigger."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Brez</userinput>, to je privzeto, kar pomeni, da orodje nima "
"sprožilca."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Before Save</userinput>, this trigger will execute right before "
"saving the document."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Pred shranjevanjem</userinput> se bo ta sprožilec izvedel tik "
"pred shranjevanjem dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:190
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>After Save</userinput>, this trigger will execute the tool after "
"the document was saved."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Po shranjevanju</userinput> bo ta sprožilec izvedel orodje po "
"shranjevanju dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:193
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Reload current document after execution</userinput>, useful when "
"the current file is modified on disk."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Znova naloži trenutni dokument po izvedbi</userinput>, uporabno, "
"ko je trenutna datoteka spremenjena na disku."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Output</userinput>, the output defines the target of stdout. It "
"is either set to <userinput>Ignored</userinput>, <userinput>Insert at Cursor "
"Position</userinput>, <userinput>Replace Selected Text</userinput>, "
"<userinput>Replace Current Document</userinput>, <userinput>Append to "
"Current Document</userinput>, <userinput>Insert in New Document</userinput>, "
"<userinput>Copy to Clipboard</userinput>, or <userinput>Display in Pane</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Izhod</userinput>, izhod določa cilj stdout-a. Nastavljen je na "
"<userinput>Prezrto</userinput>, <userinput>Vstavi na položaj kazalca</"
"userinput>, <userinput>Zamenjaj izbrano besedilo</userinput>, "
"<userinput>Zamenjaj trenutni dokument</userinput>, <userinput >Dodaj "
"trenutnemu dokumentu</userinput>, <userinput>Vstavi v nov dokument</"
"userinput>, <userinput>Kopiraj v odložišče</userinput> ali "
"<userinput>Prikaži v podoknu</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>Editor command</userinput>, optional command that can be used to "
"invoke the external tool via the built-in <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/"
"advanced.html#advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">command line</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>Ukaz urejevalnika</userinput>, izbirni ukaz, ki ga lahko "
"uporabite za priklic zunanjega orodja prek vgrajenega <ulink url=\"help:/"
"katepart/advanced.html#advanced-editing-tools-commandline\">ukaza vrstica</"
"ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:200
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The button <guilabel>Defaults</guilabel> is visible only for tools that are "
"shipped with Kate. When clicked, all tool’s settings reverted to default "
"(aka factory) values."
msgstr ""
"Gumb <guilabel>Privzeto</guilabel> je viden samo za orodja, ki so priložena "
"Kate. Ob kliku so se vse nastavitve orodja vrnile na privzete (ali "
"tovarniške) vrednosti."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Variable Expansion"
msgstr "Razširitev spremenljivke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Some editing fields such as the <guilabel>Executable</guilabel>, the "
"<guilabel>Arguments</guilabel>, the <guilabel>Input</guilabel> and the "
"<guilabel>Working Directory</guilabel> support variables that are expanded "
"on tool invocation. This is indicated by the icon <guilabel>{}</guilabel> "
"that appears once one of these text input fields has focus (see red circle):"
msgstr ""
"Nekatera polja za urejanje, kot so <guilabel>Izvedljiva</guilabel>, "
"<guilabel>Argumenti</guilabel>, <guilabel>Vnos</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Delovni imenik</guilabel>, podpirajo spremenljivke, ki so "
"razširjene pri priklicu orodja. To je označeno z ikono <guilabel>{}</"
"guilabel>, ki se prikaže, ko je eno od teh polj za vnos besedila v fokusu "
"(glejte rdeči krog):"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Hovering over one of these text input fields also shows a tooltip with the "
"current expanded text. Further, clicking on the <guilabel>{}</guilabel> "
"action will open a dialog that lists all available variables:"
msgstr ""
"Če miškin kazalec premaknete nad eno od teh polj za vnos besedila, se "
"prikaže tudi opis orodja s trenutnim razširjenim besedilom. Poleg tega se s "
"klikom na dejanje <guilabel>{}</guilabel> odpre pogovorno okno, v katerem so "
"navedene vse razpoložljive spremenljivke:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This feature provides a lot of flexibility when defining an external tool "
"since all variables of the form <userinput>%{...}</userinput> are expanded "
"when the tool gets invoked. There are two kind of variables supported: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para><userinput>%{variable-name}</userinput></"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para><userinput>%{variable-name:&lt;value&gt;}</"
"userinput></para></listitem> </itemizedlist> The first form <userinput>"
"%{variable-name}</userinput> simply replaces the variable with its contents. "
"For instance, the variable <userinput>%{Document:FileName}</userinput> is "
"replaced by the current document’s filename without its path. The second "
"form <userinput>%{variable-name:&lt;value&gt;}</userinput> gets the "
"<userinput>&lt;value&gt;</userinput> as contents. For example, this can be "
"used to expand an environment variable with <userinput>%{ENV:HOME}</"
"userinput>, or one can obtain the current date in the preferred format like "
"<userinput>%{Date:yyyy-MM-dd}</userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ta funkcija zagotavlja veliko prilagodljivosti pri definiranju zunanjega "
"orodja, saj so vse spremenljivke v obliki <userinput>%{...}</userinput> "
"razširjene, ko je orodje priklicano. Podprti sta dve vrsti spremenljivk: "
"<itemizedlist> <listitem><para><userinput>%{variable-name}</userinput></"
"para></listitem> <listitem><para><userinput>%{variable -name:&lt;value&gt;}</"
"userinput></para></listitem> </itemizedlist> Prva oblika <userinput>"
"%{variable-name}</userinput> preprosto zamenja spremenljivko z njeno "
"vsebino. Na primer, spremenljivka <userinput>%{Document:FileName}</"
"userinput> se nadomesti z imenom datoteke trenutnega dokumenta brez njegove "
"poti. Drugi obrazec <userinput>%{variable-name:&lt;value&gt;}</userinput> "
"dobi <userinput>&lt;value&gt;</userinput> kot vsebino. To lahko na primer "
"uporabite za razširitev spremenljivke okolja z <userinput>%{ENV:HOME}</"
"userinput> ali pa lahko pridobite trenutni datum v želeni obliki, kot je "
"<userinput>%{Date:yyyy-MM- dd}</userinput>."

