#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:298
#, no-c-format
msgid "List of Default Tools"
msgstr "Seznam privzetih orodij"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:300
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Several tools are shipped by default. However, if you have more useful tools "
"please contribute those to <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/utilities/kate"
"\">our GitLab project</ulink> so that we can add them to this list. All "
"default tools are visible in the list view by default. However, all tools "
"can be changed to your liking, including the category or even deleting "
"tools. Deleted tools can be added back again by clicking on the "
"<guibutton>Add</guibutton> button in the config page as described above."
msgstr ""
"Več orodij je privzeto dobavljenih. Če pa imate še več uporabnih orodij, jih "
"prosim prispevajte k <ulink url=\"https://invent.kde.org/utilities/kate"
"\">našemu projektu GitLab</ulink>, da jih bomo lahko dodali na ta seznam. "
"Vsa privzeta orodja so privzeto vidna v pogledu seznama. Vendar pa lahko vsa "
"orodja spremenite po svojih željah, vključno s kategorijo ali celo z "
"brisanjem orodij. Izbrisana orodja lahko ponovno dodate s klikom na gumb "
"<guibutton>Dodaj</guibutton> na strani za konfiguracijo, kot je opisano "
"zgoraj."

