#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:516
#, no-c-format
msgid "Backtrace Browser Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za brskalnik Backtrace"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:519
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Backtrace Browser Plugin"
msgstr "Uporaba vtičnika za brskalnik Backtrace"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:521
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin is meant for developers and probably of little use for users. It "
"shows a backtrace delivered by gdb in a listview in a &kate; toolview. "
"Clicking on an item opens the selected file and jumps to the correct line "
"number. It works for backtraces generated on your own machine, but it will "
"also work for backtraces from other people, &ie; with <filename>/home/dummy/"
"qt-copy/…/qwidget.cpp</filename> will still be found on other machines. For "
"that to work, you have to index the directories where the source code is "
"located."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik je namenjen razvijalcem in verjetno malo uporaben za uporabnike. "
"Prikazuje povratno sled, ki jo dostavi gdb, v pogledu seznama v datoteki "
"&kate; orodniPogled. S klikom na element se odpre izbrana datoteka in skoči "
"na pravilno številko vrstice. Deluje za povratne sledi, ustvarjene na vašem "
"računalniku, vendar bo deloval tudi za povratne sledi drugih ljudi, &ie; z "
"<filename>/home/dummy/qt-copy/…/qwidget.cpp</filename> bo še vedno mogoče "
"najti na drugih računalnikih. Da bo to delovalo, morate indeksirati imenike, "
"kjer se nahaja izvorna koda."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:530
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sometimes there are several files with the same name, &eg;"
msgstr "Včasih obstaja več datotek z istim imenom, &eg;"

#. Tag: filename
#: plugins.docbook:533
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdegraphics/okular/generators/dvi/config.h"
msgstr "kdegraphics/okular/generators/dvi/config.h"

#. Tag: filename
#: plugins.docbook:534
#, no-c-format
msgid "kdepim-runtime/resources/gmail/saslplugin/config.h"
msgstr "kdepim-runtime/resources/gmail/saslplugin/config.h"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To pick the right choice, the plugin picks the last two parts of the &URL;, "
"in this case this would be"
msgstr ""
"Za izbiro prave izbire vtičnik izbere zadnja dva dela &URL;, v tem primeru "
"bi to bilo"

#. Tag: filename
#: plugins.docbook:541
#, no-c-format
msgid "dvi/config.h"
msgstr "dvi/config.h"

#. Tag: filename
#: plugins.docbook:542
#, no-c-format
msgid "saslplugin/config.h"
msgstr "saslplugin/config.h"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:545
#, no-c-format
msgid "And then usually the plugin finds the correct one."
msgstr "In potem običajno vtičnik najde pravega."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Indexing master and a branches of course will lead to a clash."
msgstr "Indeksiranje glavnega in vej bo seveda povzročilo spopad."

