"png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Izbrišite "
"trenutni ukaz ali nabor ciljev"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:688
#, no-c-format
msgid "Output tab"
msgstr "Izhodni zavihek"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:690
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guilabel>Output</guilabel> tab shows the console output generated by "
"the running (build) command. If a line contains a file location, that line "
"will be clickable. If the line in the output also shows an error or warning, "
"the line will have a different color."
msgstr ""
"Zavihek <guilabel>Izhod</guilabel> prikazuje izhod konzole, ki ga generira "
"izvajajoči se (gradbeni) ukaz. Če vrstica vsebuje lokacijo datoteke, bo to "
"vrstico mogoče klikniti. Če vrstica v izhodu prikazuje tudi napako ali "
"opozorilo, bo vrstica drugačne barve."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:695
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the option <guilabel>Add errors and warnings to Diagnostics</guilabel> is "
"enabled in the plugin's settings page in Kate settings, the errors and "
"warnings will also be added to the diagnostics view. To navigate to the "
"previous error in the diagnostics view, press <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo>. To navigate to the next error, press "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Če je možnost <guilabel>Dodaj napake in opozorila v diagnostiko</guilabel> "
"omogočena na strani z nastavitvami vtičnika v nastavitvah Kate, bodo napake "
"in opozorila prav tako dodani v pogled diagnostike. Za navigacijo do "
"prejšnje napake v diagnostičnem pogledu pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul"
"\">&Alt;&Shift;&Left;</keycombo>. Za navigacijo do naslednje napake "
"pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;&Right;</keycombo>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:707 plugins.docbook:823 plugins.docbook:1031
#: plugins.docbook:1135 plugins.docbook:1180 plugins.docbook:1238
#: plugins.docbook:1487 plugins.docbook:2330 plugins.docbook:3366
#: plugins.docbook:3445 plugins.docbook:4012 plugins.docbook:4100
#: plugins.docbook:4162 plugins.docbook:4301 plugins.docbook:4390
#: plugins.docbook:4508
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Structure"
msgstr "Struktura menija"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:711
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guisubmenu>Select Target...</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izberi cilj...</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:714
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The target selection filter is focused in the Target Settings tab. Typing a "
"name will filter out targets that do not match the typed string. It is also "
"possible to use the arrow keys to navigate the tree of targets. When the "
"wanted target is selected, pressing <guilabel>Return</guilabel> or "
"<guilabel>Enter</guilabel> will execute and run the selected target."
msgstr ""
"Filter izbire cilja je usmerjen na zavihek Nastavitve cilja. Če vnesete ime, "
"boste izločili cilje, ki se ne ujemajo z vnesenim nizom. Za krmarjenje po "
"drevesu ciljev je mogoče uporabiti tudi puščične tipke. Ko je želeni cilj "
"izbran, bo pritisk <guilabel>Return</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Enter</"
"guilabel> izvršil in zagnal izbrani cilj."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:721
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Build Selected Target</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izgradi izbrani cilj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Builds the last selected target. If none has been selected, it works as "
"<guilabel>Select Target...</guilabel>"
msgstr ""
"Izgradi zadnji izbrani cilj. Če ni bil izbran noben, deluje kot "
"<guilabel>Izberi cilj...</guilabel>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:729
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Build and Run Selected Target</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izgradi in zaženi izbrani cilj</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:732
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Builds the last selected target and run the run command after the build "
"command has finished successfully."
msgstr ""
"Zgradi zadnji izbrani cilj in zažene ukaz za zagon, ko je ukaz za izgradnjo "
"uspešno končan."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:737
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Compile Current File</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prevedi trenutno datoteko</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:740
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Try to compile the current file by searching for a command in a possible "
"compile_commands.json."
msgstr ""
"Poskusi prevesti trenutno datoteko tako, da poišče ukaz v možnem "
"compile_commands.json."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:745
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Stop</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Zgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ustavi</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop building a target."
msgstr "Ustavi gradnjo cilja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:752
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Focus Next Tab to the Left</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Fokus na naslednji zavihek na levo</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the next build plugin tab to the left. Or open the build plugin tool-"
"view if it is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Fokus na naslednji zavihek vtičnika gradnje na levo. Ali pa odpri pogled "
"orodja vtičnika za gradnjo, če je skrit."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:759
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Focus Next Tab to the Right</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Fokus na naslednji zavihek na desno</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:762
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Focus the next build plugin tab to the right. Or open the build plugin tool-"
"view if it is hidden."
msgstr ""
"Fokus na naslednji zavihek vtičnika gradnje na desno. Ali pa odpri pogled "
"orodja vtičnika za gradnjo, če je skrit."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Build</guimenu><guimenuitem>Load targets from CMake Build Dir</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Izgradi</guimenu><guimenuitem>Naloži cilje iz CMake Build Dir</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the file dialog and let's the user select a <guilabel>CMakeCache.txt</"
"guilabel>. When a file is selected, the plugin generates cmake build command "
"targets that can be executed in the build directory for the CMake based "
"project."
msgstr ""
"Odpre pogovorno okno datoteke in pusti uporabniku, da izbere "
"<guilabel>CMakeCache.txt</guilabel>. Ko je datoteka izbrana, vtičnik ustvari "
"ciljne ukaze za gradnjo cmake, ki jih je mogoče izvesti v imeniku gradnje za "
"projekt, ki temelji na CMake."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:778 plugins.docbook:1895 plugins.docbook:3733
#: plugins.docbook:4065 plugins.docbook:4407 plugins.docbook:4557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Thanks and Acknowledgments"
msgstr "Hvala in zahvala"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:779
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kate; Build Plugin was written by Kåre Särs."
msgstr "&kate; Vtičnik Build je napisal Kåre Särs."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:780
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 participant Salma Sultana for writing "
"much of this section."
msgstr ""
"Posebna zahvala udeleženki Google Code-In 2011 Salmi Sultani za pisanje "
"večjega dela tega razdelka."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:787
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Except/Like Plugin"
msgstr "Zapri vtičnik Razen/Všeč mi je"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin allows you to close a group of documents based on their "
"extension and path."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik vam omogoča, da zaprete skupino dokumentov glede na njihovo "
"razširitev in pot."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:797 plugins.docbook:4080
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Close Except/Like Plugin"
msgstr "Uporaba vtičnika Zapri razen/Všeč mi je"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:799
#, no-c-format
msgid "Assumed you have these documents opened in &kate;:"
msgstr "Predpostavimo, da imate te dokumente odprte v &kate;:"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:802
#, no-c-format
msgid "/tmp/subfolder/test.h"
msgstr "/tmp/subfolder/test.h"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:803
#, no-c-format
msgid "/tmp/test.cpp"
msgstr "/tmp/test.cpp"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:804
#, no-c-format
msgid "/tmp/test.txt"
msgstr "/tmp/test.txt"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:807
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Then you have the following options to close documents as displayed in the "
"screenshot:"
msgstr ""
"Nato imate naslednje možnosti za zapiranje dokumentov, kot je prikazano na "
"posnetku zaslona:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:810
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close Except"
msgstr "Zapri razen"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:816
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the checkbox in the last item of the list to enable or disable a "
"confirmation dialog. The selected option will be applied to both close "
"actions."
msgstr ""
"Uporabite potrditveno polje v zadnjem elementu seznama, da omogočite ali "
"onemogočite potrditveno pogovorno okno. Izbrana možnost bo uporabljena za "
"obe dejanji zapiranja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:827
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Close Except</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zapri razen</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:832
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Close</action> all open documents, <emphasis>except</emphasis> those "
"which match the path or file extension selected from the submenu."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zapri</action> vse odprte dokumente, <emphasis>razen</emphasis> "
"tistih, ki se ujemajo s potjo ali končnico datoteke, izbrano v podmeniju."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:838
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Close Like</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zapri Všeč mi je</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<action>Close</action> all open documents which match the path or file "
"extension selected from the submenu."
msgstr ""
"<action>Zapri</action> vse odprte dokumente, ki se ujemajo s potjo ali "
"pripono datoteke, izbrano v podmeniju."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:856
#, no-c-format
msgid "Color Picker Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za izbiro barv"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:861
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin adds an inline color preview/picker to colors in the text (&eg;, "
"<literal>#FFFFFF</literal>, <literal>white</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik barvam v besedilu doda predogled/izbirnik barv v vrstici (&eg; "
"<literal>#FFFFFF</literal>, <literal>bela</literal>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:864
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To load this plugin open &kate;'s configuration dialog under "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kate;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then select <guilabel>Color Picker</guilabel> and "
"close the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite naložiti ta vtičnik, odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno &kate; "
"pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kate;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Nato izberite <guilabel>Izbirnik barv</"
"guilabel> in zaprite pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:873
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the Color Picker settings page in &kate;'s configuration, you can "
"configure the following options of the plugin behavior."
msgstr ""
"Na strani z nastavitvami izbirnika barv v konfiguraciji &kate; lahko "
"konfigurirate naslednje možnosti obnašanja vtičnika."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show preview for known color names"
msgstr "Pokaži predogled za znana imena barv"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Whether to show the color picker for known color names (&eg;, "
"<literal>skyblue</literal>). See <ulink url=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/"
"types.html#ColorKeywords\">this page</ulink> for the list of colors."
msgstr ""
"Ali naj se prikaže izbirnik barv za znana imena barv (&eg; <literal>nebesno "
"modra</literal>). Oglejte si <ulink url=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/types."
"html#ColorKeywords\">to stran</ulink> za seznam barv."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:885
#, no-c-format
msgid "Place preview after text color"
msgstr "Predogled postavite za barvo besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Whether to place the inline preview after text color in the text."
msgstr "Ali naj se predogled v vrstici umesti za barvo besedila v besedilu."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hex color matching"
msgstr "Hex ujemanje barv"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, you can choose the best matching option for the colors used in your "
"code."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj lahko izberete najboljšo možnost ujemanja za barve, uporabljene v vaši "
"kodi."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:905
#, no-c-format
msgid "Colored Brackets"
msgstr "Barvni oklepaji"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:908
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Colored brackets plugin colors matching bracket pairs in different colors to "
"enhance readability. However, not all brackets get colored. A bracket whose "
"matching opener or closer is not visible will be ignored. Similarly, a "
"bracket pair that is the sole bracket pair on a line will not get colored."
msgstr ""
"Barvne barve vtičnika za oklepaje, ki ujemajo pare oklepajev v različnih "
"barvah za izboljšanje berljivosti. Vendar se vsi oklepaji ne obarvajo. "
"Oklepaj, katerega ujemajoči se odpirač ali zapiralec ni viden, bo prezrt. "
"Podobno par oklepajev, ki je edini par oklepajev na vrstici, ne bo obarvan."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:914
#, no-c-format
msgid "The plugin doesn't provide any configurations."
msgstr "Vtičnik ne nudi nobenih konfiguracij."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:920
#, no-c-format
msgid "CTags Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik CTags"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:925
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ctags\">CTags</ulink> generates "
"an index (or tag) file of language objects found in source files that allows "
"these items to be quickly and easily located using this plugin in &kate;."
msgstr ""
"<ulink url=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ctags\">CTags</ulink> ustvari "
"indeksno datoteko (ali oznako) jezikovnih predmetov, najdenih v izvornih "
"datotekah, ki omogoča hitro in enostavno iskanje teh elementov uporabo tega "
"vtičnika v &kate;."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:929
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A tag signifies a language object for which an index entry is available (or, "
"alternatively, the index entry created for that object)."
msgstr ""
"Oznaka označuje jezikovni objekt, za katerega je na voljo indeksni vnos "
"(ali, alternativno, indeksni vnos, ustvarjen za ta predmet)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:932
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Tag generation is supported for these <ulink url=\"http://ctags.sourceforge."
"net/languages.html\">programming languages</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Generiranje oznak je podprto za te <ulink url=\"http://ctags.sourceforge.net/"
"languages.html\">programske jezike</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:940
#, no-c-format
msgid "The CTags plugin uses two different database files for the index."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik CTags za indeks uporablja dve različni datoteki zbirke podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:942
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On the CTags settings page in &kate;'s configuration you can add or remove "
"directories containing the source code and regenerate the common CTags "
"database."
msgstr ""
"Na strani z nastavitvami CTags v konfiguraciji &kate; lahko dodate ali "
"odstranite imenike, ki vsebujejo izvorno kodo, in ponovno ustvarite skupno "
"bazo podatkov CTags."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:946
#, no-c-format
msgid "Common Index"
msgstr "Skupni indeks"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:949
#, no-c-format
msgid "CTags Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve CTags"

#. Tag: caption
#: plugins.docbook:952
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure CTags Global Database"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte globalno bazo podatkov CTags"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:956
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At the bottom of the settings page you can adapt the <guilabel>CTags "
"command</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Na dnu strani z nastavitvami lahko prilagodite <guilabel>ukaz CTags</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:959
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more information about all available options please read the CTags man "
"page. This man page is available in &khelpcenter; and you can also enter the "
"&URL; <emphasis>man:/ctags</emphasis> directly into &konqueror;"
msgstr ""
"Za več informacij o vseh razpoložljivih možnostih preberite man stran CTags. "
"Ta stran s priročnikom je na voljo v &khelpcenter; in lahko tudi vnesete "
"&URL; <emphasis>man:/ctags</emphasis> neposredno v &konqueror;"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guibutton>Update</guibutton> will start indexing. When indexing is "
"finished, close the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guibutton>Posodobi</guibutton>, se bo začelo indeksiranje. Ko "
"je indeksiranje končano, zaprite pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Session Index"
msgstr "Indeks seje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To configure the session index open the <guilabel>CTags</guilabel> view."
msgstr ""
"Če želite konfigurirati indeks seje, odprite pogled <guilabel>CTags</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: plugins.docbook:976
#, no-c-format
msgid "Index Targets"
msgstr "Cilji indeksa"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:979
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On this tab you can add or remove directories containing the source code and "
"manually regenerate the session specific CTags database."
msgstr ""
"Na tem zavihku lahko dodate ali odstranite imenike, ki vsebujejo izvorno "
"kodo, in ročno znova ustvarite bazo podatkov CTags za sejo."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: plugins.docbook:986
#, no-c-format
msgid "Database"
msgstr "Baza podatkov"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:990
#, no-c-format
msgid "Database Settings"
msgstr "Nastavitve zbirke podatkov"

#. Tag: caption
#: plugins.docbook:993
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure CTags Session Database"
msgstr "Konfigurirajte bazo podatkov seje CTags"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:996
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select another CTags database file, configure the CTags command or revert to "
"the default command."
msgstr ""
"Izberite drugo datoteko baze podatkov CTags, konfigurirajte ukaz CTags ali "
"vrnite na privzeti ukaz."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1008
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the CTags Plugin"
msgstr "Uporaba vtičnika CTags"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You place the mouse cursor on the language object like function, symbol "
"&etc; that you are interested in and then select one of the actions in the "
"<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> menu to jump to the line and file where the object "
"is defined or declared."
msgstr ""
"Kazalec miške postavite na jezikovni predmet, kot je funkcija, simbol &etc; "
"ki vas zanima, in nato izberite eno od dejanj v meniju <guimenu>CTags</"
"guimenu>, da skočite na vrstico in datoteko, kjer je objekt definiran ali "
"deklariran."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the actions in the <guimenu>CTags</guimenu> menu have no "
"shortcuts assigned. Use the <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html"
"\">keyboard shortcut editor</ulink> to configure your own shortcuts."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto dejanja v meniju <guimenu>CTags</guimenu> nimajo dodeljenih "
"bližnjic. Uporabite <ulink url=\"help:/fundamentals/shortcuts.html"
"\">urejevalnik bližnjic na tipkovnici</ulink> za konfiguracijo lastnih "
"bližnjic."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively use the search field on the <guilabel>Lookup</guilabel> tab of "
"the CTags view."
msgstr ""
"Druga možnost je, da uporabite iskalno polje na zavihku <guilabel>Iskanje</"
"guilabel> v pogledu CTags."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1021
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering characters into the search field will start the search and display "
"matching names of language objects like functions, classes, symbols &etc; "
"together with type and filename."
msgstr ""
"Če v iskalno polje vnesete znake, se začne iskanje in prikažejo se ujemajoča "
"se imena jezikovnih objektov, kot so funkcije, razredi, simboli &etc; skupaj "
"z vrsto in imenom datoteke."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1023 plugins.docbook:2231 plugins.docbook:2243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select an item in the list to jump to the corresponding line in the source "
"file."
msgstr ""
"Izberite element na seznamu, da skočite na ustrezno vrstico v izvorni "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1036
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Jump back one step</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Skoči en korak nazaj</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1041
#, no-c-format
msgid "Navigate back in the history to the last visited tag."
msgstr "Pomaknite se nazaj v zgodovino do zadnje obiskane oznake."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1046
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Lookup Current Text</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Iskanje trenutnega besedila</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1051
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the <guilabel>Lookup</guilabel> tab of the CTags view and displays all "
"language objects matching the current text selection in the list."
msgstr ""
"Odpre zavihek <guilabel>Iskanje</guilabel> v pogledu CTags in prikaže vse "
"jezikovne objekte, ki se ujemajo s trenutno izbiro besedila na seznamu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1057
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Declaration</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na deklaracijo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the cursor is in a definition object this will open the document "
"containing the corresponding declaration if needed, activate its view and "
"place the cursor at the start of the declaration."
msgstr ""
"Če je kazalec v objektu definicije, bo to po potrebi odprlo dokument, ki "
"vsebuje ustrezno deklaracijo, aktiviral njegov pogled in kazalko postavil na "
"začetek deklaracije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1069
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Definition</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>CTags</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na definicijo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1074
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the cursor is in a declaration object this will open the document "
"containing the corresponding definition if needed, activate its view and "
"place the cursor at the start of the definition."
msgstr ""
"Če je kazalec v objektu deklaracije, bo to po potrebi odprlo dokument, ki "
"vsebuje ustrezno definicijo, aktiviralo njegov pogled in postavilo kazalko "
"na začetek definicije."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Preview Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za predogled dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin enables a live preview of the currently edited text document in "
"the final format in the sidebar. So when editing &eg; a &Markdown; text or "
"an &SVG; image, the result is instantly visible next to the source text."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik za predogled dokumenta Vtičnik omogoča predogled v živo trenutno "
"urejenega besedilnega dokumenta v končni obliki v stranski vrstici. Torej "
"pri urejanju &eg; &Markdown; besedilo ali &SVG; sliko, je rezultat takoj "
"viden poleg izvornega besedila."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1100
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the display the plugin uses that &kparts; plugin which is currently "
"selected as the preferred one for the &MIME; type of the document. If there "
"is no &kparts; plugin for that type, no preview is possible."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz vtičnik uporablja &kparts; vtičnik, ki je trenutno izbran kot "
"prednostni za &MIME; vrsto dokumenta. Če ni &kparts; vtičnika za to vrsto, "
"predogled ni mogoč."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To change the preferred plugin open the <guilabel>File Associations</"
"guilabel> module in the &systemsettings; and edit the <guilabel>Services "
"Preference Order</guilabel> on the <guilabel>Embedding</guilabel> tab."
msgstr ""
"Če želite spremeniti prednostni vtičnik, odprite modul <guilabel>Povezave "
"datotek</guilabel> v &systemsettings; in uredite <guilabel>Prednostni vrstni "
"red storitev</guilabel> na zavihku <guilabel>Vdelava</guilabel>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1111
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some available &kparts; plugins"
msgstr "Nekaj razpoložljivih &kparts; vtičniki"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "&MIME; type"
msgstr "&MIME; vrsta"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1115
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kparts; plugin"
msgstr "&kparts; vtičnik"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Markdown; text"
msgstr "&Markdown; besedilo"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1118
#, no-c-format
msgid "KMarkdownWebViewPart or OkularPart"
msgstr "KMarkdownWebViewPart ali OkularPart"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid "&SVG; image"
msgstr "&SVG; slika"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1121
#, no-c-format
msgid "SVGPart"
msgstr "SVGPart"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Qt; UI files"
msgstr "&Qt; datoteke uporabniškega vmesnika"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1124
#, no-c-format
msgid "KUIViewerPart"
msgstr "KUIViewerPart"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid "&DOT; graph files"
msgstr "&DOT; grafične datoteke"

#. Tag: entry
#: plugins.docbook:1127
#, no-c-format
msgid "KGraphviewerPart"
msgstr "KGraphviewerPart"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1139
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Preview</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži predogled</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1144
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the display of &kate;'s Document preview in a sidebar."
msgstr "Preklopi prikaz predogleda dokumenta &kate; v stranski vrstici."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1151 plugins.docbook:1255 plugins.docbook:3094
#, no-c-format
msgid "Interface"
msgstr "Vmesnik"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1152
#, no-c-format
msgid "The buttons at the top of the preview window provide these actions:"
msgstr "Gumbi na vrhu okna za predogled omogočajo ta dejanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Lock the preview to a given document. Selecting this option ensures that if "
"switching the focus to the view of another document in the same &kate; "
"window, the preview will not follow to that document, but keep previewing "
"this document."
msgstr ""
"Zakleni predogled na dani dokument. Če izberete to možnost, zagotovite, da "
"če preklopite fokus na pogled drugega dokumenta v istem &kate; oknu, "
"predogled ne bo sledil temu dokumentu, ampak bo nadaljeval s predogledom "
"tega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enable or disable updates of the preview of the current document content"
msgstr ""
"Omogočite ali onemogočite posodobitve predogleda vsebine trenutnega dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1165
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manually update the preview of the current document content"
msgstr "Ročno posodobite predogled vsebine trenutnega dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1168
#, no-c-format
msgid "A dropdown menu with actions from the &kparts; plugin"
msgstr "Spustni meni z dejanji iz &kparts; vključiti"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1177
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Switcher Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za preklop dokumentov"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1185
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Tab;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Last Used Views</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Tab;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zadnji uporabljeni pogledi</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Last Used Views (Reverse)</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;&Tab;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zadnji uporabljeni pogledi "
"(obratno)</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1201
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Opens</action> a list with the last viewed documents:"
msgstr "<action>Odpre</action> seznam z nazadnje ogledanimi dokumenti:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:1204
#, no-c-format
msgid "Last viewed documents"
msgstr "Zadnji ogledani dokumenti"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep the &Ctrl; key pressed and use the &Tab; key to cycle forward through "
"the list. Additionally press the &Shift; key to reverse the direction."
msgstr ""
"Obdržite &Ctrl; pritisnjena tipka in uporabite &Tab; tipko za premikanje "
"naprej po seznamu. Poleg tega pritisnite &Shift; tipko za obratno smer."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Keep the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Tab;</keycombo> pressed "
"and can use the &Up;, &Down;, &Home; or &End; keys to navigate in the list. "
"Pressing a char key consecutively will cycle through all items with the "
"first matching in the list. If you release the shortcut keys the view will "
"switch to the selected document in the list."
msgstr ""
"Držite pritisnjeno bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Tab;</"
"keycombo> in lahko uporabite tipke &Up;, &Down;, &Home; ali &End; tipke za "
"navigacijo po seznamu. Če zaporedoma pritisnete tipko s črkami, se pomikate "
"po vseh elementih s prvim ujemanjem na seznamu. Če spustite bližnjične "
"tipke, se pogled preklopi na izbran dokument na seznamu."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1232
#, no-c-format
msgid "File System Browser"
msgstr "Brskalnik datotečnega sistema"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1234
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The File System Browser is a folder viewer, allowing you to open files from "
"a displayed folder in the current frame."
msgstr ""
"Brskalnik datotečnega sistema je pregledovalnik map, ki vam omogoča "
"odpiranje datotek iz prikazane mape v trenutnem okviru."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Filesystem Browser</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži brskalnik datotečnega sistema</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1247
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggle the display of &kate;'s Filesystem Browser."
msgstr "Preklopi prikaz brskalnika datotečnega sistema &kate;."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1257
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the top down, the Filesystem Browser consists of the following elements:"
msgstr ""
"Od zgoraj navzdol je brskalnik datotečnega sistema sestavljen iz naslednjih "
"elementov:"

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:1262
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1264
#, no-c-format
msgid "This contains standard navigations tool buttons:"
msgstr "To vsebuje standardne gumbe orodij za krmarjenje:"

#. Tag: guiicon
#: plugins.docbook:1267
#, no-c-format
msgid "Back"
msgstr "Nazaj"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1268
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the folder view to <command>cd</command> to the previously displayed "
"folder in the history. This button is disabled, if there is no previous item."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči, da pogled mape <command>cd</command> na prej prikazano mapo v "
"zgodovini. Ta gumb je onemogočen, če ni prejšnjega elementa."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: plugins.docbook:1272
#, no-c-format
msgid "Forward"
msgstr "Naprej"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1273
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Causes the folder view to <command>cd</command> to the next folder in the "
"history. This button is disabled, if there is no next folder."
msgstr ""
"Povzroči pogled mape na <command>cd</command> v naslednjo mapo v zgodovini. "
"Ta gumb je onemogočen, če ni naslednje mape."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: plugins.docbook:1282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Bookmarks"
msgstr "Zaznamki"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens a submenu to edit or add bookmarks and to add a new bookmark folder."
msgstr ""
"Odpre podmeni za urejanje ali dodajanje zaznamkov in dodajanje nove mape z "
"zaznamki."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: plugins.docbook:1286
#, no-c-format
msgid "Current Document Folder"
msgstr "Trenutna mapa dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1287
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button will cause the folder view to <command>cd</command> to the "
"folder of the currently active document if possible. This button is "
"disabled, if the active document is a new, unsaved file, or the folder in "
"which it resides can not be decided."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb bo povzročil, da bo pogled mape <command>cd</command> v mapo "
"trenutno aktivnega dokumenta, če je to mogoče. Ta gumb je onemogočen, če je "
"aktivni dokument nova, neshranjena datoteka ali ni mogoče določiti mape, v "
"kateri se nahaja."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: plugins.docbook:1294
#, no-c-format
msgid "Options"
msgstr "Opcije"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1298
#, no-c-format
msgid "Short View"
msgstr "Kratek pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1299
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays only the filenames."
msgstr "Prikaže samo imena datotek."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detailed View"
msgstr "Podroben pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Displays <guilabel>Name</guilabel>, <guilabel>Date</guilabel> and "
"<guilabel>Size</guilabel> of the files."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže <guilabel>Ime</guilabel>, <guilabel>Datum</guilabel> in "
"<guilabel>Velikost</guilabel> datotek."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1307
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tree View"
msgstr "Drevesni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1308
#, no-c-format
msgid "Like Short View, but folders can be expanded to view their contents."
msgstr ""
"Kot Kratek pogled, vendar je mogoče mape razširiti za ogled njihove vsebine."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Detailed Tree View"
msgstr "Podroben drevesni pogled"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This also allows folders to be expanded, but displays the additional columns "
"available in Detailed View."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča tudi razširitev map, vendar prikaže dodatne stolpce, ki so na "
"voljo v podrobnem pogledu."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1316
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Hidden Files"
msgstr "Pokaži skrite datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1317
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays files normally hidden by your &OS;."
msgstr "Prikaže datoteke, ki jih vaš &OS; običajno skriva."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1320
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically synchronize with current document"
msgstr "Samodejna sinhronizacija s trenutnim dokumentom"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1321
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this option is enabled the filesystem browser will automatically "
"<command>cd</command> to the folder of the document currently open in the "
"editing area every time it changes."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta možnost omogočena, bo brskalnik datotečnega sistema samodejno "
"<command>cd</command> v mapo dokumenta, ki je trenutno odprt v območju za "
"urejanje, vsakič, ko se spremeni."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:1332
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Location Entry"
msgstr "Vnos lokacije"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1334
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This displays a breadcrumb navigation to the currently open folder, "
"similarly to &dolphin;. You can click on a any folder to browse to it, or "
"click on one of the arrows to the left of a folder to select any folders "
"beneath it. You may also select from your list of Places by clicking the "
"leftmost icon in the breadcrumb navigation, which displays an icon that "
"represents your current Place."
msgstr ""
"To prikaže navigacijo po poti do trenutno odprte mape, podobno kot "
"&dolphin;. Lahko kliknete katero koli mapo, da jo poiščete, ali kliknete eno "
"od puščic na levi strani mape, da izberete katero koli mapo pod njo. "
"Izberete lahko tudi s seznama mest, tako da kliknete skrajno levo ikono v "
"navigacijski poti, ki prikaže ikono, ki predstavlja vaše trenutno mesto."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1340
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can also click to the right of the breadcrumbs to change them to a text "
"box where you can type the path of a folder to browse. The &URL; entry "
"maintains a list of previously typed paths. To choose one, use the arrow "
"button to the right of the entry."
msgstr ""
"Lahko tudi kliknete desno od drobtin, da jih spremenite v besedilno polje, "
"kjer lahko vnesete pot do mape za brskanje. &URL; vnos vzdržuje seznam "
"predhodno vnesenih poti. Če ga želite izbrati, uporabite puščični gumb na "
"desni strani vnosa."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1344
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &URL; entry has folder auto-completion. The completion method can be set "
"using the &RMB; menu of the text entry."
msgstr ""
"&URL; vnos ima samodejno dokončanje mape. Metodo dokončanja lahko nastavite "
"z &RMB; meni vnosa besedila."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:1351
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Folder View"
msgstr "Pogled mape"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1352
#, no-c-format
msgid "This is a standard &kde; folder view."
msgstr "To je standardni &kde; pogled mape."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:1356
#, no-c-format
msgid "A Filter Entry"
msgstr "Vnos filtra"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Filter entry allows you to enter a filter for the files displayed in the "
"folder view. The filter uses standard globs; patterns must be separated by "
"white space. Example: <userinput>*.cpp *.h *.moc</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Vnos Filter vam omogoča, da vnesete filter za datoteke, prikazane v pogledu "
"mape. Filter uporablja standardne kroglice; vzorci morajo biti ločeni s "
"presledkom. Primer: <userinput>*.cpp *.h *.moc</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1362
#, no-c-format
msgid "To display all files, enter a single asterisk <userinput>*</userinput>."
msgstr "Za prikaz vseh datotek vnesite eno zvezdico <userinput>*</userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The filter entry saves the last 10 filters entered between sessions. To use "
"one, press the arrow button on the right of the entry and select the desired "
"filter string. You can disable the filter by pressing the <guibutton>Clear "
"text</guibutton> button to the left of the autocompletion arrow button."
msgstr ""
"Vnos filtra shrani zadnjih 10 filtrov, vnesenih med sejami. Če ga želite "
"uporabiti, pritisnite puščični gumb na desni strani vnosa in izberite želeni "
"niz filtrov. Filter lahko onemogočite tako, da pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>Počisti besedilo</guibutton> levo od puščičnega gumba za "
"samodokončanje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin can be configured on the <guilabel>Filesystem Browser</guilabel> "
"page of <link linkend=\"configuring-kate-configdialog\">&kate;'s "
"configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik je mogoče konfigurirati na strani <guilabel>Brskalnik datotečnega "
"sistema</guilabel> v <link linkend=\"configuring-kate-configdialog"
"\">konfiguraciji &kate;</link>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1384
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toolbar"
msgstr "Orodna vrstica"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1385
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Configure the buttons on the Filesystem Browser toolbar by moving the ones "
"you want enabled to the <guilabel>Selected Actions</guilabel> list, and "
"order them using the arrow buttons at the side of the list."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirajte gumbe v orodni vrstici brskalnika datotečnega sistema tako, "
"da premaknete tiste, ki jih želite omogočiti, na seznam <guilabel>Izbrana "
"dejanja</guilabel> in jih razporedite s puščičnimi gumbi ob strani seznama."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1396
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Documents List"
msgstr "Seznam dokumentov"

#. Tag: primary
#: plugins.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documents list"
msgstr "Seznam dokumentov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1401
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The documents list displays a list of all documents currently open in "
"&kate;. Modified files will have a small <guiicon>floppy disk</guiicon> icon "
"on their left to indicate that state."
msgstr ""
"Seznam dokumentov prikaže seznam vseh dokumentov, ki so trenutno odprti v "
"&kate;. Spremenjene datoteke bodo imele majhno ikono <guiicon>diskete</"
"guiicon> na levi, ki označuje to stanje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1406
#, no-c-format
msgid "On the top the Documents list has a toolbar with the following buttons:"
msgstr "Na vrhu seznama dokumentov je orodna vrstica z naslednjimi gumbi:"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:1409
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"new-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Create new document"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"new-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Ustvari nov dokument"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:1412
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"open-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Open an existing document"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"open-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Odpri obstoječi dokument"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:1415
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-up-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Previous "
"Document"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-up-22.png\" "
"format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Prejšnji "
"dokument"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:1418
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Next Document"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-down-22.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> Naslednji "
"dokument"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:1421
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"save-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Save the current document"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"save-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Shranite trenutni dokument"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:1424
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-save-"
"as-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Save the current document under a new name"
msgstr ""
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-save-"
"as-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guiicon> "
"Shranite trenutni dokument pod novim ime"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1429
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default, the Documents list appears in <guimenuitem>Tree Mode</"
"guimenuitem>, which displays the folder structure surrounding all currently "
"open documents. Also available is <guimenuitem>List Mode</guimenuitem>, "
"which displays a simple list of all open documents. You can switch modes by "
"right-clicking on the list and selecting from the <guisubmenu>View Mode</"
"guisubmenu> menu."
msgstr ""
"Privzeto se seznam dokumentov prikaže v <guimenuitem>Drevesnem načinu</"
"guimenuitem>, ki prikazuje strukturo map, ki obdajajo vse trenutno odprte "
"dokumente. Na voljo je tudi <guimenuitem>Način seznama</guimenuitem>, ki "
"prikaže preprost seznam vseh odprtih dokumentov. Načine lahko preklopite "
"tako, da z desno miškino tipko kliknete seznam in izberete v meniju "
"<guisubmenu>Način pogleda</guisubmenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If two or more files with the same name (located in different folders) are "
"open in <guimenuitem>List Mode</guimenuitem>, the names of the second will "
"be prepended <quote>(2)</quote> and so on. The tool-tip for the file will "
"display its full name including the path, allowing you to choose the desired "
"one."
msgstr ""
"Če sta v <guimenuitem>načinu seznama</guimenuitem> odprti dve ali več "
"datotek z enakim imenom (ki se nahajajo v različnih mapah), bodo imena druge "
"dodane <quote>(2)</quote> in tako naprej. Namig za orodje za datoteko bo "
"prikazal njeno polno ime, vključno s potjo, kar vam bo omogočilo, da "
"izberete želeno."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To display a document in the currently active frame, click the document name "
"in the list."
msgstr ""
"Za prikaz dokumenta v trenutno aktivnem okviru kliknite ime dokumenta na "
"seznamu."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1443
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The context menu has some common actions from the <guimenu>File</guimenu> "
"menu."
msgstr ""
"Kontekstni meni ima nekaj običajnih dejanj iz menija <guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1445
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally there are filemanager actions to rename or delete the file. "
"With <guimenuitem>Copy Location</guimenuitem> you can copy the full path of "
"the document to the clipboard."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega obstajajo dejanja upravitelja datotek za preimenovanje ali "
"brisanje datoteke. Z <guimenuitem>Kopiraj lokacijo</guimenuitem> lahko "
"kopirate celotno pot dokumenta v odložišče."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can sort the list in a few different ways by right clicking the list and "
"selecting from the <guisubmenu>Sort By</guisubmenu> menu. The options are:"
msgstr ""
"Seznam lahko razvrstite na več različnih načinov, tako da z desno miškino "
"tipko kliknete seznam in izberete v meniju <guisubmenu>Razvrsti po</"
"guisubmenu>. Možnosti so:"

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1456
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Name"
msgstr "Ime dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1457
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists the documents alphabetically by their name."
msgstr "Navede dokumente po abecednem redu po njihovih imenih."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Document Path"
msgstr "Pot dokumenta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1462
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists the documents alphabetically by the path to them."
msgstr "Navede dokumente po abecedi poti do njih."

#. Tag: guimenuitem
#: plugins.docbook:1466
#, no-c-format
msgid "Opening Order"
msgstr "Otvoritveni ukaz"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1467
#, no-c-format
msgid "Lists the documents in the order of opening."
msgstr "Navede dokumente po vrstnem redu odpiranja."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1474
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The document list will per default visualize your history by shading the "
"entries for the most recent documents with a background color. If the "
"document was edited, an extra color is blended in. The most recent document "
"has the strongest color, so that you can easily find the documents you are "
"working on. This feature can be disabled in the <link linkend=\"config-"
"dialog-documents\">Documents</link> page of the configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Seznam dokumentov bo privzeto prikazal vašo zgodovino tako, da bo vnose za "
"najnovejše dokumente osenčil z barvo ozadja. Če je bil dokument urejen, se "
"doda dodatna barva. Najnovejši dokument ima najmočnejšo barvo, tako da lahko "
"preprosto najdete dokumente, na katerih delate. To funkcijo lahko "
"onemogočite na strani <link linkend=\"config-dialog-documents\">Dokumenti</"
"link> v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1481
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default location of the document list in the &kate; window is to the "
"left of the editing area."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta lokacija seznama dokumentov v datoteki &kate; okno je levo od "
"območja za urejanje."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1492
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Previous Document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Up;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Prejšnji dokument</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1500
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the document displayed above the currently open document in the "
"Documents list."
msgstr ""
"Odpre dokument, prikazan nad trenutno odprtim dokumentom na seznamu "
"dokumentov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1505
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Next Document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Down;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naslednji dokument</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1513
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Opens the document displayed below the currently open document in the "
"Documents list."
msgstr ""
"Odpre dokument, prikazan pod trenutno odprtim dokumentom na seznamu "
"dokumentov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1518
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>View</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Show Active</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pokaži aktivno</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1523
#, no-c-format
msgid "Displays the currently open document in the Documents list."
msgstr "Prikaže trenutno odprt dokument na seznamu dokumentov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1536
#, no-c-format
msgid "Background Shading"
msgstr "Senčenje ozadja"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This section allows you to enable or disable the background shading "
"visualization of your recent activity, and choose which colors to use if "
"enabled."
msgstr ""
"Ta razdelek vam omogoča, da omogočite ali onemogočite vizualizacijo senčenja "
"ozadja vaše nedavne dejavnosti in izberete, katere barve želite uporabiti, "
"če so omogočene."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1543
#, no-c-format
msgid "Sort By"
msgstr "Razvrsti po"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1544
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Set how you want the document list sorted. This can be set from the &RMB; "
"menu in the document list as well."
msgstr ""
"Nastavite, kako želite razvrstiti seznam dokumentov. To lahko nastavite iz "
"&RMB; meni tudi na seznamu dokumentov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1549
#, no-c-format
msgid "View Mode"
msgstr "Način pogleda"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1550
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This provides two options that effect the display of the Documents tool "
"view. The <guilabel>Tree View</guilabel> option will display the documents "
"in a tree underneath the folders they are in, while the <guilabel>List View</"
"guilabel> option will display a flat list of documents."
msgstr ""
"To ponuja dve možnosti, ki vplivata na prikaz pogleda orodja Dokumenti. "
"Možnost <guilabel>Drevesni pogled</guilabel> bo prikazala dokumente v "
"drevesu pod mapami, v katerih so, medtem ko bo možnost <guilabel>Pogled "
"seznama</guilabel> prikazala ploski seznam dokumentov."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Full Path"
msgstr "Prikaži celotno pot"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1559
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Tree View and this option are enabled, the folder entries displayed in "
"the Documents tool view will display the full filesystem path to the folder "
"in addition to the name of the folder. It has no effect in List View."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta omogočena drevesni pogled in ta možnost, bodo vnosi mape, prikazani v "
"pogledu orodja Dokumenti, poleg imena mape prikazali celotno pot datotečnega "
"sistema do mape. V pogledu seznama nima učinka."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1566
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Toolbar"
msgstr "Prikaži orodno vrstico"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1567
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When Tree View and this option are enabled, a toolbar with actions like "
"<guibutton>Save</guibutton> is displayed above the list of documents. "
"Uncheck this option if the toolbar should be hidden."
msgstr ""
"Ko sta omogočena drevesni pogled in ta možnost, je nad seznamom dokumentov "
"prikazana orodna vrstica z dejanji, kot je <guibutton>Shrani</guibutton>. "
"Počistite to možnost, če naj bo orodna vrstica skrita."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:1574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show Close Button"
msgstr "Prikaži gumb za zapiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When this option is enabled, &kate; will show a close button for opened "
"documents on hover."
msgstr ""
"Ko je ta možnost omogočena, &kate; bo prikazal gumb za zapiranje za odprte "
"dokumente, ko premaknete miškin kazalec."

#. Tag: author
#: plugins.docbook:1589 plugins.docbook:3424
#, no-c-format
msgid "<firstname>Martin</firstname> <surname>Gergov</surname>"
msgstr "<firstname>Martin</firstname> <surname>Gergov</surname>"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1593
#, no-c-format
msgid "&gdb; Plugin"
msgstr "&gdb; Vtičnik"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1598
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate;'s &gdb; plugin provides a simple frontend to any debugger that "
"supports the <ulink url=\"https://microsoft.github.io/debug-adapter-protocol/"
"\">Debugger Adapter Protocol</ulink>. In particular, that includes the GNU "
"Project Debugger, aka GDB, as <ulink url=\"https://sourceware.org/gdb/"
"current/onlinedocs/gdb.html/Debugger-Adapter-Protocol.html\">outlined here</"
"ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik &kate; &gdb; ponuja preprost vmesnik za kateri koli razhroščevalnik, "
"ki podpira <ulink url=\"https://microsoft.github.io/debug-adapter-protocol/"
"\">Protokol adapterja razhroščevalnika</ulink>. To vključuje zlasti "
"razhroščevalnik projekta GNU, znan tudi kot GDB, kot je <ulink url=\"https://"
"sourceware.org/gdb/current/onlinedocs/gdb.html/Debugger-Adapter-Protocol.html"
"\">opisan tukaj</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Previous experience with &gdb; is strongly recommended. For more information "
"on using &gdb;, visit <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/gdb/\">the "
"&gdb; website</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Prejšnje izkušnje z &gdb; je močno priporočljivo. Za več informacij o "
"uporabi &gdb; obiščite <ulink url=\"https://www.gnu.org/software/gdb/"
"\">&gdb; spletno mesto</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enable the &gdb; plugin in <link linkend=\"config-dialog-plugins"
"\">the Plugins section of &kate;'s configuration</link>."
msgstr ""
"Omogočite lahko &gdb; vtičnik v <link linkend=\"config-dialog-plugins"
"\">razdelku Vtičniki konfiguracije &kate;</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1616
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you compile using &gcc;/<command>g++</command> you might want to use the "
"<command><parameter>-ggdb</parameter></command> command line argument."
msgstr ""
"Če prevajate z &gcc;/<command>g++</command>, boste morda želeli uporabiti "
"argument ukazne vrstice <command><parameter>-ggdb</parameter></command>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After these preparations are made, open the source file in &kate;, select "
"the \"debugger profile\", enter the path to the executable in the "
"<guilabel>Settings</guilabel> tab of the <guilabel>Debug View</guilabel> "
"tool view, and select <menuchoice><guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Start "
"Debugging</guimenuitem></menuchoice> from the menu to get started."
msgstr ""
"Ko so te priprave opravljene, odprite izvorno datoteko v &kate;, izberite "
"\"profil razhroščevalnika\", v zavihek <guilabel>Nastavitve</guilabel> v "
"pogledu orodij <guilabel>Pogled razhroščevalnika</guilabel> vnesite pot do "
"izvedljive datoteke in v meniju izberite "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Razhroščevalnik</guimenu><guimenuitem>Začni "
"razhroščevanje</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, da začnete."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1628
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The \"debugger profile\" selects the DAP server to use (e.g. GDB) and the "
"way in which to launch this server. A typical case is to have the server "
"launch a process as specified above, but it may also attach to a running "
"process (in which case a PID will have to be specified rather than an "
"executable). There may also be other modes which are specific to the "
"language and DAP server. See also later for additional background and "
"configuration details on this."
msgstr ""
"\"Profil razhroščevalnika\" izbere strežnik DAP, ki ga bo uporabil (npr. "
"GDB), in način zagona tega strežnika. Tipičen primer je, da strežnik zažene "
"proces, kot je določeno zgoraj, lahko pa se poveže tudi z delujočim procesom "
"(v tem primeru je treba namesto izvedljive datoteke določiti PID). Obstajajo "
"lahko tudi drugi načini, ki so specifični za jezik in strežnik DAP. Za "
"dodatne podrobnosti o ozadju in konfiguraciji glejte tudi kasneje."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1640
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu and Toolbar Structure"
msgstr "Struktura menija in orodne vrstice"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1642
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All of these options are available in &kate;'s menus, and many are available "
"on the Debug toolbar as well."
msgstr ""
"Vse te možnosti so na voljo v menijih &kate;, mnoge pa so na voljo tudi v "
"orodni vrstici za odpravljanje napak."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1648
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool View</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show "
"Debug View</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled orodja</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži pogled za odpravljanje napak</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a tool view containing &gdb; output, the &gdb; command line used, and "
"other settings."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže pogled orodja, ki vsebuje &gdb; izhod, &gdb; uporabljena ukazna "
"vrstica in druge nastavitve."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1656
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool View</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Show "
"Locals and Stack</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogled orodij</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Pokaži lokalno in sklad</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1659
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows a list of all currently loaded variables and their values and a &gdb; "
"backtrace."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže seznam vseh trenutno naloženih spremenljivk in njihovih vrednosti "
"ter &gdb; povratna sled."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1664
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guisubmenu>Targets</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tarče</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1667
#, no-c-format
msgid "A submenu containing a list of targets (executables)."
msgstr "Podmeni, ki vsebuje seznam ciljev (izvršljivih datotek)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1672
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Start Debugging</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Začni odpravljanje napak</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1675
#, no-c-format
msgid "Starts &gdb; with a target."
msgstr "Zažene &gdb; s tarčo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1679
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Kill / Stop Debugging</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uniči/ustavi odpravljanje "
"napak</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stops &gdb;."
msgstr "Ustavi &gdb;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1686
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Restart Debugging</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"Ustavi &gdb;.<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Ponovni zagon "
"odpravljanja napak</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1689
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restarts &gdb;."
msgstr "Ponovno zažene &gdb;."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1693
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Toggle Breakpoint / Break</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Preklopi prekinitveno "
"točko / prekinitev</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1696
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set a breakpoint at the current cursor position."
msgstr "Nastavite prelomno točko na trenutnem položaju kazalke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1701
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Step In</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Vstopite</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1704
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute the present statement (function call will be debugged)."
msgstr "Izvedite trenutni stavek (klic funkcije bo odpravljen)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1709
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Step Over</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Prestopite</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1712
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute the present statement (function call will not be debugged)."
msgstr "Izvedite trenutni stavek (klic funkcije ne bo odpravljen)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:1717
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Debug</guimenu><guimenuitem>Step Out</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odpravljanje napak</guimenu><guimenuitem>Izstopite</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
