#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1897 plugins.docbook:3735
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 participant Martin Gergov for writing "
"much of this section."
msgstr ""
"Posebna zahvala udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 Martinu Gergovu za pisanje "
"večjega dela tega razdelka."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1905
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin's configuration page defines the \"debugger profiles\" which can "
"be selected. The default configuration (JSON) is shown there, and it can be "
"\"overlayed\" by a user provided of similar form. An example excerpt is as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"Stran konfiguracije vtičnika določa \"profile razhroščevalnikov\", ki jih je "
"mogoče izbrati. Tam je prikazana privzeta konfiguracija (JSON), ki jo lahko "
"uporabnik \"prekrije\" s podobnim obrazcem. Primer odlomka je naslednji:"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:1911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \"dap\": {\n"
"        \"debugpy\": {\n"
"            \"url\": \"https://github.com/microsoft/debugpy\",\n"
"            \"run\": {\n"
"                \"command\": [\"python\", \"-m\", \"debugpy\", \"--listen\", "
"\"${#run.port}\", \"--wait-for-client\"],\n"
"                \"port\": 0,\n"
"                \"supportsSourceRequest\": false\n"
"            },\n"
"            \"configurations\": {\n"
"                \"launch\": {\n"
"                    \"commandArgs\": [\"${file}\", \"${args|list}\"],\n"
"                    \"request\": {\n"
"                        \"command\": \"attach\",\n"
"                        \"stopOnEntry\": true,\n"
"                        \"redirectOutput\": true\n"
"                    }\n"
"                },\n"
"                \"attach\": {\n"
"                    \"commandArgs\": [\"--pid\", \"${pid}\"],\n"
"                    \"request\": {\n"
"                        \"command\": \"attach\",\n"
"                        \"stopOnEntry\": true,\n"
"                        \"redirectOutput\": true\n"
"                    }\n"
"                },\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"gdb\": {\n"
"            \"url\": \"gdb\",\n"
"            \"run\": {\n"
"                \"command\": [\n"
"                    \"gdb\",\n"
"                    \"-i\",\n"
"                    \"dap\"\n"
"                ],\n"
"                \"redirectStderr\": true,\n"
"                \"redirectStdout\": true,\n"
"                \"supportsSourceRequest\": true\n"
"            },\n"
"            \"configurations\": {\n"
"                \"launch (debug)\": {\n"
"                    \"request\": {\n"
"                        \"command\": \"launch\",\n"
"                        \"mode\": \"debug\",\n"
"                        \"program\": \"${file}\",\n"
"                        \"args\": \"${args|list}\",\n"
"                        \"cwd\": \"${workdir}\"\n"
"                    }\n"
"                }\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \"dap\": {\n"
"        \"debugpy\": {\n"
"            \"url\": \"https://github.com/microsoft/debugpy\",\n"
"            \"run\": {\n"
"                \"command\": [\"python\", \"-m\", \"debugpy\", \"--listen\", "
"\"${#run.port}\", \"--wait-for-client\"],\n"
"                \"port\": 0,\n"
"                \"supportsSourceRequest\": false\n"
"            },\n"
"            \"configurations\": {\n"
"                \"launch\": {\n"
"                    \"commandArgs\": [\"${file}\", \"${args|list}\"],\n"
"                    \"request\": {\n"
"                        \"command\": \"attach\",\n"
"                        \"stopOnEntry\": true,\n"
"                        \"redirectOutput\": true\n"
"                    }\n"
"                },\n"
"                \"attach\": {\n"
"                    \"commandArgs\": [\"--pid\", \"${pid}\"],\n"
"                    \"request\": {\n"
"                        \"command\": \"attach\",\n"
"                        \"stopOnEntry\": true,\n"
"                        \"redirectOutput\": true\n"
"                    }\n"
"                },\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"gdb\": {\n"
"            \"url\": \"gdb\",\n"
"            \"run\": {\n"
"                \"command\": [\n"
"                    \"gdb\",\n"
"                    \"-i\",\n"
"                    \"dap\"\n"
"                ],\n"
"                \"redirectStderr\": true,\n"
"                \"redirectStdout\": true,\n"
"                \"supportsSourceRequest\": true\n"
"            },\n"
"            \"configurations\": {\n"
"                \"launch (debug)\": {\n"
"                    \"request\": {\n"
"                        \"command\": \"launch\",\n"
"                        \"mode\": \"debug\",\n"
"                        \"program\": \"${file}\",\n"
"                        \"args\": \"${args|list}\",\n"
"                        \"cwd\": \"${workdir}\"\n"
"                    }\n"
"                }\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1913
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each of the entries in <literal>configurations</literal> is combined with "
"the <literal>run</literal> data and forms a \"profile\". This specifies the "
"DAP server to launch along with its arguments, where the latter are specific "
"to the profile (<literal>commandArgs</literal>). The other parts specify the "
"DAP protocol request (<literal>launch</literal> or <literal>attach</"
"literal>), along with DAP specific extensions."
msgstr ""
"Vsak od vnosov v <literal>configurations</literal> je združen s podatki "
"<literal>run</literal> in tvori \"profil\". Ta določa strežnik DAP, ki ga je "
"treba zagnati, skupaj z njegovimi argumenti, pri čemer so slednji specifični "
"za profil (<literal>commandArgs</literal>). Drugi deli določajo zahtevo "
"protokola DAP (<literal>launch</literal> ali <literal>attach</literal>) "
"skupaj z razširitvami, specifičnimi za DAP."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1922
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Of course, the specified server should be installed (and typically also in "
"<literal>PATH</literal> for proper execution)."
msgstr ""
"Seveda mora biti navedeni strežnik nameščen (in običajno tudi v "
"<literal>PATH</literal> za pravilno izvajanje)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1927
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Various stages of override/merge are applied; user configuration (loaded "
"from file) overrides (internal) default configuration, and the \"dap\" entry "
"in <literal>.kateproject</literal> project configuration in turn overrides."
msgstr ""
"Uporabljene so različne stopnje preglasitve/združitve; uporabniška "
"konfiguracija (naložena iz datoteke) preglasi (notranjo) privzeto "
"konfiguracijo, vnos \"dap\" v konfiguraciji projekta <literal>.kateproject</"
"literal> pa nato preglasi."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:1936 plugins.docbook:2892
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execution environment setup"
msgstr "Nastavitev izvajalnega okolja"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1938
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"More background and specifics can be found in the <link linkend=\"lspclient-"
"exec\">LSP Client Execution environment</link> section below. But suffice it "
"to say here it may be needed to run the debuggee process (and the DAP "
"server) in a \"special environment\", whether merely defined by environment "
"variables or some container (providing the required dependencies and "
"circumstances for proper execution)."
msgstr ""
"Več ozadja in podrobnosti najdete v spodnjem razdelku <link linkend="
"\"lspclient-exec\">Izvedbeno okolje odjemalca LSP</link>. Vendar zadostuje, "
"če tukaj omenimo, da bo morda treba zagnati proces debuggee (in strežnik "
"DAP) v \"posebnem okolju\", ki ga določajo zgolj spremenljivke okolja ali "
"kakšen vsebnik (ki zagotavlja potrebne odvisnosti in okoliščine za pravilno "
"izvajanje)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1947
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Similar to the example in the referenced section, the following "
"configuration may be provided in a <literal>.kateproject</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Podobno kot v primeru v omenjenem razdelku je lahko naslednja konfiguracija "
"podana v datoteki <literal>.kateproject</literal>."

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:1952
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    // this may also be an array of objects\n"
"    \"exec\": {\n"
"        \"hostname\": \"foobar\"\n"
"        // the command could also be an array of string\n"
"        \"prefix\": \"podman exec -i foobarcontainer\",\n"
"        \"mapRemoteRoot\": true,\n"
"        \"pathMappings\": [\n"
"            // either of the following forms are possible\n"
"            // a more automagic alternative exists as well, see referenced "
"section\n"
"            [ \"/dir/on/host\", \"/mounted/in/container\" ]\n"
"            { \"localRoot\": \"/local/dir\", \"remoteRoot\": \"/remote/dir"
"\" }\n"
"        ]\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"dap\": {\n"
"        \"debugpy\": {\n"
"            \"run\": {\n"
"                // in this section, it applies to all configurations\n"
"                // this will match/join with the above object\n"
"                \"exec\": { \"hostname\": \"foobar\" },\n"
"                // if server is connected to,\n"
"                // optionally specify explicit port (which is suitable "
"published/forwarded)\n"
"                \"port\": 5678,\n"
"                // the server may then also have to accept more than "
"localhost\n"
"                \"host\": \"0.0.0.0\"\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    // this may also be an array of objects\n"
"    \"exec\": {\n"
"        \"hostname\": \"foobar\"\n"
"        // the command could also be an array of string\n"
"        \"prefix\": \"podman exec -i foobarcontainer\",\n"
"        \"mapRemoteRoot\": true,\n"
"        \"pathMappings\": [\n"
"            // either of the following forms are possible\n"
"            // a more automagic alternative exists as well, see referenced "
"section\n"
"            [ \"/dir/on/host\", \"/mounted/in/container\" ]\n"
"            { \"localRoot\": \"/local/dir\", \"remoteRoot\": \"/remote/dir"
"\" }\n"
"        ]\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"dap\": {\n"
"        \"debugpy\": {\n"
"            \"run\": {\n"
"                // in this section, it applies to all configurations\n"
"                // this will match/join with the above object\n"
"                \"exec\": { \"hostname\": \"foobar\" },\n"
"                // if server is connected to,\n"
"                // optionally specify explicit port (which is suitable "
"published/forwarded)\n"
"                \"port\": 5678,\n"
"                // the server may then also have to accept more than "
"localhost\n"
"                \"host\": \"0.0.0.0\"\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The referenced section should be consulted for details, but in essence the "
"<literal>prefix</literal> will be prepended before the DAP server command "
"line specified elsewhere. The effect is that the server is run within the "
"specified container and then in turn also the launched process. The "
"<literal>pathMapping</literal> arranges for transformation of filepaths "
"between editor's view and DAP server (container) view, e.g. when dealing "
"with setting of breakpoints or handling of reported backtraces. Note that "
"such mapping is optional and may or may not be useful. When dealing with C/C+"
"+ code that is compiled on \"host\", the symbol info references source files "
"on host which do not exist at all in the other environment. However, in "
"other scripted (e.g. python) circumstances, actual runtime files are "
"referenced (on the other environment)."
msgstr ""
"Za podrobnosti glejte navedeni razdelek, vendar bo v bistvu "
"<literal>predpona</literal> dodana pred ukazno vrstico strežnika DAP, ki je "
"navedena drugje. Učinek je, da se strežnik izvaja znotraj določenega "
"vsebnika, nato pa tudi zagnani proces. <literal>pathMapping</literal> "
"poskrbi za pretvorbo poti datotek med pogledom urejevalnika in pogledom "
"strežnika DAP (vsebnika), npr. pri nastavljanju prekinitvenih točk ali "
"obravnavi sporočenih povratnih sledi. Upoštevajte, da je takšno "
"preslikavanje neobvezno in je lahko uporabno ali pa tudi ne. Pri delu s kodo "
"C/C++, ki je prevedena na \"gostitelju\", se informacije o simbolih "
"sklicujejo na izvorne datoteke na gostitelju, ki v drugem okolju sploh ne "
"obstajajo. Vendar pa se v drugih okoliščinah skripta (npr. python) "
"sklicujejo na dejanske datoteke izvajalnega okolja (v drugem okolju)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1969
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following must evidently be kept in mind."
msgstr "Očitno je treba upoštevati naslednje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The DAP server must be present in the environment/container, which must be "
"configured to support proper debugger operation (so, if needed, privileged, "
"capabilities)."
msgstr ""
"Strežnik DAP mora biti prisoten v okolju/vsebniku, ki mora biti konfiguriran "
"tako, da podpira pravilno delovanje razhroščevalnika (torej, če je potrebno, "
"tudi privilegirane zmogljivosti)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1981
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Communication between editor and DAP must be possible. In case of a "
"container, the latter should either use host networking, or provide a "
"suitable mapped/published port along with corresponding config snippet as in "
"above example (as an auto-selected one in case of port 0 would not make it "
"through)."
msgstr ""
"Komunikacija med urejevalnikom in DAP mora biti možna. V primeru vsebnika "
"mora slednji uporabljati omrežje gostitelja ali zagotoviti ustrezna "
"preslikana/objavljena vrata skupaj z ustreznim delčkom konfiguracije, kot v "
"zgornjem primeru (saj samodejno izbrana vrata v primeru vrat 0 ne bi šla "
"skozi)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A specified executable/PID should be in \"container\" perspective, as well "
"as any (debuggee executable) arguments."
msgstr ""
"Določena izvedljiva datoteka/PID mora biti v perspektivi \"vsebnika\", kot "
"tudi vsi argumenti (izvedljive datoteke, iz katere je odpravljena napaka)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:1995
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also, as in the LSP case, some environment variables are set; "
"<literal>KATE_EXEC_PLUGIN</literal> is set to <literal>dap</literal>, "
"<literal>KATE_EXEC_SERVER</literal> is set to the debugger/language type (e."
"g. <literal>python</literal>) and <literal>KATE_EXEC_PROFILE</literal> is "
"set to the configuration entry (e.g. <literal>launch</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako so, tako kot v primeru LSP, nastavljene nekatere okoljske "
"spremenljivke; <literal>KATE_EXEC_PLUGIN</literal> je nastavljena na "
"<literal>dap</literal>, <literal>KATE_EXEC_SERVER</literal> je nastavljena "
"na vrsto razhroščevalnika/jezika (npr. <literal>python</literal>) in "
"<literal>KATE_EXEC_PROFILE</literal> je nastavljena na  vnos konfiguracije "
"(npr. <literal>launch</literal>)."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2014
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Plugin"
msgstr "Projektni vtičnik"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2019
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The basic idea of the Project plugin is to have a structured list of files "
"belonging to the project with the following properties:"
msgstr ""
"Osnovna ideja vtičnika Projekt je imeti strukturiran seznam datotek, ki "
"pripadajo projektu, z naslednjimi lastnostmi:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2023
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provide a structured view of the files"
msgstr "Zagotovite strukturiran pogled na datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2024
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make it easy and very fast to open and switch projects"
msgstr ""
"Omogočite preprosto in zelo hitro odpiranje in preklapljanje med projekti"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2025
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support search and replace for a project"
msgstr "Podpora za iskanje in zamenjavo za projekt"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2026
#, no-c-format
msgid "Provide simple auto completion"
msgstr "Zagotovite preprosto samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2027
#, no-c-format
msgid "Make it simple to quickly open files in the project"
msgstr "Poenostavite hitro odpiranje datotek v projektu"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2028
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support for building the project"
msgstr "Podpora za gradnjo projekta"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2033
#, no-c-format
msgid "Structured View of the Files"
msgstr "Strukturiran pogled datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2035
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the Project plugin is loaded in the &kate; configuration page, open a "
"file in a project and a sidebar appears that lists all projects as well as "
"the project files as follows:"
msgstr ""
"Ko je vtičnik Projekt naložen v &kate; konfiguracijsko stran, odprite "
"datoteko v projektu in prikaže se stranska vrstica, ki navaja vse projekte "
"in projektne datoteke, kot sledi:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:2040
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project View"
msgstr "Pogled projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2046
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As you can see, the currently active project is <quote>Kate</quote>, and its "
"contents is listed in the tree view. Clicking on files in the tree view "
"opens the file in the editor. Further, a context menu is provided with which "
"you can open files with other applications, such as a <filename class="
"\"extension\">.ui</filename> file with Qt Designer."
msgstr ""
"Kot lahko vidite, je trenutno aktiven projekt <quote>Kate</quote>, njegova "
"vsebina pa je navedena v drevesnem pogledu. S klikom na datoteke v drevesnem "
"pogledu se datoteka odpre v urejevalniku. Poleg tega je na voljo kontekstni "
"meni, s katerim lahko odprete datoteke z drugimi aplikacijami, kot je "
"datoteka <filename class=\"extension\">.ui</filename> s Qt Designerjem."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2050
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can filter the items by typing parts of the file name you are looking "
"for into the search bar at the bottom of the list."
msgstr ""
"Elemente lahko filtrirate tako, da v iskalno vrstico na dnu seznama vnesete "
"dele imena datoteke, ki jo iščete."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2055
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switching Projects"
msgstr "Preklapljanje projektov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2057
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The idea is that you never have to open a project manually, this is even not "
"supported at all. Hence, what happens if you open a file, the Project plugin "
"quickly scans the folder and its parent folders for a <filename>."
"kateproject</filename> file. If found, the project is automatically loaded."
msgstr ""
"Ideja je, da vam nikoli ni treba odpreti projekta ročno, to celo sploh ni "
"podprto. Torej, kaj se zgodi, če odprete datoteko, vtičnik Projekt hitro "
"pregleda mapo in njene nadrejene mape za datoteko <filename>.kateproject</"
"filename>. Če je najden, se projekt samodejno naloži."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2062
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Furthermore, if you open another document in &kate;, that belongs to another "
"project, the Project plugin automatically switches the current project. So "
"intuitively, always the correct project is active. Of course, you can also "
"switch the currently active project using the combo box."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega, če v &kate; odprete drug dokument, ki pripada drugemu projektu, "
"vtičnik Projekt samodejno preklopi trenutni projekt. Tako je intuitivno "
"vedno aktiven pravi projekt. Seveda lahko s kombiniranim poljem tudi "
"zamenjate trenutno aktivni projekt."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2070
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search and Replace in Projects"
msgstr "Iskanje in zamenjava v projektih"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2072
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; has a Search and Replace plugin that shows up in the bottom sidebar. "
"If a project is loaded, open the Search and Replace sidebar, and switch to "
"the mode to search and replace in the current project:"
msgstr ""
"&kate; ima vtičnik za iskanje in zamenjavo, ki se prikaže v spodnji stranski "
"vrstici. Če je projekt naložen, odprite stransko vrstico Iskanje in "
"zamenjava in preklopite v način za iskanje in zamenjavo v trenutnem projektu:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:2077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in Projects"
msgstr "Iskanje v Projektih"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2086
#, no-c-format
msgid "Simple Auto Completion"
msgstr "Preprosto samodejno dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2088
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"With the knowledge of all files belonging to a project, the Project plugin "
"provides simple auto completion facilities based on CTags. If a project is "
"initially opened, CTags parses all project files in a background thread and "
"saves the CTags information to <filename class=\"directory\">/tmp</"
"filename>. This file then is used to populate the auto completion popup in "
"&kate;."
msgstr ""
"S poznavanjem vseh datotek, ki pripadajo projektu, vtičnik Projekt "
"zagotavlja preproste zmogljivosti za samodejno dokončanje, ki temeljijo na "
"CTags. Če je projekt prvotno odprt, CTags razčleni vse projektne datoteke v "
"niti v ozadju in shrani informacije CTags v <filename class=\"directory\">/"
"tmp</filename>. Ta datoteka se nato uporabi za zapolnitev pojavnega okna za "
"samodejno dokončanje v &kate;."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In contrast, without this auto completion, &kate; is only capable of showing "
"auto completion items based on the words in the current file. So the auto "
"completion provided by the Project plugin is much more powerful."
msgstr ""
"Nasprotno pa brez tega samodejnega dokončanja &kate; je sposoben prikazati "
"le elemente samodokončanja na podlagi besed v trenutni datoteki. Tako je "
"samodejno dokončanje, ki ga ponuja vtičnik Projekt, veliko močnejše."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:2099
#, no-c-format
msgid "Completion in Projects"
msgstr "Dokončanje v projektih"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2105
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If CTags is missing, a passive popup warns you about this issue. It is also "
"noteworthy, that the CTags file in <filename class=\"directory\">/tmp</"
"filename> is cleaned up when &kate; exits, so the plugin does not pollute "
"any folder with unwanted files."
msgstr ""
"Če CTags manjka, vas o tej težavi opozori pasivno pojavno okno. Omeniti "
"velja tudi, da se datoteka CTags v <filename class=\"directory\">/tmp</"
"filename> počisti, ko &kate; zapre, tako da vtičnik ne onesnaži nobene mape "
"z neželenimi datotekami."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Support for Building the Project"
msgstr "Podpora za izgradnjo projekta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2114
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Another feature is to have support for the <link linkend=\"projects-build-"
"support\">Build Plugin</link>, so that it automatically is configured "
"correctly."
msgstr ""
"Druga funkcija je podpora za <link linkend=\"projects-build-support\">Build "
"Vtičnik</link>, tako da je samodejno pravilno konfiguriran."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2120
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Projects"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje projektov"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2124
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading Projects Automatically"
msgstr "Samodejno nalaganje projektov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2126
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Project plugin has an auto-loading feature. You can read the file list "
"from the version control system. To this end, auto-loading for the "
"respective version control system needs to be enabled in the settings "
"(enabled by default):"
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik Projekt ima funkcijo samodejnega nalaganja. Seznam datotek lahko "
"preberete iz sistema za nadzor različic. V ta namen mora biti v nastavitvah "
"omogočeno samodejno nalaganje za ustrezni sistem za nadzor različic "
"(privzeto omogočeno):"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:2132
#, no-c-format
msgid "Project Plugin Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija vtičnika projekta"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating Projects Manually"
msgstr "Ročno ustvarjanje projektov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2142
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You just have to create a <filename>.kateproject</filename> file in the root "
"folder of the project. For instance, the <quote>Kate</quote> <filename>."
"kateproject</filename> file looks like this:"
msgstr ""
"Samo ustvariti morate datoteko <filename>.kateproject</filename> v korenski "
"mapi projekta. Na primer, datoteka <quote>Kate</quote> <filename>."
"kateproject</filename> je videti takole:"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"Kate\",\n"
"  \"files\": [\n"
"    {\n"
"      \"git\": 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  ]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"   \"ime\": \"Kate\",\n"
"   \"datoteke\": [\n"
"     {\n"
"       \"git\": 1\n"
"     }\n"
"   ]\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2149
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The file content is written in &JSON; syntax. The project name is "
"<quote>Kate</quote>, and the files contained in should be read from &git;."
msgstr ""
"Vsebina datoteke je zapisana v &JSON; sintaksa. Ime projekta je <quote>Kate</"
"quote>, datoteke, ki jih vsebuje, pa je treba brati iz &git;."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Also supported instead of <literal>git</literal> is subversion through "
"<literal>svn</literal> and mercurial through <literal>hg</literal>. If you "
"do not want to read files from a version control system, you can just invoke "
"kate from command line as: <screen>\n"
"kate /path/to/folder\n"
"</screen> or you can tell it to recursively load files from directories as "
"follows:"
msgstr ""
"Namesto <literal>git</literal> je podprta tudi subverzija prek <literal>svn</"
"literal> in mercurial prek <literal>hg</literal>. Če ne želite brati datotek "
"iz sistema za nadzor različic, lahko preprosto pokličete kate iz ukazne "
"vrstice kot: <screen>\n"
"kate /pot/do/mape\n"
"</screen> ali pa mu naročite, naj rekurzivno nalaga datoteke iz imenikov, "
"kot sledi:"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2162
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"Kate\",\n"
"  \"files\": [\n"
"    {\n"
"      \"directory\": \"kate\",\n"
"      \"filters\": [\n"
"        \"*.cpp\",\n"
"        \"*.h\",\n"
"        \"*.ui\",\n"
"        \"CMakeLists.txt\",\n"
"        \"Find*.cmake\"\n"
"      ],\n"
"      \"recursive\": 1,\n"
"      \"hidden\": 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  ],\n"
"  \"exclude_patterns\" : [\n"
"    \"^build/.*\"\n"
"  ]\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"Kate\",\n"
"  \"files\": [\n"
"    {\n"
"      \"directory\": \"kate\",\n"
"      \"filters\": [\n"
"        \"*.cpp\",\n"
"        \"*.h\",\n"
"        \"*.ui\",\n"
"        \"CMakeLists.txt\",\n"
"        \"Find*.cmake\"\n"
"      ],\n"
"      \"recursive\": 1,\n"
"      \"hidden\": 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  ],\n"
"  \"exclude_patterns\" : [\n"
"    \"^build/.*\"\n"
"  ]\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2164
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here, subfolders and filters define what’s part of the project. You can also "
"mix version control and files based on filters. Hidden files will not be "
"retrieved if the option <code>\"hidden\"</code> is 0. <code>"
"\"exclude_patterns\"</code> is a list of regex patterns that can be used to "
"exclude folders and files from the project tree. In this example, All files "
"and folders in a directory <filename>build</filename> from the root will be "
"excluded."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj podmape in filtri določajo, kaj je del projekta. Prav tako lahko "
"kombinirate nadzor različic in datoteke na podlagi filtrov. Skrite datoteke "
"ne bodo pridobljene, če je možnost <code>\"hidden\"</code> 0. <code>"
"\"exclude_patterns\"</code> je seznam vzorcev regularnih izrazov, ki jih je "
"mogoče uporabiti za izključitev map in datotek iz projekta drevo. V tem "
"primeru bodo vse datoteke in mape v imeniku <filename>build</filename> iz "
"korena izključene."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2173
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to add support for the building, you can write a <filename>."
"kateproject</filename> like this:"
msgstr ""
"Če želite dodati podporo za zgradbo, lahko <filename>.kateproject</filename> "
"napišete takole:"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2176
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"Kate\",\n"
"  \"files\": [\n"
"    {\n"
"      \"git\": 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  ],\n"
"  \"build\": {\n"
"    \"directory\": \"build\",\n"
"    \"build\": \"make all\",\n"
"    \"clean\": \"make clean\",\n"
"    \"install\": \"make install\",\n"
"    \"targets\": [\n"
"      {\n"
"        \"name\": \"all\",\n"
"        \"build_cmd\": \"ninja\"\n"
"        \"run_cmd\": \"./bin/kate\"\n"
"      },\n"
"      {\n"
"        \"name\": \"kate\",\n"
"        \"build_cmd\": \"ninja kate-bin\"\n"
"      }\n"
"    ]\n"
"  }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"  \"name\": \"Kate\",\n"
"  \"files\": [\n"
"    {\n"
"      \"git\": 1\n"
"    }\n"
"  ],\n"
"  \"build\": {\n"
"    \"directory\": \"build\",\n"
"    \"build\": \"make all\",\n"
"    \"clean\": \"make clean\",\n"
"    \"install\": \"make install\",\n"
"    \"targets\": [\n"
"      {\n"
"        \"name\": \"all\",\n"
"        \"build_cmd\": \"ninja\"\n"
"        \"run_cmd\": \"./bin/kate\"\n"
"      },\n"
"      {\n"
"        \"name\": \"kate\",\n"
"        \"build_cmd\": \"ninja kate-bin\"\n"
"      }\n"
"    ]\n"
"  }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2178
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The targets specified above will then appear in the <link linkend=\"kate-"
"application-plugin-build\">Build Plugin </link> under <emphasis role=\"bold"
"\"> \"Project Plugin Targets\"</emphasis>. If the <code>\"targets\"</code> "
"array is specified then <code>\"build\"</code>, <code>\"clean\"</code> and "
"<code>\"install\"</code> are ignored. Each element in the array specifies a "
"target. <code>\"name\"</code> is the name of the target, <code>\"build_cmd"
"\"</code> will be used to build the target, <code>\"run_cmd\"</code> will be "
"used to run the target. Most important of all is <code>\"directory\"</code>, "
"this is where the commands will be executed."
msgstr ""
"Zgoraj navedeni cilji bodo nato prikazani v <link linkend=\"kate-application-"
"plugin-build\">vtičniku za gradnjo </link> pod <emphasis role=\"bold\"> "
"»Cilji vtičnika projekta«</emphasis>. Če je podano polje <code>\"targets\"</"
"code>, so <code>\"build\"</code>, <code>\"clean\"</code> in <code>\"install"
"\"</code> prezrti . Vsak element v matriki določa cilj. <code>\"name\"</"
"code> je ime cilja, <code>\"build_cmd\"</code> bo uporabljen za izdelavo "
"cilja, <code>\"run_cmd\"</code> bo uporabljen za zagon tarča. Najpomembnejši "
"od vsega je <code>\"imenik\"</code>, kjer se bodo izvajali ukazi."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In case you have a <filename>.kateproject</filename> file tracked by a "
"control version system, but you need to tweak the configuration for a "
"particular workspace, you can save those changes to a separated file named "
"<filename>.kateproject.local</filename>. The content of this file will take "
"precedence over <filename>.kateproject</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Če imate datoteko <filename>.kateproject</filename>, ki ji sledi sistem "
"nadzorne različice, vendar morate spremeniti konfiguracijo za določen "
"delovni prostor, lahko te spremembe shranite v ločeno datoteko z imenom "
"<filename>.kateproject. lokalni</filename>. Vsebina te datoteke bo imela "
"prednost pred <filename>.kateproject</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2199
#, no-c-format
msgid "<title>Current Project</title>"
msgstr "<title>Trenutni projekt</title>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Using <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>1</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Projects</guimenu><guimenuitem>Go To</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice> you can open the <guilabel>Current Project</"
"guilabel> view at the bottom of the editor window with four tabs:"
msgstr ""
"Uporaba <menuchoice><shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>1</"
"keycap></keycombo></shortcut> <guimenu>Projekti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pojdi "
"na</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> lahko odprete pogled <guilabel>Trenutni "
"projekt</guilabel> na dnu okna urejevalnika s štirimi zavihki:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:2206
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Current Project</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Trenutni projekt</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: guimenu
#: plugins.docbook:2216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal Panel"
msgstr "Terminalna plošča"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-konsole\">Terminal emulator</link> "
"starting in the root folder of the project."
msgstr ""
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-konsole\">Emulator terminala</link>, "
"ki se začne v korenski mapi projekta."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: plugins.docbook:2226
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code Index"
msgstr "Indeks kod"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2229
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering characters into the search bar will start the search and display "
"matching names of functions, classes, symbols &etc; together with kind, "
"filename and line number."
msgstr ""
"Če v iskalno vrstico vnesete znake, se bo začelo iskanje in prikazala bodo "
"imena funkcij, razredov, simbolov itd. skupaj z vrsto, imenom datoteke in "
"številko vrstice."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: plugins.docbook:2237
#, no-c-format
msgid "Code Analysis"
msgstr "Analiza kode"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guilabel>Start Analysis</guilabel> to run a static code analysis for "
"the C and C++ using <command>cppcheck</command> and to generate a report "
"showing filename, line number, severity (style, warning &etc;) and the issue "
"found."
msgstr ""
"Kliknite <guilabel>Začni analizo</guilabel>, da zaženete analizo statične "
"kode za C in C++ z <command>cppcheck</command> in ustvarite poročilo, ki "
"prikazuje ime datoteke, številko vrstice, resnost (slog, opozorilo &etc;) in "
"težava je bila najdena."

#. Tag: guimenu
#: plugins.docbook:2249
#, no-c-format
msgid "Notes"
msgstr "Opombe"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Text entered in this tab will be saved in the file <filename>.kateproject."
"notes</filename>."
msgstr ""
"Besedilo, vneseno v ta zavihek, bo shranjeno v datoteko <filename>."
"kateproject.notes</filename>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2262
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Projects Menu"
msgstr "Meni Projekti"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2264
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <guimenu>Projects</guimenu> menu allows you to switch between currently "
"open projects. It is displayed by the Project plugin."
msgstr ""
"Meni <guimenu>Projekti</guimenu> omogoča preklapljanje med trenutno odprtimi "
"projekti. Prikaže ga vtičnik Projekt."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2270
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Left;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Projects</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Back</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Left;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Projekti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Nazaj</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2278
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to the previous project."
msgstr "Preklopite na prejšnji projekt."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Right;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Projects</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Forward</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Right;</keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Projekti</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Naprej</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2291
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to the next project."
msgstr "Preklopite na naslednji projekt."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2296
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Projects</guimenu><guimenuitem>Go To</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;<keycap>1</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Projekti</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pojdi na</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Open the <guilabel>Current Project</guilabel> view at the bottom of the "
"editor window."
msgstr ""
"Odprite pogled <guilabel>Trenutni projekt</guilabel> na dnu okna "
"urejevalnika."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2320
#, no-c-format
msgid "LSP Client Plugin"
msgstr "Odjemalski vtičnik LSP"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2322
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The LSP Client plugin provides many language features such as code "
"completion, code navigation or finding references based on the <ulink url="
"\"https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/\">Language Server "
"Protocol</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik LSP Client ponuja številne jezikovne funkcije, kot so dokončanje "
"kode, krmarjenje po kodi ali iskanje referenc na podlagi <ulink url="
"\"https://microsoft.github.io/language-server-protocol/\">protokola "
"jezikovnega strežnika</ulink >."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2325
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once you have enabled the LSP Client in the plugin page, a new page called "
"LSP Client will appear in your &kate; configuration dialog."
msgstr ""
"Ko omogočite odjemalca LSP na strani vtičnika, se bo v vašem &kate; pojavila "
"nova stran z imenom Odjemalec LSP. konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2332
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If appropriate, a corresponding LSP command is also mentioned in the "
"explanation below, the documentation of which may then provide additional "
"background and interpretation, though it may vary depending on the actual "
"language. The phrase 'current symbol' refers to the symbol corresponding to "
"the current cursor position, as so determined by the language and server "
"implementation."
msgstr ""
"Če je primerno, je v spodnji razlagi omenjen tudi ustrezen ukaz LSP, "
"katerega dokumentacija lahko nudi dodatno ozadje in razlago, čeprav se lahko "
"razlikuje glede na dejanski jezik. Besedna zveza 'trenutni simbol' se nanaša "
"na simbol, ki ustreza trenutnemu položaju kazalca, kot je določeno z jezikom "
"in implementacijo strežnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2344
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Definition</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na definicijo</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2349
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/definition] Go to current symbol definition."
msgstr "[besedilniDokument/definicija] Pojdi na trenutno definicijo simbola."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2354
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Declaration</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na deklaracijo</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2359
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/declaration] Go to current symbol declaration."
msgstr "[besedilniDokument/deklaracija] Pojdi na trenutno deklaracijo simbola."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2364
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Go to Type Definition</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pojdi na definicijo tipa</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2369
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/typeDefinition] Go to current symbol type definition."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/definicijaVrste] Pojdi na trenutno definicijo tipa "
"simbola."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2374
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find References</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Iskanje referenc</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2379
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/references] Find references to current symbol."
msgstr "[besedilniDokument/sklici] Poišči sklice na trenutni simbol."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2384
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Find Implementations</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Poišči implementacije</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2389
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/implementation] Find implementations of current symbol."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/implementacija] Poiščite implementacije trenutnega "
"simbola."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2394
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Highlight</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Označi</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2399
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[textDocument/documentHighlight] Highlight current symbol references in "
"current document."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/označiDokument] Označi trenutne reference simbolov v "
"trenutnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2404
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Hover</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Lebdenje</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2409
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/hover] Hover info for current symbol."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/lebdenje] Informacije o lebdenju trenutnega simbola."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2414
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Format</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Oblika</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2419
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[textDocument/formatting] [textDocument/rangeFormatting] Format the current "
"document or current selection."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/oblikovanje] [besedilniDokument/oblikovanjeObsega] "
"Oblikujte trenutni dokument ali trenutni izbor."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2425
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Rename</guisubmenu>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preimenuj</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2430
#, no-c-format
msgid "[textDocument/rename] Rename current symbol."
msgstr "[besedilniDokument/preimenuj] Preimenuj trenutni simbol."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2435
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Quick Fix</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Hitri popravek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2440
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[textDocument/codeAction, workspace/executeCommand] Computes and applies a "
"quick fix for a diagnostic on current position (or line)."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/codeAction, delovni prostor/izvedi ukaz] Izračuna in "
"uporabi hiter popravek za diagnostiko na trenutnem položaju (ali vrstici)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show selected completion "
"documentation</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pokaži izbrano dokumentacijo o "
"dokončanju</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2451
#, no-c-format
msgid "Show documentation for a selected item in the completion list."
msgstr "Pokažite dokumentacijo za izbrani element na seznamu dokončanja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2456
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Enable signature help with auto "
"completion</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Omogoči pomoč pri podpisu s "
"samodejnim dokončanjem</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2461
#, no-c-format
msgid "Also show signature help in the completion list."
msgstr "Na seznamu za dokončanje prikaži tudi pomoč za podpis."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2466
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Include declaration in references</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Vključi izjavo v reference</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Request to include a symbol's declaration when requesting references."
msgstr "Zahtevajte vključitev deklaracije simbola, ko zahtevate reference."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2476
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Add parentheses upon function "
"completion</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Dodaj oklepaje ob zaključku "
"funkcije</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2481
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically add a pair of parentheses after completion of a function."
msgstr "Samodejno dodajte par oklepajev po zaključku funkcije."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2486
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show hover information</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži informacije o lebdenju</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2491
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Show hover information upon (mouse cursor) hover. Regardless of this "
"setting, the request can always be manually initiated."
msgstr ""
"Pokaži informacije o lebdenju ob lebdenju (miškine kazalke). Ne glede na to "
"nastavitev je zahtevo vedno mogoče sprožiti ročno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2498
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Format on typing</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Oblika ob tipkanju</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[document/onTypeFormatting] Format parts of document when typing certain "
"trigger characters. For example, this might apply indentation upon newline, "
"or as otherwise determined by LSP Server. Note that editor indentation "
"scripts might be trying to do the same (depending on the mode) and so it may "
"not be advisable to have both enabled at the same time."
msgstr ""
"[dokument/onTypeFormatting] Oblikujte dele dokumenta pri vnašanju določenih "
"sprožilnih znakov. To lahko na primer uporabi zamik ob novi vrstici ali "
"kakor drugače določi strežnik LSP. Upoštevajte, da skripti za zamik "
"urejevalnika morda poskušajo storiti enako (odvisno od načina), zato morda "
"ni priporočljivo, da sta oba omogočena hkrati."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Incremental document "
"synchronization</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Inkrementalna sinhronizacija "
"dokumentov</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2517
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Send partial document edits to update the server rather than whole document "
"text (if supported)."
msgstr ""
"Pošlji delna urejanja dokumenta za posodobitev strežnika namesto celotnega "
"besedila dokumenta (če je podprto)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Highlight goto location</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Označi pojdi na lokacijo</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2527
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Provide a transient visual cue after performing a goto to a location (of "
"definition, declaration, etc)."
msgstr ""
"Zagotovite prehodno vizualno iztočnico po izvedbi prehoda na lokacijo "
"(definicije, deklaracije itd.)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2532
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show diagnostics notifications</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pokaži diagnostična obvestila</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[textDocument/publishDiagnostics] Process and show diagnostics notifications "
"sent by server."
msgstr ""
"[besedilniDokument/objaviDiagnostiko] Obdelava in prikaz diagnostičnih "
"obvestil, ki jih pošlje strežnik."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2542
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show diagnostics highlights</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži poudarke diagnostike</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2547
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add text highlights for ranges indicated in diagnostics."
msgstr "Dodajte poudarke besedila za obsege, navedene v diagnostiki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2552
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Show diagnostics marks</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Prikaži diagnostične oznake</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2557
#, no-c-format
msgid "Add document marks for lines indicated in diagnostics."
msgstr "Dodajte oznake dokumenta za vrstice, navedene v diagnostiki."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2562
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Switch to diagnostic tab</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Preklopi na diagnostični "
"zavihek</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2567
#, no-c-format
msgid "Switch to the diagnostic tab in the plugin toolview."
msgstr "Preklopite na diagnostični zavihek v pogledu orodja vtičnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2572
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Close all non-diagnostics tabs</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Zapri vse zavihke brez "
"diagnostike</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2577
#, no-c-format
msgid "Close all non-diagnostics (&eg; references) tabs in plugin toolview."
msgstr ""
"Zaprite vse zavihke brez diagnostike (&eg; reference) v orodnem pogledu "
"vtičnika."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2582
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Restart LSP Server</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Ponovni zagon strežnika LSP</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2587
#, no-c-format
msgid "Restart current document's LSP Server."
msgstr "Znova zaženite strežnik LSP trenutnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:2592
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>LSP Client</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Restart all LSP Servers</"
"guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Odjemalec LSP</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Ponovni zagon vseh strežnikov "
"LSP</guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2597
#, no-c-format
msgid "Stop all LSP Servers which will then be (re)started as needed."
msgstr ""
"Zaustavite vse strežnike LSP, ki bodo nato po potrebi (ponovno) zagnani."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2606
#, no-c-format
msgid "Goto Symbol support"
msgstr "Podpora Goto Symbol"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2607
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"LSP Client can help you jump to any symbol in your project or current file. "
"To jump to any symbol in the file, use the toolview \"LSP Client Symbol "
"Outline\" on the right border of kate. This toolview lists all symbols found "
"by the server in current document."
msgstr ""
"Odjemalec LSP vam lahko pomaga skočiti na kateri koli simbol v vašem "
"projektu ali trenutni datoteki. Če želite skočiti na kateri koli simbol v "
"datoteki, uporabite pogled orodja \"Oris simbola odjemalca LSP\" na desni "
"strani kate. Ta pogled orodij navaja vse simbole, ki jih je strežnik našel v "
"trenutnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configuring LSP Client Symbol Outline"
msgstr "Konfiguriranje orisa simbola odjemalca LSP"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"By default the symbols are sorted by their occurrence in the document but "
"you can change the sort to be alphabetical. To do so, right click in the "
"toolview and check \"Sort Alphabetically\"."
msgstr ""
"Simboli so privzeto razvrščeni glede na njihovo pojavljanje v dokumentu, "
"vendar lahko razvrščanje spremenite v abecedno. To storite tako, da z desno "
"miškino tipko kliknete pogled orodij in obkljukate »Razvrsti po abecedi«."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2624
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The toolview shows the symbols in tree mode by default, however you can "
"change it to a list using the context menu."
msgstr ""
"Orodni pogled privzeto prikazuje simbole v drevesnem načinu, vendar ga lahko "
"spremenite v seznam s kontekstnim menijem."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2631
#, no-c-format
msgid "Global Goto symbol support"
msgstr "Podpora za globalni simbol Goto"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2632
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To jump to any symbol in your project, you can open the goto symbol dialog "
"using <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>p</keycap></keycombo>. "
"The dialog is empty when it opens but as soon as you type something the "
"dialog will start showing you matching symbols. The quality of matches as "
"well as filtering capabilities depend upon the server that you use. For "
"example, clangd supports fuzzy filtering but some other server may not."
msgstr ""
"Če želite skočiti na kateri koli simbol v vašem projektu, lahko odprete "
"pogovorno okno za prehod na simbol s <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;"
"<keycap>p</keycap></keycombo>. Pogovorno okno je prazno, ko se odpre, vendar "
"takoj, ko nekaj vnesete, vam bo pogovorno okno začelo prikazovati ujemajoče "
"se simbole. Kakovost ujemanja in zmožnosti filtriranja so odvisne od "
"strežnika, ki ga uporabljate. Clangd na primer podpira mehko filtriranje, "
"nekateri drugi strežniki pa morda ne."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2644
#, no-c-format
msgid "Other Features"
msgstr "Druge funkcije"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clangd switch source header command is supported. To switch source header in "
"a C or C++ project either use the \"Switch Source Header\" option from the "
"context menu or the shortcut <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F12</"
"keycap></keycombo>."
msgstr ""
"Podprt je ukaz Clangd preklopite izvorno glavo. Če želite zamenjati izvorno "
"glavo v projektu C ali C++, uporabite možnost »Preklopite Izvorno Glavo« v "
"kontekstnem meniju ali bližnjico <keycombo action=\"simul\"><keycap>F12</"
"keycap></keycombo>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can jump to a symbol quickly by putting your mouse over the symbol and "
"then pressing <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> + left mouse "
"button."
msgstr ""
"Na simbol lahko hitro skočite tako, da postavite miško nad simbol in nato "
"pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;</keycombo> + levi gumb miške."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2661
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin's configuration page mostly allows for persistent configuration "
"of some of the above menu items. However, there is one additional entry to "
"specify the Server Configuration file. This is a &JSON; file that can be "
"used to specify the LSP server to start (and then to communicate with over "
"stdin/stdout). For convenience, some default configuration is included, "
"which can be inspected in the plugin's configuration page. To aid in the "
"explanation below, an excerpt of that configuration is given here:"
msgstr ""
"Konfiguracijska stran vtičnika večinoma omogoča stalno konfiguracijo "
"nekaterih zgornjih elementov menija. Vendar obstaja en dodaten vnos za "
"podajanje datoteke s konfiguracijo strežnika. To je &JSON; datoteko, ki jo "
"lahko uporabite za določitev strežnika LSP za zagon (in nato za komunikacijo "
"prek stdin/stdout). Za udobje je vključena nekaj privzetih konfiguracij, ki "
"jih lahko pregledate na konfiguracijski strani vtičnika. Za pomoč pri "
"spodnji razlagi je tukaj podan izsek te konfiguracije:"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2671
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \"servers\": {\n"
"        \"bibtex\": {\n"
"            \"use\": \"latex\",\n"
"            \"highlightingModeRegex\": \"^BibTeX$\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"c\": {\n"
"            \"command\": [\"clangd\", \"-log=error\", \"--background-index"
"\"],\n"
"            \"commandDebug\": [\"clangd\", \"-log=verbose\", \"--background-"
"index\"],\n"
"            \"url\": \"https://clang.llvm.org/extra/clangd/\",\n"
"            \"highlightingModeRegex\": \"^(C|ANSI C89|Objective-C)$\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"cpp\": {\n"
"            \"use\": \"c\",\n"
"            \"highlightingModeRegex\": \"^(C\\\\+\\\\+|ISO C\\\\+\\\\+|"
"Objective-C\\\\+\\\\+)$\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"d\": {\n"
"            \"command\": [\"dls\", \"--stdio\"],\n"
"            \"url\": \"https://github.com/d-language-server/dls\",\n"
"            \"highlightingModeRegex\": \"^D$\"\n"
"        },\n"
"        \"fortran\": {\n"
"            \"command\": [\"fortls\"],\n"
"            \"rootIndicationFileNames\": [\".fortls\"],\n"
