#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that each \"command\" may be an array or a string (in which case it is "
"split into an array). Also, a top-level \"global\" entry (next to \"server"
"\") is considered as well (see further below). The specified binary is "
"searched for in the usual way, e.g. using <literal>PATH</literal>. If it is "
"installed in some custom location, then the latter may have to be extended. "
"Or alternatively, a (sym)link or wrapper script may be used in a location "
"that is within the usual <literal>PATH</literal>. As illustrated above, one "
"may also specify a \"path\" that will be searched for after the standard "
"locations."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je vsak \"ukaz\" lahko matrika ali niz (v tem primeru je "
"razdeljen na matriko). Upoštevan je tudi \"globalni\" vnos na najvišji ravni "
"(poleg \"strežnika\") (glejte več spodaj). Navedeno dvojiško datoteko se "
"išče na običajen način, npr. z uporabo <literal>PATH</literal>. Če je "
"nameščen na določeni lokaciji po meri, bo slednjo morda treba razširiti. "
"Druga možnost je, da se (sim)povezava ali ovojni skript uporabi na mestu, ki "
"je znotraj običajne <literal>PATH</literal>. Kot je prikazano zgoraj, lahko "
"določite tudi \"pot\", ki bo iskana po standardnih lokacijah."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2684
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All of the entries in \"command\", \"root\" and \"path\" are subject to "
"variable expansion."
msgstr ""
"Vsi vnosi v \"ukaz\", \"koren\" in \"pot\" so predmet razširitve "
"spremenljivke."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2688
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The \"highlightingModeRegex\" is used to map the highlighting mode as used "
"by &kate; to the language id of the server. If no regular expression is "
"given, the language id itself is used. If a \"documentLanguageId\" entry is "
"set to false, then no language id is provided to the server when opening the "
"document. This may have better results for some servers that are more "
"precise in determining the document type than doing so based on a kate mode."
msgstr ""
"\"OznačevanjeNačinaRegex\" se uporablja za preslikavo načina označevanja, "
"kot ga uporablja &kate; na ID jezika strežnika. Če ni podanega regularnega "
"izraza, se uporabi sam ID jezika. Če je vnos »jezikDokumentaId« nastavljen "
"na false, potem strežniku pri odpiranju dokumenta ni posredovan ID jezika. "
"To ima morda boljše rezultate za nekatere strežnike, ki so bolj natančni pri "
"določanju vrste dokumenta, kot če to počnejo na podlagi načina kate."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2697
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"From the above example, the gist is presumably clear. In addition, each "
"server entry object may also have an \"initializationOptions\" entry, which "
"is passed along to the server as part of the 'initialize' method. If "
"present, a \"settings\" entry is passed to the server by means of the "
"'workspace/didChangeConfiguration' notification. Either of "
"\"completionTriggerCharacters\" or \"signatureTriggerCharacters\" may be "
"specified as a JSON object with string members \"exclude\" and/or \"include"
"\". These will be used to respectively exclude or add some characters to the "
"respective trigger set as provided by the server."
msgstr ""
"Iz zgornjega primera je bistvo menda jasno. Poleg tega ima lahko vsak objekt "
"vnosa strežnika tudi vnos \"inicialzacijskeOpcije\", ki se posreduje "
"strežniku kot del metode \"inicializiraj\". Če je prisoten, se vnos "
"»nastavitve« posreduje strežniku s pomočjo obvestila »delovni prostor/"
"jeSpremenjenaKonfiguracija«. Bodisi od »dokončaniSprožilniZnaki« ali "
"»značilniSprožilniZnaki« je mogoče podati kot objekt JSON s člani niza "
"»izključi« in/ali »vključi«. Ti bodo uporabljeni za ustrezno izključitev ali "
"dodajanje nekaterih znakov ustreznemu naboru sprožilcev, ki jih zagotavlja "
"strežnik."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Various stages of override/merge are applied;"
msgstr "Uporabljene so različne stopnje preglasitve/združevanja;"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2713
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"user configuration (loaded from file) overrides (internal) default "
"configuration"
msgstr ""
"uporabniška konfiguracija (naložena iz datoteke) preglasi (notranjo) "
"privzeto konfiguracijo"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2716
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"\"lspclient\" entry in <filename>.kateproject</filename> project "
"configuration overrides the above"
msgstr ""
"Vnos »lsp client« v konfiguraciji projekta <filename>.kate project</"
"filename> preglasi zgornje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"the resulting \"global\" entry is used to supplement (not override) any "
"server entry"
msgstr ""
"nastali \"globalni\" vnos se uporablja za dopolnitev (ne preglasitev) "
"katerega koli vnosa v strežnik"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2724
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"One server instance is used per (root, servertype) combination. If \"root\" "
"is specified as an absolute path, then it used as-is, otherwise it is "
"relative to the <quote>projectBase</quote> (as determined by the <link "
"linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-projects\">Project plugin</link>) if "
"applicable, or otherwise relative to the document's directory. If not "
"specified and \"rootIndicationFileNames\" is an array as filenames, then a "
"parent directory of current document containing such a file is selected. "
"Alternatively, if \"root\" is not specified and \"rootIndicationFilePatterns"
"\" is an array of file patterns, then a parent directory of the current "
"document matching the file pattern is selected. As a last fallback, the home "
"directory is selected as \"root\". For any document, the resulting \"root\" "
"then determines whether or not a separate instance is needed. If so, the "
"\"root\" is passed as rootUri/rootPath."
msgstr ""
"En primerek strežnika se uporablja na kombinacijo (koren, tip strežnika). Če "
"je \"root\" podana kot absolutna pot, potem je uporabljena takšna, kot je, "
"drugače je relativna glede na <quote>projektna osnova</quote> (kot določa "
"<link linkend=\"kate-application-plugin-projects\" >Projektni vtičnik</"
"link>), če je primerno, ali kako drugače glede na imenik dokumenta. Če ni "
"navedeno in je \"korenVzorciIndikacijskihDatotek\" matrika kot imena "
"datotek, je izbran nadrejeni imenik trenutnega dokumenta, ki vsebuje takšno "
"datoteko. Če »koren« ni podan in je »korenVzorciIndikacijskihDatotek« niz "
"vzorcev datotek, je izbran nadrejeni imenik trenutnega dokumenta, ki se "
"ujema z vzorcem datoteke. Kot zadnja rezerva je domači imenik izbran kot "
"\"koren\". Za vsak dokument nastali \"koren\" nato določi, ali je potreben "
"ločen primerek ali ne. Če je tako, se \"koren\" posreduje kot rootUri/"
"rootPath."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2738
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In general, it is recommended to leave root unspecified, as it is not that "
"important for a server (your mileage may vary though). Fewer server "
"instances are obviously more efficient, and they also have a 'wider' view "
"than the view of many separate instances."
msgstr ""
"Na splošno je priporočljivo, da koren pustite nedoločen, saj za strežnik ni "
"tako pomemben (vaša kilometrina se lahko razlikuje). Manj primerkov "
"strežnika je očitno učinkovitejših in imajo tudi 'širši' pogled kot pogled "
"številnih ločenih primerkov."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As mentioned above, several entries are subject to variable expansion. A "
"suitable application of that combined with \"wrapper script\" approaches "
"allows for customization to a great many circumstances. For example, "
"consider a python development scenario that consists of multiple projects (e."
"g. git repos), each with its own virtualenv setup. Using the default "
"configuration, the python language server will not be aware of the virtual "
"env. However, that can be remedied with the following approach. First, the "
"following fragment can be entered in LSPClient plugin's \"User Server "
"Settings\":"
msgstr ""
"Kot je navedeno zgoraj, je več vnosov predmet spremenljive razširitve. "
"Ustrezna uporaba tega v kombinaciji s pristopi \"ovijalnega skripta\" "
"omogoča prilagajanje številnim okoliščinam. Na primer, razmislite o "
"scenariju razvoja pythona, ki je sestavljen iz več projektov (npr. git "
"repos), od katerih ima vsak svojo lastno nastavitev virtualenv. Če "
"uporabljate privzeto konfiguracijo, jezikovni strežnik python ne bo poznal "
"virtualnega env. Vendar pa je to mogoče odpraviti z naslednjim pristopom. "
"Najprej lahko v \"Nastavitve uporabniškega strežnika\" vtičnika LSPClient "
"vnesete naslednji fragment:"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2755
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"        \"servers\":\n"
"        {\n"
"                \"python\":\n"
"                {\n"
"                        \"command\": [\"pylsp_in_env\", \"%{Project:"
"NativePath}\"],\n"
"                        \"root\": \".\"\n"
"                }\n"
"        }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"        \"servers\":\n"
"        {\n"
"                \"python\":\n"
"                {\n"
"                        \"command\": [\"pylsp_in_env\", \"%{Project:"
"NativePath}\"],\n"
"                        \"root\": \".\"\n"
"                }\n"
"        }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2756
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The root entry above is relative to the project directory and ensures that a "
"separate language server is started for each project, which is necessary in "
"this case as each has a distinct virtual environment."
msgstr ""
"Zgornji korenski vnos je povezan z imenikom projekta in zagotavlja, da se za "
"vsak projekt zažene ločen jezikovni strežnik, kar je v tem primeru potrebno, "
"saj ima vsak ločeno virtualno okolje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2761
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<filename>pylsp_in_env</filename> is a small \"wrapper script\" that should "
"be placed in <literal>PATH</literal> with the following (to-be-adjusted) "
"content:"
msgstr ""
"<filename>pylsp_in_env</filename> je majhen \"ovijni skript\", ki ga je "
"treba postaviti v <literal>PATH</literal> z naslednjo vsebino (ki jo je "
"treba prilagoditi):"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2765
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"#!/bin/bash\n"
"cd $1\n"
"# run the server (python-lsp-server) within the virtualenv\n"
"# (i.e. with virtualenv variables setup)\n"
"# so source the virtualenv\n"
"source XYZ\n"
"# server mileage or arguments may vary\n"
"exec myserver"
msgstr ""
"#!/bin/bash\n"
"cd $1\n"
"# run the server (python-lsp-server) within the virtualenv\n"
"# (i.e. with virtualenv variables setup)\n"
"# so source the virtualenv\n"
"source XYZ\n"
"# server mileage or arguments may vary\n"
"exec myserver"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2766
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is but one example of a more general pattern which may be handled a bit "
"more comfortably as outlined in the <link linkend=\"lspclient-exec"
"\">Execution environment</link> section below."
msgstr ""
"To je le en primer bolj splošnega vzorca, ki ga je mogoče nekoliko udobneje "
"obravnavati, kot je opisano v spodnjem razdelku <link linkend=\"lspclient-"
"exec\">Izvedbeno okolje</link>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2773
#, no-c-format
msgid "LSP Server Configuration"
msgstr "Konfiguracija strežnika LSP"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2775
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each particular LSP server has its own way of customization and may use "
"language/tool specific means for configuration, &eg; <filename>tox.ini</"
"filename> (a.o. for python), <filename>.clang-format</filename> for C++ "
"style format. Such configuration may then also be used by other (non-LSP) "
"tools (such as then <application>tox</application> or <application>clang-"
"format</application>). On top of that, some LSP servers also load "
"configuration from custom files (&eg; <filename>.ccls</filename>). "
"Furthermore, custom server configuration can also be passed through LSP "
"(protocol), see the aforementioned \"initializationOptions\" and \"settings"
"\" entries in server configuration."
msgstr ""
"Vsak posamezen strežnik LSP ima svoj način prilagajanja in lahko za "
"konfiguracijo uporablja specifična sredstva za jezik/orodje, &eg; "
"<filename>tox.ini</filename> (a.o. za python), <filename>.clang-format</"
"filename> za obliko v slogu C++. Tako konfiguracijo lahko nato uporabljajo "
"tudi druga orodja (ki niso LSP) (kot je <application>tox</application> ali "
"<application>clang-format</application>). Poleg tega nekateri strežniki LSP "
"tudi naložijo konfiguracijo iz datotek po meri (&eg; <filename>.ccls</"
"filename>). Poleg tega je mogoče konfiguracijo strežnika po meri posredovati "
"tudi prek LSP (protokol), glejte zgoraj omenjene vnose "
"»možnostiInicializacije« in »nastavitve« v konfiguraciji strežnika."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2790
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Since various level of override/merge are applied, the following example of "
"user specified client configuration tweaks some python-language-server "
"configuration."
msgstr ""
"Ker so uporabljene različne ravni preglasitve/združevanja, naslednji primer "
"uporabniško podane konfiguracije odjemalca prilagodi nekaj konfiguracije "
"strežnika v jeziku python."

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2796
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \"servers\": {\n"
"        \"python\": {\n"
"            \"settings\": {\n"
"                \"pyls\": {\n"
"                    \"plugins\": {\n"
"                        \"pylint\": {\n"
"                            \"enable\": true\n"
"                        }\n"
"                    }\n"
"                }\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    \"servers\": {\n"
"        \"python\": {\n"
"            \"settings\": {\n"
"                \"pyls\": {\n"
"                    \"plugins\": {\n"
"                        \"pylint\": {\n"
"                            \"enable\": true\n"
"                        }\n"
"                    }\n"
"                }\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2798
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Unfortunately, LSP server configuration/customization is often not so well "
"documented, in ways that only examining the source code shows configuration "
"approaches and the set of available configuration options. In particular, "
"the above example's server supports many more options in \"settings\". See "
"<ulink url=\"https://github.com/neoclide/coc.nvim/wiki/Language-servers\"> "
"another LSP client's documentation</ulink> for various other language server "
"examples and corresponding settings, which can easily and readily be "
"transformed to the &JSON; configuration that is used here and outlined above."
msgstr ""
"Na žalost konfiguracija/prilagajanje strežnika LSP pogosto ni tako dobro "
"dokumentirano, tako da samo pregledovanje izvorne kode pokaže "
"konfiguracijske pristope in nabor razpoložljivih konfiguracijskih možnosti. "
"Zlasti strežnik zgornjega primera podpira veliko več možnosti v \"nastavitvah"
"\". Oglejte si <ulink url=\"https://github.com/neoclide/coc.nvim/wiki/"
"Language-servers\"> dokumentacijo drugega odjemalca LSP</ulink> za različne "
"primere drugih jezikovnih strežnikov in ustrezne nastavitve, ki jih lahko "
"preprosto in preprosto preoblikovati v &JSON; konfiguracijo, ki se uporablja "
"tukaj in je opisana zgoraj."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2812
#, no-c-format
msgid "LSP Server Format On Save"
msgstr "Oblika strežnika LSP ob shranjevanju"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2814
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can enable \"format on save\" from LSP settings in configure dialog."
msgstr ""
"V nastavitvah LSP v konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu lahko omogočite "
"\"format ob shranjevanju\"."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2821
#, no-c-format
msgid "LSP Server Diagnostic Suppression"
msgstr "Zatiranje diagnostike strežnika LSP"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2823
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It may happen that diagnostics are reported which are not quite useful. This "
"can be quite cumbersome, especially if there are many (often of the same "
"kind). In some cases, this may be tweaked by language (server) specific "
"means. For example, the <ulink url=\"https://clangd.llvm.org/config.html"
"\">clangd configuration mechanism</ulink> allows tweaking of some "
"diagnostics aspects. In general, however, it may not always be evident how "
"to do so, or it may not even be possible at all in desired ways due to "
"server limitations or bug."
msgstr ""
"Lahko se zgodi, da se poroča o diagnostiki, ki ni povsem uporabna. To je "
"lahko precej okorno, še posebej, če jih je veliko (pogosto iste vrste). V "
"nekaterih primerih je to mogoče prilagoditi s posebnimi sredstvi za jezik "
"(strežnik). Na primer, <ulink url=\"https://clangd.llvm.org/config.html"
"\">konfiguracijski mehanizem clangd</ulink> omogoča spreminjanje nekaterih "
"diagnostičnih vidikov. Na splošno pa morda ni vedno jasno, kako to storiti, "
"ali pa morda sploh ne bo mogoče na želene načine zaradi omejitev strežnika "
"ali napake."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2833
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As such, the plugin supports diagnostics suppression similar to e.g. "
"valgrind suppressions. The most fine-grained configuration can be supplied "
"in a \"suppressions\" key in the (merged) &JSON; configuration."
msgstr ""
"Kot tak vtičnik podpira zatiranje diagnostike, podobno kot npr. zatiranje "
"valgrinda. Najbolj natančno konfiguracijo je mogoče zagotoviti v ključu "
"\"zatiranja\" v (združenem) &JSON; konfiguracijo."

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2839
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    \"servers\": {\n"
"        \"c\": {\n"
"            \"suppressions\": {\n"
"                \"rulename\": [\"filename\", \"foo\"],\n"
"                \"clang_pointer\": [\"\", \"clang-tidy\", \"clear_pointer"
"\"],\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"     \"strežniki\": {\n"
"         \"c\": {\n"
"             \"zatiranja\": {\n"
"                 \"ime pravila\": [\"ime datoteke\", \"foo\"],\n"
"                 \"clang_pointer\": [\"\", \"clang-tidy\", \"clear_pointer"
"\"],\n"
"             }\n"
"         }\n"
"     }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2841
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Each (valid) rule has an arbitrary name and is defined by an array of length "
"2 or 3 which provides a regex to match against the (full) filename, a regex "
"to match against the diagnostic (text) and an optional regex matched against "
"the (source code range of) text to which the diagnostic applies."
msgstr ""
"Vsako (veljavno) pravilo ima poljubno ime in je definirano z nizom dolžine 2 "
"ali 3, ki zagotavlja regularni izraz za ujemanje s (polnim) imenom datoteke, "
"regularni izraz za ujemanje z diagnostiko (besedilo) in izbirni regularni "
"izraz za ujemanje z (obseg izvorne kode) besedilo, na katerega se nanaša "
"diagnostika."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2848
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In addition to the above fine-grained configuration, the context menu in the "
"diagnostics tab also supports add/remove of suppressions that match a "
"particular diagnostic (text) exactly, either globally (any file) or locally "
"(the specific file in question). These suppression are stored in and loaded "
"from session config."
msgstr ""
"Poleg zgornje natančne konfiguracije kontekstni meni na zavihku diagnostike "
"podpira tudi dodajanje/odstranjevanje izključitev, ki se natančno ujemajo z "
"določeno diagnostiko (besedilo), bodisi globalno (katera koli datoteka) ali "
"lokalno (določena zadevna datoteka). Ta zatiranja so shranjena in naložena "
"iz konfiguracije seje."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:2858
#, no-c-format
msgid "LSP Server Troubleshooting"
msgstr "Odpravljanje težav s strežnikom LSP"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2860
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is one thing to describe how to configure a (custom) LSP server for any "
"particular language, it is another to end up with the server running "
"smoothly. Usually, the latter is fortunately the case. Sometimes, however, "
"problems may arise due to either some \"silly\" misconfiguration or a more "
"fundamental problem with the server itself. The latter might typically "
"manifest itself as a couple of attempts at starting the server, as so "
"reported in &kate; Output tab. The latter, however, is only meant to convey "
"high-level messages or progress rather than to provide detailed diagnostics, "
"and even less so for what is in fact another process (the LSP server)."
msgstr ""
"Eno je opisati, kako konfigurirati (po meri) strežnik LSP za kateri koli "
"določen jezik, drugo pa je, da na koncu strežnik deluje gladko. Običajno je "
"na srečo slednje. Včasih pa lahko nastanejo težave bodisi zaradi kakšne "
"\"neumne\" napačne konfiguracije ali bolj temeljne težave s samim "
"strežnikom. Slednje se običajno lahko kaže kot nekaj poskusov zagona "
"strežnika, kot je navedeno v &kate; Izhodni zavihek. Slednje pa je namenjeno "
"le posredovanju sporočil na visoki ravni ali napredku, ne pa zagotavljanju "
"podrobne diagnostike, še manj pa temu, kar je v resnici drug proces "
"(strežnik LSP)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2872
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The usual way to diagnose this is to add some flag(s) to the startup command "
"(of the language server) that enables (additional) logging (to some file or "
"standard error), in as far as it does not do so by default. If &kate; is "
"then started on the command line, then one might be able to obtain more "
"(in)sight in what might be going wrong."
msgstr ""
"Običajni način za diagnosticiranje tega je dodajanje zastavic zagonskemu "
"ukazu (jezikovnega strežnika), ki omogoča (dodatno) beleženje (v neko "
"datoteko ali standardno napako), v kolikor tega ne počne privzeto . Če "
"&kate; se nato zažene v ukazni vrstici, potem bi morda lahko dobili več "
"(v)pogleda v to, kaj bi lahko šlo narobe."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2880
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It may also be informative to examine the protocol exchange between &kate;'s "
"LSP client and the LSP server. Again, the latter usually has ways to trace "
"that. The LSP client also provides additional debug tracing (to stderr) when "
"&kate; is invoked with the following <literal>LSPCLIENT_DEBUG=1</literal> "
"suitably <literal>export</literal>'ed."
msgstr ""
"Prav tako bi bilo koristno preučiti izmenjavo protokolov med odjemalcem LSP "
"&kate; in strežnikom LSP. Spet ima slednji običajno načine, kako to "
"izslediti. Odjemalec LSP nudi tudi dodatno sledenje odpravljanju napak (v "
"stderr), ko se &kate; prikliče z naslednjim <literal>LSPCLIENT_DEBUG=1</"
"literal>, kar je ustrezno za <literal>izvoz</literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2894
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The python virtualenv example above is but one example of an \"execution "
"environment\" that operates in a distinct and separate way from the usual "
"host environment. This could be achieved by different variable settings (e."
"g. virtualenv), or a (s)chroot setup (switching to another dir as new root), "
"a container (e.g. podman, docker), or an ssh session to another host. In "
"each case, the \"other environment\" is defined by an \"execution prefix\". "
"That is, some program can be invoked/run in the other environment by means "
"of a \"prefix\" (a program and arguments) appended with the intended "
"invocation. For example, <literal>podman exec -i containername</literal> or "
"<literal>ssh user@host</literal>."
msgstr ""
"Zgornji primer pythonov virtualenv je le en primer \"izvajalnega okolja\", "
"ki deluje na drugačen in ločen način od običajnega gostiteljskega okolja. To "
"je mogoče doseči z različnimi nastavitvami spremenljivk (npr. virtualenv) "
"ali nastavitvijo (s)chroot (preklop na drug imenik kot nov root), vsebnikom "
"(npr. podman, docker) ali sejo ssh na drugega gostitelja. V vsakem primeru "
"je \"drugo okolje\" definirano z \"predpono izvajanja\". To pomeni, da je "
"mogoče nek program zagnati/izvajati v drugem okolju s pomočjo \"predpone"
"\" (program in argumenti), ki je dodana predvidenemu klicu. Na primer, "
"<literal>podman exec -i containername</literal> ali <literal>ssh user@host</"
"literal>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2907
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In particular, as in the previous virtualenv example, one may choose/need to "
"run an LSP server is such a separate environment (e.g. a container with all "
"dependencies needed by some project). The \"manual\" approach outlined above "
"has as disadvantage that it replaces the standard LSP command-line, which "
"then has to specified and duplicated again in the wrapper script. Also, in "
"some of the other examples mentioned above the \"path namespace\" of host "
"(as viewed by the editor) may be different from that of the environment. To "
"address these matters in a more systematic way (than a \"custom\" approach), "
"some additional configuration can be specified."
msgstr ""
"Še posebej, kot v prejšnjem primeru virtualenv, se lahko odločimo/"
"potrebujemo za zagon strežnika LSP kot ločenega okolja (npr. vsebnika z "
"vsemi odvisnostmi, ki jih potrebuje nek projekt). Zgoraj opisani \"ročni\" "
"pristop ima slabost, da nadomešča standardno ukazno vrstico LSP, ki jo je "
"nato treba ponovno določiti in podvojiti v ovojnem skriptu. Tudi v nekaterih "
"drugih zgoraj omenjenih primerih se lahko \"imenski prostor poti\" "
"gostitelja (kot ga vidi urejevalnik) razlikuje od imen okolja. Za bolj "
"sistematično obravnavo teh zadev (kot s \"pristopom po meri\") je mogoče "
"določiti nekaj dodatnih konfiguracij."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2919
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For example, the following can be specified in a <literal>.kateproject</"
"literal> configuration. Obviously, the \"fake\" comments should not be "
"included."
msgstr ""
"Na primer, naslednje je mogoče določiti v konfiguraciji <literal>."
"kateproject</literal>. Seveda \"lažnih\" komentarjev ne smete vključiti."

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:2924
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    // this may also be an array of objects\n"
"    \"exec\": {\n"
"        \"hostname\": \"foobar\"\n"
"        // the command could also be an array of string\n"
"        \"prefix\": \"podman exec -i foobarcontainer\",\n"
"        \"mapRemoteRoot\": true,\n"
"        \"pathMappings\": [\n"
"            // either of the following forms are possible\n"
"            // a more automagic alternative exists as well, see later/below\n"
"            [ \"/dir/on/host\", \"/mounted/in/container\" ]\n"
"            { \"localRoot\": \"/local/dir\", \"remoteRoot\": \"/remote/dir"
"\" }\n"
"        ]\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"lspclient\": {\n"
"        \"servers\": {\n"
"            \"python\": {\n"
"                // this will match/join with the above object\n"
"                \"exec\": { \"hostname\": \"foobar\" },\n"
"                // confine this server to this project root,\n"
"                // so it is not used for other projects that may be opened\n"
"                // (other servers may already employ specific roots, but "
"python generally not)\n"
"                \"root\": \".\"\n"
"            },\n"
"            \"c\": {\n"
"                // as above\n"
"                \"exec\": { \"hostname\": \"foobar\" },\n"
"                \"root\": \".\"\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    // this may also be an array of objects\n"
"    \"exec\": {\n"
"        \"hostname\": \"foobar\"\n"
"        // the command could also be an array of string\n"
"        \"prefix\": \"podman exec -i foobarcontainer\",\n"
"        \"mapRemoteRoot\": true,\n"
"        \"pathMappings\": [\n"
"            // either of the following forms are possible\n"
"            // a more automagic alternative exists as well, see later/below\n"
"            [ \"/dir/on/host\", \"/mounted/in/container\" ]\n"
"            { \"localRoot\": \"/local/dir\", \"remoteRoot\": \"/remote/dir"
"\" }\n"
"        ]\n"
"    },\n"
"    \"lspclient\": {\n"
"        \"servers\": {\n"
"            \"python\": {\n"
"                // this will match/join with the above object\n"
"                \"exec\": { \"hostname\": \"foobar\" },\n"
"                // confine this server to this project root,\n"
"                // so it is not used for other projects that may be opened\n"
"                // (other servers may already employ specific roots, but "
"python generally not)\n"
"                \"root\": \".\"\n"
"            },\n"
"            \"c\": {\n"
"                // as above\n"
"                \"exec\": { \"hostname\": \"foobar\" },\n"
"                \"root\": \".\"\n"
"            }\n"
"        }\n"
"    }\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2926
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"So, what happens as a result of the above? As mentioned, the "
"<literal>lspclient</literal> part of the above is merged onto the global "
"config, hence an <literal>exec</literal> section is found (for specified "
"languages). A search is performed for another object (that specifies "
"matching <literal>hostname</literal>) in either <literal>exec</literal> or "
"<literal>lspclient</literal> section, and a matching one is as a basis for a "
"merge. As a result, an LSP server (for C and python) will have its "
"commandline appended to the specified (variable substituted) prefix, and "
"will therefore be started within the given container. Of course, the "
"container must have been created, in a proper started state and equipped "
"with proper LSP servers. One might have been tempted to use the "
"<literal>global</literal> section (within <literal>lspclient</literal>.) "
"That could also work, but then <emphasis>all</emphasis> LSP servers would be "
"started with that prefix, including those for e.g. Markdown, Bash script or "
"JSON. It is more likely that the usual host will still supply these (if in "
"use). So, as always, it depends on your particular setup."
msgstr ""
"Kaj se torej zgodi kot posledica zgoraj navedenega? Kot že omenjeno, se del "
"<literal>lspclient</literal> zgornjega združi v globalno konfiguracijo, zato "
"se najde razdelek <literal>exec</literal> (za določene jezike). Izvede se "
"iskanje drugega objekta (ki določa ujemajoče se <literal>hostname</literal>) "
"v razdelku <literal>exec</literal> ali <literal>lspclient</literal>, "
"ujemajoči se pa služi kot osnova za združitev. Posledično bo strežnik LSP "
"(za C in python) imel svojo ukazno vrstico dodano določeni (spremenljivka "
"nadomeščena) predponi in se bo zato zagnal znotraj danega vsebnika. Seveda "
"mora biti vsebnik ustvarjen, v pravilno zagnanem stanju in opremljen z "
"ustreznimi strežniki LSP. Morda bi kdo želel uporabiti razdelek "
"<literal>global</literal> (znotraj <literal>lspclient</literal>). Tudi to bi "
"lahko delovalo, vendar bi se potem <emphasis>vsi</emphasis> strežniki LSP "
"zagnali s to predpono, vključno s tistimi za npr. Markdown, Bash skript ali "
"JSON. Bolj verjetno je, da jih bo običajni gostitelj še vedno zagotavljal "
"(če so v uporabi). Torej je, kot vedno, odvisno od vaše posebne nastavitve."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2945
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"However, the LSP server may now observe different (remote) paths than the "
"(local) ones that are seen and used by the editor. The specified "
"<literal>pathMappings</literal> are used to translate back and forth between "
"either within the communication with the LSP server. That is, of course, as "
"much as possible. Clearly, not all local paths have a remote representation, "
"but the missing ones are also not seen (by the server) and do not pose a "
"problem. Conversely, however, the (remote) server may now see and provide "
"references in the \"remote root\" which are not evidently/easily represented "
"in the local system. The enabled <literal>mapRemoteRoot</literal> implicitly "
"maps the remote root onto a \"local URL\" <literal>exec://foobar/</literal>, "
"which is then handled by a plain-and-simple KIO protocol. The latter "
"essentially uses (e.g.) <literal>podman exec -i foobarcontainer cat somefile"
"\"</literal> for copy from remote to local (and other such variations using "
"tools from the <literal>coreutils</literal> suite). Suffice it to say it is "
"not meant for general use and claims no performance whatsoever, but it does "
"suffice to get a referenced file quickly and easily loaded into editor."
msgstr ""
"Vendar pa lahko strežnik LSP zdaj opazuje drugačne (oddaljene) poti kot "
"(lokalne), ki jih vidi in uporablja urejevalnik. Določene preslikave poti "
"<literal>pathMappings</literal> se uporabljajo za prevajanje med obema "
"znotraj komunikacije s strežnikom LSP. To je seveda čim več. Jasno je, da "
"nimajo vse lokalne poti oddaljene predstavitve, vendar manjkajočih poti tudi "
"strežnik ne vidi in ne predstavljajo težave. Nasprotno pa lahko (oddaljeni) "
"strežnik zdaj vidi in zagotovi reference v \"oddaljenem korenu\", ki niso "
"očitno/enostavno predstavljene v lokalnem sistemu. Omogočena možnost "
"<literal>mapRemoteRoot</literal> implicitno preslika oddaljeni koren na "
"\"lokalni URL\" <literal>exec://foobar/</literal>, ki ga nato obravnava "
"preprost protokol KIO. Slednji v bistvu uporablja (npr.) <literal>podman "
"exec -i foobarcontainer cat somefile\"</literal> za kopiranje z oddaljenega "
"na lokalno okolje (in druge podobne različice z uporabo orodij iz paketa "
"<literal>coreutils</literal>). Naj povemo, da ni namenjen splošni uporabi in "
"ne zahteva nobene zmogljivosti, vendar zadostuje za hitro in enostavno "
"nalaganje referenčne datoteke v urejevalnik."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2964
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It is now easily seen that a simplified version of above configuration "
"(without <literal>hostname</literal> or <literal>pathMappings</literal>) "
"could be used to handle the virtualenv without having to duplicate server "
"commandline (in wrapper script)."
msgstr ""
"Sedaj je enostavno videti, da bi lahko poenostavljeno različico zgornje "
"konfiguracije (brez <literal>hostname</literal> ali <literal>pathMappings</"
"literal>) uporabili za upravljanje virtualnega okolja brez podvajanja ukazne "
"vrstice strežnika (v ovojnem skriptu)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2971
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following may not be so easily seen, so it is mentioned here explicitly."
msgstr ""
"Naslednje morda ni tako enostavno videti, zato je tukaj izrecno omenjeno."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2976
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both a <literal>hostname</literal> and the actual <literal>prefix</literal> "
"define the execution environment (the former by name, the latter by "
"content). Within an editor process instance, the same <literal>hostname</"
"literal> should not be associated with different <literal>prefix</literal>, "
"as such leads to undefined behavior (with no diagnostic required)."
msgstr ""
"Tako <literal>hostname</literal> kot dejanska <literal>predpona</literal> "
"določata okolje izvajanja (prva po imenu, druga po vsebini). Znotraj pojavka "
"procesa urejevalnika isto <literal>hostname</literal> ne sme biti povezano z "
"različnimi <literal>predponami</literal>, saj to vodi do nedefiniranega "
"vedenja (brez potrebne diagnostike)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2985
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Both <literal>prefix</literal> and <literal>pathMappings</literal> are "
"subject to (editor) variable expansion (but do mind the foregoing item)."
msgstr ""
"Tako <literal>prefix</literal> kot <literal>pathMappings</literal> sta "
"predmet razširitve (urejevalnikovih) spremenljivk (vendar upoštevajte "
"zgornji element)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:2991
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"At runtime, some environment variables are also set, which may be used to "
"(subtly) adjust the \"prefix launcher\"'s behavior (though again mind the "
"first item). In particular, <literal>KATE_EXEC_PLUGIN</literal> is set to "
"<literal>lspclient</literal> and <literal>KATE_EXEC_SERVER</literal> is set "
"to the server's id (e.g. <literal>python</literal>)."
msgstr ""
"Med izvajanjem se nastavijo tudi nekatere okoljske spremenljivke, ki jih je "
"mogoče uporabiti za (subtilno) prilagajanje vedenja \"predpone zaganjalnika"
"\" (čeprav spet upoštevajte prvo postavko). Predvsem je "
"<literal>KATE_EXEC_PLUGIN</literal> nastavljen na <literal>lspclient</"
"literal>, <literal>KATE_EXEC_SERVER</literal> pa na ID strežnika (npr. "
"<literal>python</literal>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3000
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In particular, also <literal>KATE_EXEC_INSPECT</literal> is set to "
"<literal>1</literal>. This notifies the \"prefix launcher\" that the "
"receiver (Kate plugin) accepts some out-of-band/protocol data. This allows "
"the launcher to use some means to determine path mappings (e.g. "
"<literal>podman inspect</literal>) and to communicate this in suitable "
"format. This will then be removed from the otherwise LSP protocol conforming "
"stream and used to extend any defined path mapping. This may serve as an "
"alternative to specifying e.g. bind mounts explicitly (again, duplicating "
"the container's definition). Concretely, the above snippet could then be "
"used instead;"
msgstr ""
"Še posebej je tudi <literal>KATE_EXEC_INSPECT</literal> nastavljen na "
"<literal>1</literal>. To obvesti »predponski zaganjalnik«, da sprejemnik "
"(vtičnik Kate) sprejema nekatere podatke zunaj pasu/protokola. To omogoča "
"zaganjalniku, da uporabi nekatera sredstva za določanje preslikav poti (npr. "
"<literal>podman inspect</literal>) in da to sporoči v ustrezni obliki. To bo "
"nato odstranjeno iz toka, ki je sicer skladen s protokolom LSP, in "
"uporabljeno za razširitev katerega koli definiranega preslikavanja poti. To "
"lahko služi kot alternativa eksplicitnemu določanju npr. povezav (spet "
"podvajanje definicije vsebnika). Konkretno bi se lahko namesto tega uporabil "
"zgornji delček kode;"

#. Tag: screen
#: plugins.docbook:3010
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"{\n"
"    // ...\n"
"    \"exec\": {\n"
"        \"hostname\": \"foobar\"\n"
"        // unfortunate repetition of name, but the helper script is plain-"
"and-simple\n"
"        \"prefix\": \"exec_inspect.sh foobarcontainer podman exec -i "
"foobarcontainer\",\n"
"        \"mapRemoteRoot\": true,\n"
"        \"pathMappings\": []\n"
"    }\n"
"    // ...\n"
"}"
msgstr ""
"{\n"
"    // ...\n"
"    \"exec\": {\n"
"        \"hostname\": \"foobar\"\n"
"        // unfortunate repetition of name, but the helper script is plain-"
"and-simple\n"
"        \"prefix\": \"exec_inspect.sh foobarcontainer podman exec -i "
"foobarcontainer\",\n"
"        \"mapRemoteRoot\": true,\n"
"        \"pathMappings\": []\n"
"    }\n"
"    // ...\n"
"}"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3015
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Last but not least, what if the \"fallback KIO\" approach is not considered "
"adequate? It is in practice often possible to \"mount\" the remote root into "
"the local filesystem and then specify the latter in a <literal>pathMappings</"
"literal>. For starters, the well-known <literal>sshfs</literal> (fuse) "
"filesystem can mount a (really) remote system into the local one. For a "
"container (podman/docker), most (filesystem driver) setups support the "
"following trick; <screen>\n"
"$ rootdir=/proc/`podman inspect --format '{{.State.Pid}}' containername`/"
"root\n"
"# some symlinks may cause issues, see also alternative below\n"
"$ sudo mount --bind $rootdir /somewhere/containername\n"
"</screen> If that fails, then one could resort to <literal>sshfs</literal>, "
"or in fact a subset thereof to mount the remote/container root; <screen>\n"
"# see respective man-pages; sftp-server suffices for actual (unencrypted) "
"file ops protocol\n"
"$ socat 'exec:podman exec -i containername /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server'\n"
"   'exec:sshfs -o transform_symlinks -o passive \\:/ /somewhere/"
"containername'\n"
"# ...\n"
"$ fusermount -u /somewhere/containername\n"
"</screen> Note that such mount of remote root into host filesystem is likely "
"to be specified manually and explicitly in a <literal>pathMappings</literal> "
"section (barring a very intelligent prefix launcher that arranges all such "
"automagically)."
msgstr ""
"Nenazadnje, kaj pa, če pristop \"rezervnega KIO\" ni ustrezen? V praksi je "
"pogosto mogoče \"priklopiti\" oddaljeni korenski sistem v lokalni datotečni "
"sistem in nato slednjega določiti v <literal>pathMappings</literal>. Za "
"začetek lahko dobro znani datotečni sistem <literal>sshfs</literal> (fuse) "
"priklopi (resnično) oddaljeni sistem v lokalni. Za vsebnik (podman/docker) "
"večina nastavitev (gonilnika datotečnega sistema) podpira naslednji trik; "
"<screen>\n"
"$ rootdir=/proc/`podman inspect --format '{{.State.Pid}}' containername`/"
"root\n"
"# nekatere simbolične povezave lahko povzročijo težave, glejte tudi "
"alternativo spodaj\n"
"$ sudo mount --bind $rootdir /somewhere/containername\n"
"</screen> Če to ne uspe, se lahko za priklop oddaljenega/korenskega vsebnika "
"zatečete k <literal>sshfs</literal> ali pravzaprav k njegovi podmnožici; "
"<screen>\n"
"# glejte ustrezne strani priročnika; sftp-server zadostuje za dejanski "
"(nešifrirani) protokol za upravljanje datotek\n"
"$ socat 'exec:podman exec -i containername /usr/lib/openssh/sftp-server'\n"
"'exec:sshfs -o transform_symlinks -o passive \\:/ /somewhere/containername'\n"
"# ...\n"
"$ fusermount -u /somewhere/containername\n"
"</screen> Upoštevajte, da bo takšno priklop oddaljenega korenskega sistema v "
"datotečni sistem gostitelja verjetno ročno in eksplicitno določeno v "
"razdelku <literal>pathMappings</literal> (razen zelo inteligentnega "
"zaganjalnika predpon, ki vse to samodejno uredi)."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3080
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search &amp; Replace"
msgstr "Iskanje &amp; Zamenjati"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3084
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate;'s Search &amp; Replace plugin allows you to search for text or <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html\">regular expressions</ulink> "
"in many different files at once. You can search all open files, all the "
"files in one directory and optionally its subdirectories, or in the active "
"file. You can even filter by filename, for instance searching only files "
"that end with a particular file extension."
msgstr ""
"Iskanje &amp;kate; Vtičnik Zamenjaj vam omogoča iskanje besedila ali <ulink "
"url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html\">regularnih izrazov</ulink> v "
"več različnih datotekah hkrati. Iščete lahko po vseh odprtih datotekah, po "
"vseh datotekah v enem imeniku in po želji v njegovih podimenikih ali v "
"aktivni datoteki. Lahko celo filtrirate po imenu datoteke, na primer iščete "
"samo datoteke, ki se končajo z določeno datotečno pripono."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3097
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Query"
msgstr "Iskalna poizvedba"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3099
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following options are always displayed at the top of the Search in Files "
"tool view:"
msgstr ""
"Na vrhu pogleda orodja Iskanje v datotekah so vedno prikazane naslednje "
"možnosti:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3107
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can have as many searches as you want open at the same time. Simply "
"click the new tab button at the top-left corner of the Search tool view and "
"a new results tab will open permitting you to perform another search."
msgstr ""
"Hkrati imate lahko odprtih poljubno število iskanj. Preprosto kliknite gumb "
"za nov zavihek v zgornjem levem kotu pogleda iskalnega orodja in odprl se bo "
"nov zavihek z rezultati, ki vam bo omogočil novo iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3118
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The button in the top right-corner of the Search in Files tool view will "
"toggle the bottom half of the tool view between displaying additional "
"options for the Search in Folder mode and the results of your search."
msgstr ""
"Gumb v zgornjem desnem kotu pogleda orodja Iskanje v datotekah preklopi "
"spodnjo polovico pogleda orodja med prikazom dodatnih možnosti za način "
"Iskanje v mapi in rezultati vašega iskanja."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Find"
msgstr "Najdi"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3127
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This is where you type in what you want to find. You may enter standard "
"text, or a regular expression if enabled."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj vnesete, kar želite najti. Vnesete lahko standardno besedilo ali "
"regularni izraz, če je omogočen."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:3134
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Replace</guilabel> (text box)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Zamenjaj</guilabel> (besedilno polje)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3135
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Replacement text that will be added to file(s) in place of the text in the "
"<guilabel>Find</guilabel> text box."
msgstr ""
"Nadomestno besedilo, ki bo dodano datoteki(-am) namesto besedila v "
"besedilnem polju <guilabel>Najdi</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3142
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search"
msgstr "Iskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you've finished configuring everything, just press the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button to perform your search; to perform the "
"search in a new tab press and hold &Ctrl; before pressing the "
"<guibutton>Search</guibutton> button. You may also press &Enter; in the "
"<guilabel>Find</guilabel> text box to do the same (similarly pressing "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> will perform the search "
"in a new tab)."
msgstr ""
"Ko ste končali z vsemi konfiguracijami, samo pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Išči</guibutton>, da izvedete iskanje; za izvedbo iskanja v novem "
"zavihku pritisnite in držite &Ctrl; preden pritisnete gumb <guibutton>Išči</"
"guibutton>. Lahko tudi pritisnete &Enter; v besedilnem polju "
"<guilabel>Najdi</guilabel>, da storite enako (podobno s pritiskom <keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> izvedete iskanje v novem zavihku)."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3155
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace"
msgstr "Zamenjati"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you've finished configuring everything, just press the "
"<guibutton>Replace</guibutton> button to replace the text entered in the "
"<guilabel>Find</guilabel> text box with that of the <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> text box. You may also press &Enter; in the <guilabel>Replace</"
"guilabel> text box to do the same."
msgstr ""
"Ko končate z vsemi konfiguracijami, samo pritisnite gumb "
"<guibutton>Zamenjaj</guibutton>, da nadomestite besedilo, vneseno v "
"besedilno polje <guilabel>Najdi</guilabel>, z besedilom <guilabel>Zamenjaj</"
"guilabel> škatla. Lahko tudi pritisnete &Enter; v besedilnem polju "
"<guilabel>Zamenjaj</guilabel>, da storite enako."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3166
#, no-c-format
msgid "Next"
msgstr "Naslednji"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the next match of your search query, switching files if necessary."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na naslednje ujemanje vaše iskalne poizvedbe in po potrebi "
"zamenjajte datoteke."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3173
#, no-c-format
msgid "Replace Checked"
msgstr "Zamenjaj označeno"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The same as <guibutton>Replace</guibutton>, but will only perform "
"replacements in files that are checked in the pane below."
msgstr ""
"Enako kot <guibutton>Zamenjaj</guibutton>, vendar bo izvedel samo zamenjave "
"v datotekah, ki so označene v spodnjem podoknu."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3184
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in Folder Options"
msgstr "Iščite v možnostih mape"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3186
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"These options are displayed below the aforementioned query options. If "
"search results are being displayed instead, press the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"games-config-"
"options-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> button to display them."
msgstr ""
"Te možnosti so prikazane pod zgoraj omenjenimi možnostmi poizvedbe. Če so "
"namesto tega prikazani rezultati iskanja, pritisnite "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject> <imagedata fileref=\"games-config-"
"options-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon>, da jih prikažete."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3194
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search in"
msgstr "Išči v"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3195
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This has three options. Select <guilabel>Open Files</guilabel> to search all "
"files currently open in &kate;. Select <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> to search "
"inside a folder and optionally its subfolders. Select <guilabel>Current "
"File</guilabel> to search only in the active file."
msgstr ""
"To ima tri možnosti. Izberite <guilabel>Odpri datoteke</guilabel> za iskanje "
"po vseh trenutno odprtih datotekah v &kate;. Izberite <guilabel>Mapa</"
"guilabel> za iskanje znotraj mape in po želji v njenih podmapah. Izberite "
"<guilabel>Trenutna datoteka</guilabel> za iskanje samo v aktivni datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the <guilabel>Projects</guilabel> plugin is loaded, you can also search "
"in the <guilabel>Current Project</guilabel> or in <guilabel>All Open "
"Projects</guilabel>."
msgstr ""
"Če je vtičnik <guilabel>Projekti</guilabel> naložen, lahko iščete tudi v "
"<guilabel>Trenutni projekt</guilabel> ali <guilabel>Vsi odprti projekti</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3208
#, no-c-format
msgid "Match case"
msgstr "Primer vžigalice"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3209
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Restricts search results to only those that have the exact same combination "
"of upper and lower case letters as your search query."
msgstr ""
"Omeji rezultate iskanja samo na tiste, ki imajo popolnoma enako kombinacijo "
"velikih in malih črk kot vaša iskalna poizvedba."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3216
#, no-c-format
msgid "Regular expressions"
msgstr "Regularni izrazi"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Permits you to use <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html"
"\">regular expressions</ulink> instead of simple text as your search query."
msgstr ""
"Omogoča uporabo <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/regular-expressions.html"
"\">regularnih izrazov</ulink> namesto preprostega besedila kot iskalno "
"poizvedbo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3224
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand results"
msgstr "Razširi rezultate"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3225
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Display all the results found in each file, instead of just a list of files "
"that contain the search query."
msgstr ""
"Prikažite vse rezultate, najdene v posamezni datoteki, namesto le seznama "
"datotek, ki vsebujejo iskalno poizvedbo."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3232
#, no-c-format
msgid "Folder"
msgstr "Mapa"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may enter the path of the folder you wish to search. For instance, you "
"might enter <userinput>~/development/kde/kate/</userinput> if you wished to "
"search the &kate; source code. This option is only available when using "
"<guilabel>in Folder</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Vnesete lahko pot do mape, po kateri želite iskati. Na primer, lahko vnesete "
"<userinput>~/development/kde/kate/</userinput>, če želite iskati po &kate; "
"izvorna koda. Ta možnost je na voljo le pri uporabi načina <guilabel>v mapi</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guiicon
#: plugins.docbook:3242
#, no-c-format
msgid "Open file dialog"
msgstr "Odpri pogovorno okno datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to locate the folder in your desktop's folder browser. "
"This button only works when using <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, da poiščete mapo v brskalniku map na namizju. Ta gumb "
"deluje samo v načinu <guilabel>Mapa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Press this button to change <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> to the parent of the "
"currently selected folder. This button only works when using "
"<guilabel>Folder</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Pritisnite ta gumb, če želite spremeniti <guilabel>Mapa</guilabel> v "
"nadrejenega elementa trenutno izbrane mape. Ta gumb deluje samo v načinu "
"<guilabel>Mapa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3262
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This button will set the <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> entry to the folder in "
"which the currently open document is located. This button only works when "
"using <guilabel>Folder</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Ta gumb nastavi vnos <guilabel>Mapa</guilabel> na mapo, v kateri se nahaja "
"trenutno odprt dokument. Ta gumb deluje samo v načinu <guilabel>Mapa</"
"guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3270
#, no-c-format
msgid "Filter"
msgstr "Filter"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This permits you to only search filenames that match a particular pattern. "
"For instance, to only search files written in C++, change it to <userinput>*."
"cpp</userinput>. To search only files beginning with <literal>kate</"
"literal>, change it to <userinput>kate*</userinput>. You can enter multiple "
"filters separated with a comma (<userinput>,</userinput>). This option is "
"not available when using <guilabel>Open files</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"To vam omogoča, da iščete samo imena datotek, ki se ujemajo z določenim "
"vzorcem. Če želite na primer iskati samo datoteke, napisane v C++, ga "
"spremenite v <userinput>*.cpp</userinput>. Če želite preiskati samo "
"datoteke, ki se začnejo z <literal>kate</literal>, ga spremenite v "
"<userinput>kate*</userinput>. Vnesete lahko več filtrov, ločenih z vejico "
"(<userinput>,</userinput>). Ta možnost ni na voljo, ko uporabljate način "
"<guilabel>Odpiranje datotek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3282
#, no-c-format
msgid "Exclude"
msgstr "Izključi"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3283
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The opposite of <guilabel>Filter</guilabel>, this prevents &kate; from "
"searching files that match the specified patterns. As with <guilabel>Filter</"
"guilabel>, you can enter multiple patterns separated with a comma "
"(<userinput>,</userinput>). This option is not available when using "
"<guilabel>Open files</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Nasprotno od <guilabel >Filter</guilabel >, to preprečuje &kate; iz iskanja "
"datotek, ki se ujemajo z določenimi vzorci. Kot pri <guilabel>Filter</"
"guilabel> lahko vnesete več vzorcev, ločenih z vejico (<userinput>,</"
"userinput>). Ta možnost ni na voljo, ko uporabljate način "
"<guilabel>Odpiranje datotek</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3293
#, no-c-format
msgid "Recursive"
msgstr "Rekurzivno"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, &kate; will also search in all subfolders of the "
"selected folder. This option is only available when using <guilabel>Folder</"
"guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, &kate; bo iskal tudi v vseh podmapah izbrane "
"mape. Ta možnost je na voljo le pri uporabi načina <guilabel>Mapa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3302
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include hidden"
msgstr "Vključi skrito"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3303
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this option is enabled, &kate; will also search in files or folders that "
"are typically hidden by your &OS;. This option is only available when using "
"<guilabel>Folder</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Če je ta možnost omogočena, &kate; bo iskal tudi v datotekah ali mapah, ki "
"jih vaš &OS; običajno skriva. Ta možnost je na voljo le pri uporabi načina "
"<guilabel>Mapa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3311
#, no-c-format
msgid "Follow symbolic links"
msgstr "Sledite simboličnim povezavam"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3312
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Search in Files plugin typically does not follow <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Symbolic_link\">symbolic links</ulink>. When this option "
"is enabled, the plugin will follow them instead and search inside the files "
"or folders they reference. This option is only available when using "
"<guilabel>Folder</guilabel> mode."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik Iskanje v datotekah običajno ne sledi <ulink url=\"https://en."
"wikipedia.org/wiki/Symbolic_link\">simboličnim povezavam</ulink>. Ko je ta "
"možnost omogočena, jim bo vtičnik sledil in iskal znotraj datotek ali map, "
"na katere se sklicujejo. Ta možnost je na voljo le pri uporabi načina "
"<guilabel>Mapa</guilabel>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It's possible for symbolic links to reference a folder that is the parent of "
"the folder currently being searched, or other folders that contain symbolic "
"links to their parent. If there is such a link in the folder being searched "
"and this option is enabled, &kate; will repeatedly follow the link and "
"search the folder, and the search will never complete."
msgstr ""
"Možno je, da se simbolične povezave sklicujejo na mapo, ki je nadrejena "
"trenutno iskani mapi, ali na druge mape, ki vsebujejo simbolične povezave na "
"nadrejeno mapo. Če je taka povezava v mapi, ki jo iščete, in je ta možnost "
"omogočena, &kate; bo večkrat sledil povezavi in iskal mapo, pri čemer "
"iskanje ne bo nikoli dokončano."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3328
#, no-c-format
msgid "Include binary files"
msgstr "Vključi binarne datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3329
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If enabled, &kate; will also search in files that do not appear to be text "
"files."
msgstr ""
"Če je omogočeno, &kate; bo iskal tudi v datotekah, ki niso videti kot "
"besedilne datoteke."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3339
#, no-c-format
msgid "Search Results"
msgstr "Rezultati iskanja"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3341
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The results of your search are displayed below the query options. If options "
"for Search in Folder mode are displayed, simply press the "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"games-config-"
"options-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon> button to display them. They will also automatically be displayed "
"as soon as a search is performed."
msgstr ""
"Rezultati vašega iskanja so prikazani pod možnostmi poizvedbe. Če so "
"prikazane možnosti za iskanje v načinu mape, preprosto pritisnite "
"<guiicon><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"games-config-"
"options-22.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guiicon>, da jih prikažete. Prav tako se samodejno prikažejo, takoj ko se "
"izvede iskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3348
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The search results display a list of files that contains text that matches "
"your search query, followed by the number of matches found in that file."
msgstr ""
"Rezultati iskanja prikažejo seznam datotek, ki vsebujejo besedilo, ki se "
"ujema z vašo iskalno poizvedbo, ki mu sledi število najdenih ujemanj v tej "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To see a list of matches in that file, simply click the expansion arrow to "
"the left of the file name. (If you selected the <guilabel>Expand results</"
"guilabel> option, this will already be done for you.) The line number each "
"match is found on will be displayed, followed by the contents of that line, "
"with your search query indicated in bold text."
msgstr ""
"Če si želite ogledati seznam ujemanj v tej datoteki, preprosto kliknite "
"puščico za razširitev na levi strani imena datoteke. (Če ste izbrali možnost "
"<guilabel>Razširi rezultate</guilabel>, bo to že opravljeno namesto vas.) "
"Prikazana bo številka vrstice, v kateri je najdeno ujemanje, ki ji bo "
"sledila vsebina te vrstice, z vašo iskalno poizvedbo. v krepkem tisku."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To open the file your result was found in, simply double-click it. &kate; "
"will open the file if needed. You can also move the cursor to the location "
"of a particular match by double-clicking on its listing instead of the file "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Če želite odpreti datoteko, v kateri je bil najden vaš rezultat, jo "
"preprosto dvakrat kliknite. &kate; po potrebi odpre datoteko. Kazalko lahko "
"premaknete tudi na lokacijo določenega ujemanja tako, da dvakrat kliknete "
"njegov seznam namesto imena datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:3371
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Search in Files</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>F</keycap></"
"keycombo> </shortcut> <guimenu>Urejanje</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Iskanje v "
"datotekah</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3379
#, no-c-format
msgid "Launches the Search and Replace tool view."
msgstr "Zažene pogled orodja za iskanje in zamenjavo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:3384
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Next Match</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na naslednje ujemanje</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3389
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the next match in a search performed by the Search and Replace plugin."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na naslednje ujemanje v iskanju, ki ga izvede vtičnik Iskanje in "
"zamenjava."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:3395
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Edit</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Go to Previous Match</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Uredi</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Pojdi na prejšnje ujemanje</"
"guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3400
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Go to the previous match in a search performed by the Search and Replace "
"plugin."
msgstr ""
"Pojdite na prejšnje ujemanje pri iskanju, ki ga izvaja vtičnik Iskanje in "
"zamenjava."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:3406
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Search and Replace</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži iskanje in zamenjavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3411
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle the display of &kate;'s <guilabel>Search and Replace</guilabel> tool."
msgstr "Preklopi prikaz orodja <guilabel>Išči in zamenjaj</guilabel> &kate;."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3428
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; Scripts &amp; Snippets"
msgstr "&kate; skripti in delčki kode"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3432
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The &kate; Scripts &amp; Snippets plugin allows you to add, and manage your "
"own bits of automation. This can range from static re-useable pieces of "
"plain text, over sophisticated templates with custom automated and "
"scriptable fields, to fully custom &javascript; scripts to modify the "
"contents of your document."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik &kate; Skripti in delčki kode vam omogoča dodajanje in upravljanje "
"lastnih avtomatizacij. To lahko sega od statičnih, ponovno uporabnih kosov "
"navadnega besedila, preko dovršenih predlog s prilagojenimi avtomatiziranimi "
"in skriptnimi polji, do popolnoma prilagojenih skript v &javascript; za "
"spreminjanje vsebine vašega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3436
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For the most part, these types of content are managed in exactly the same "
"way. Therefore, for ease of reading, the following discussion does not "
"differentiate between static snippets, scripted snippets, and scripts. "
"Rather, the term <quote>snippet</quote> is used to refer to all of them."
msgstr ""
"Večinoma se vsebine te vrste upravljajo na popolnoma enak način. Zato zaradi "
"lažjega branja naslednja razprava ne razlikuje med statičnimi delčki kode, "
"skriptiranimi delčki kode in skripti. Namesto tega se za vse uporablja izraz "
"<quote>delček kode</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3439
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin also supports assigning keyboard shortcuts, and inserting "
"snippets via code completion. Further, you can download collections of "
"snippets (so-called repositories) from the internet."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik podpira tudi dodeljevanje bližnjic na tipkovnici in vstavljanje "
"delčkov kode prek dokončanja kode. Poleg tega lahko z interneta prenesete "
"zbirke delčkov kode (tako imenovane repozitorije)."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:3449
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Snippets</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Prikaži delčke kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3451
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Shows snippets panel containing all snippets in your repository that are for "
"the currently opened file type."
msgstr ""
"Prikaže ploščo z delčki kode, ki vsebuje vse delčke kode v vašem skladišču, "
"ki so za trenutno odprto vrsto datoteke."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:3456
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Create Snippet</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Ustvari delček kode</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3461
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a new snippet, which is a reusable chunk of text you may insert in "
"any part of any document, or a small script."
msgstr ""
"Ustvari nov delček kode, ki je del besedila za večkratno uporabo in ga lahko "
"vstavite v kateri koli del katerega koli dokumenta, ali pa majhen skript."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3471
#, no-c-format
msgid "Snippets panel"
msgstr "Plošča z delčki kode"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:3474
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; Snippets Panel"
msgstr "&kate; Plošča z delčki kode"

#. Tag: phrase
#: plugins.docbook:3477
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kate; snippets panel."
msgstr "&kate; plošča z delčki kode."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3478
#, no-c-format
msgid "The panel for &kate; Snippets."
msgstr "Plošča za &kate; Delčki kode."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3482
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the panel you should see a list of snippet repositories, along with "
"options to create your own, get them from the Internet or load them from a "
"local file. Each repository has a checkbox that can be used to activate or "
"deactivate it. There are also buttons to edit and delete existing "
"repositories."
msgstr ""
"Na plošči bi morali videti seznam skladišč delčkov kode, skupaj z možnostmi, "
"da ustvarite svoje, jih pridobite iz interneta ali naložite iz lokalne "
"datoteke. Vsak repozitorij ima potrditveno polje, s katerim ga lahko "
"aktivirate ali deaktivirate. Obstajajo tudi gumbi za urejanje in brisanje "
"obstoječih repozitorijev."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3489
#, no-c-format
msgid "Loading Snippet Repository Files"
msgstr "Nalaganje datotek repozitorija delčkov kode"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3490
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can download snippet repositories from the Internet. Just click "
"<guibutton>Get New Snippets</guibutton> and a window with a list of snippet "
"repositories will open. After downloading the desired snippet, make sure "
"that you have activated it."
msgstr ""
"Repozitorije delčkov kode lahko prenesete iz interneta. Samo kliknite "
"<guibutton>Pridobi nove delčke kode</guibutton> in odprlo se bo okno s "
"seznamom repozitorijev delčkov kode. Ko prenesete želeni delček kode, se "
"prepričajte, da ste ga aktivirali."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3501
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating and Editing Repositories"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje in urejanje repozitorijev"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3503
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To create a new snippet repository, click <guibutton>Add Repository</"
"guibutton>. You should now see a dialog that asks for the name of the "
"snippet file, license and author. After choosing the desired options, click "
"<guibutton>OK</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite ustvariti novo skladišče delčkov kode, kliknite <guibutton>Dodaj "
"skladišče</guibutton>. Zdaj bi morali videti pogovorno okno, ki zahteva ime "
"datoteke delčka kode, licenco in avtorja. Ko izberete želene možnosti, "
"kliknite <guibutton>V redu</guibutton>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:3508 plugins.docbook:3558
#, no-c-format
msgid "Snippet Editor"
msgstr "Urejevalnik delčkov kode"

#. Tag: phrase
#: plugins.docbook:3511
#, no-c-format
msgid "The repository editor."
msgstr "Urejevalnik repozitorija."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3512
#, no-c-format
msgid "The repository editor interface."
msgstr "Vmesnik urejevalnika repozitorija."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3516
#, no-c-format
msgid "The snippet repository editor contains the following options:"
msgstr "Urejevalnik skladišča delčkov kode vsebuje naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3521 plugins.docbook:3569
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Ime"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3522
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Appears in the list of snippets in the tool view and is also searched when "
"using the code completion feature."
msgstr ""
"Pojavi se na seznamu delčkov kode v pogledu orodij in se išče tudi pri "
"uporabi funkcije dokončanja kode."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3527
#, no-c-format
msgid "Namespace"
msgstr "Imenski prostor"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3528
#, no-c-format
msgid "Prefix used while using code completion."
msgstr "Predpona, uporabljena med uporabo dopolnjevanja kode."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3532
#, no-c-format
msgid "License"
msgstr "Licenca"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3533
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select the license for you snippet repository."
msgstr "Izberite licenco za svoje skladišče delčkov kode."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3537
#, no-c-format
msgid "Authors"
msgstr "Avtorji"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3538
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enter the name(s) of the author(s) of the snippet file."
msgstr "Vnesite ime(-na) avtorja(-ov) datoteke delčkov kode."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3542
#, no-c-format
msgid "File types"
msgstr "Vrste datotek"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3543
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select the file type(s) you want the snippet repository to apply to. It is "
"set to <quote></quote> by default, so the repository applies to all files. "
"You can change it to something like <userinput>C++</userinput> for instance, "
"or select from a list by clicking on the items. You can specify more than "
"one file type pressing the &Shift; while adding types."
msgstr ""
"Izberite vrste datotek, za katere želite, da se uporablja repozitorij "
"delčkov kode. Privzeto je nastavljen na <quote></quote>, tako da skladišče "
"velja za vse datoteke. Spremenite ga lahko na primer v <userinput>C++</"
"userinput> ali pa izberete s seznama s klikom na elemente. Določite lahko "
"več kot eno vrsto datoteke s pritiskom &Shift; med dodajanjem vrst."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3555
#, no-c-format
msgid "Creating and Editing Snippets"
msgstr "Ustvarjanje in urejanje delčkov kode"

#. Tag: phrase
#: plugins.docbook:3561
#, no-c-format
msgid "The snippet editor."
msgstr "Urejevalnik delčkov kode."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3562
#, no-c-format
msgid "The snippet editor interface."
msgstr "Vmesnik urejevalnika izrezkov."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The name as shown in the list of snippets, and in the completion list "
"(required)."
msgstr ""
"Ime, kot je prikazano na seznamu koščkov kode in na seznamu za dokončanje "
"(obvezno)."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3574
#, no-c-format
msgid "Type"
msgstr "Vrsta"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Snippets may either be defined as text templates or scripts. Both types "
"allow to use &javascript; functions (see below for details), and can thus be "
"used to similar effect. However, as a rule of thumb, text templates will be "
"more suitable if you mostly want to <emphasis>insert</emphasis> text, while "
"scripts are often an easier solution if you want to <emphasis>modify</"
"emphasis> text)."
msgstr ""
"Delčki kode so lahko definirani kot besedilne predloge ali skripti. Obe "
"vrsti omogočata uporabo funkcij &javascript; (za podrobnosti glejte spodaj) "
"in ju je zato mogoče uporabiti s podobnim učinkom. Vendar pa so besedilne "
"predloge praviloma bolj primerne, če želite predvsem <emphasis>vstaviti</"
"emphasis> besedilo, medtem ko so skripti pogosto lažja rešitev, če želite "
"<emphasis>spremeniti</emphasis> besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Kate needs to be compiled against KTextEditor version 6.15.0 or higher, for "
"this feature to be available. For earlier versions, only text template "
"snippets can be used."
msgstr ""
"Za uporabo te funkcije je treba Kate prevesti v KTextEditor različice 6.15.0 "
"ali novejše. V starejših različicah je mogoče uporabljati le delčke predlog "
"besedila."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:3583
#, no-c-format
msgid "Shortcut"
msgstr "Bližnjica"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3584
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Pressing this shortcut will insert (or run) the snippet into the current "
"document."
msgstr ""
"S pritiskom na to bližnjico boste vstavili (ali zagnali) delček kode v "
"trenutni dokument."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:3588
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guilabel>Snippet</guilabel> (type <userinput>Text Template</userinput>)"
msgstr ""
"<guilabel>Delček kode</guilabel> (vrsta <userinput>predloga besedila</"
"userinput>)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3589
#, no-c-format
msgid "The text your snippet will insert into the document."
msgstr "Besedilo, ki ga bo vaš delček vstavil v dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3590
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A snippet can contain editable fields. They can be cycled by pressing &Tab;. "
"The following expressions can be used in the template text to create fields:"
msgstr ""
"Delček lahko vsebuje polja, ki jih je mogoče urejati. Preklapljate jih lahko "
"s pritiskom na &Tab;. Za ustvarjanje polj lahko v besedilu predloge "
"uporabite naslednje izraze:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3593
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name</replaceable>}</userinput> creates a "
"simple, editable field. All subsequent occurrences of the same "
"<replaceable>field_name</replaceable> create fields which mirror the "
"contents of the first during editing."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name</replaceable>}</userinput> ustvari "
"preprosto polje, ki ga je mogoče urejati. Vse naslednje pojavitve istega "
"<replaceable>polje_ime</replaceable> ustvarijo polja, ki zrcalijo vsebino "
"prvega med urejanjem."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3599
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Field names may contain any character except for the closing curly bracket "
"(<userinput>}</userinput>)."
msgstr ""
"Imena polj lahko vsebujejo kateri koli znak, razen desnega zavitega oklepaja "
"(<userinput>}</userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3600
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To insert <userinput>${text}</userinput> literally in a snippet, escape the "
"<userinput>$</userinput> sign with a backslash: <userinput>\\${text}</"
"userinput>. The text will then not be turned into a field. To insert literal "
"backslashes before a field, escape each individual backslash: <userinput>\\\\"
"${field}</userinput>, <userinput>\\\\\\\\${field}</userinput>, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Če želite dobesedno vstaviti <userinput>${text}</userinput> v delček kode, "
"znaku <userinput>$</userinput> dodajte poševnico nazaj: <userinput>\\${text}"
"</userinput>. Besedilo se nato ne bo pretvorilo v polje. Če želite pred "
"polje vstaviti dobesedno poševnico nazaj, uporabite še eno posamezno "
"poševnico nazaj: <userinput>\\\\${field}</userinput>, <userinput>\\\\\\\\"
"${field}</userinput> in tako naprej."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3606
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>${func(<replaceable>other_field1</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>other_field2</replaceable>, ...)}</userinput> creates a field "
"which evaluates a &javascript; function on each edit and is replaced by that "
"function's return value. See the <link linkend=\"snippet-input-library"
"\"><guilabel>Script Library</guilabel></link> tab for more information."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>${func(<replaceable>other_field1</replaceable>, "
"<replaceable>other_field2</replaceable>, ...)}</userinput> ustvari polje, ki "
"ob vsakem urejanju ovrednoti funkcijo &javascript; in ga nadomesti vrnjena "
"vrednost te funkcije. Za več informacij glejte zavihek <link linkend="
"\"snippet-input-library\"><guilabel>Knjižnica skriptov</guilabel></link>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3612
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name=default</replaceable>}</userinput> sets "
"a default value for the field. <replaceable>default</replaceable> is a "
"&javascript; expression. Use quotes (<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name</"
"replaceable>=<replaceable>\"text\"</replaceable>}</userinput>) to specify a "
"fixed string as the default value."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name=default</replaceable>}</userinput> "
"nastavi privzeto vrednost za polje. <replaceable>default</replaceable> je "
"izraz &javascript;. Za določitev fiksnega niza kot privzete vrednosti "
"uporabite narekovaje (<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name</"
"replaceable>=<replaceable>\"text\"</replaceable>}</userinput>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3618
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When using default values (<userinput>${<replaceable>field_name=default</"
"replaceable>}</userinput>), keep in mind that the default value is evaluated "
"immediately when the snippet is inserted into the document, and it is not "
"updated later when fields are changed."
msgstr ""
"Pri uporabi privzetih vrednosti (<userinput>"
"${<replaceable>field_name=default</replaceable>}</userinput>) upoštevajte, "
"da se privzeta vrednost ovrednoti takoj, ko je delček kode vstavljen v "
"dokument, in se kasneje ne posodobi, ko se polja spremenijo."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3621
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can reference other fields in default values if they are defined before "
"the default value that is being evaluated. However, this will only give you "
"access to the default value of these fields."
msgstr ""
"V privzetih vrednostih se lahko sklicujete na druga polja, če so definirana "
"pred privzeto vrednostjo, ki se ocenjuje. Vendar boste s tem imeli dostop le "
"do privzete vrednosti teh polj."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3623
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If no custom default value is defined, the default value is a field's name."
msgstr ""
"Če ni določena nobena privzeta vrednost po meri, je privzeta vrednost ime "
"polja."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3626
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<userinput>${cursor}</userinput> marks the end position of the cursor after "
"everything else was filled in. Inserting text at this position will finish "
"editing. Plus after pressing &Esc; to finish editing, the cursor will jump "
"to this position."
msgstr ""
"<userinput>${cursor}</userinput> označuje končni položaj kazalca po tem, ko "
"je vse ostalo izpolnjeno. Z vstavljanjem besedila na ta položaj se urejanje "
"zaključi. Poleg tega se po pritisku tipke <keycap>&Esc;</keycap> za "
"dokončanje urejanja kazalec premakne na ta položaj."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:3633
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guilabel>Snippet</guilabel> (type <userinput>Script</userinput>)"
msgstr "<guilabel>Delček kode</guilabel> (vrsta <userinput>Skript</userinput>)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3634
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &javascript; code to evaluate for this snippet"
msgstr "Koda &javascript; za ovrednotenje tega koščka"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3635
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this code contains a <userinput>return</userinput> statement, the "
"returned string will be inserted at the current cursor position. You can "
"also use the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-scripting-api"
"\">&kate; scripting API</ulink> to modify the document directly."
msgstr ""
"Če ta koda vsebuje stavek <userinput>return</userinput>, bo vrnjeni niz "
"vstavljen na trenutni položaj kazalca. Za spreminjanje dokumenta lahko "
"uporabite neposredno tudi <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-"
"scripting-api\">&kate; skriptni API</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3638
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Additionally, your code may use functions defined in the <link linkend="
"\"snippet-input-library\"><guilabel>Script Library</guilabel></link> tab, "
"which are shared between all snippets in a repository."
msgstr ""
"Poleg tega lahko vaša koda uporablja funkcije, definirane na zavihku <link "
"linkend=\"snippet-input-library\"><guilabel>Knjižnica skriptov</guilabel></"
"link>, ki si jih delijo vsi delčki kode v repozitoriju."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3645
#, no-c-format
msgid "Script Library"
msgstr "Knjižnica skriptov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3646
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&javascript; helper functions to use in your snippets. These functions are "
"shared between all snippets in a repository."
msgstr ""
"Pomožne funkcije &javascript; za uporabo v vaših delčkih kode. Te funkcije "
"si delijo vsi delčki kode v repozitoriju."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3647
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use the <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting.html#dev-scripting-"
"api\">&kate; scripting API</ulink> to get the selected text, full text, file "
"name, and more by using the appropriate methods of the <userinput>document</"
"userinput> and <userinput>view</userinput> objects. Refer to the scripting "
"API documentation for more information."
msgstr ""
"Z uporabo ustreznih metod objektov <ulink url=\"help:/katepart/dev-scripting."
"html#dev-scripting-api\">&kate; skriptnega API-ja</ulink> lahko pridobite "
"izbrano besedilo, celotno besedilo, ime datoteke in drugo. Za več informacij "
"glejte dokumentacijo skriptnega API-ja."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3651
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When a function is called in a field of a <userinput>Text Template</"
"userinput> snippet, its <emphasis>return</emphasis> value is inserted into "
"the text."
msgstr ""
"Ko je funkcija poklicana v polju delčka kode <userinput>Predloga besedila</"
"userinput>, se njena <emphasis>vrnjena vrednost </emphasis>vstavi v besedilo."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3655
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using functions in <userinput>Text Template</userinput> snippets:"
msgstr ""
"Uporaba funkcij v delčkih kode <userinput>Predloga besedila</userinput>:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3657
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Functions can access the up-to-date contents of all fields through the "
"<userinput>fields</userinput> object: use <userinput>fields.my_field</"
"userinput> or <userinput>fields[\"my_field\"]</userinput>. When using a "
"function as the default value for a field, only fields defined in the text "
"before are available."
msgstr ""
"Funkcije lahko dostopajo do posodobljene vsebine vseh polj prek objekta "
"<userinput>fields</userinput>: uporabite <userinput>fields.my_field</"
"userinput> ali <userinput>fields[\"my_field\"]</userinput>. Ko uporabljate "
"funkcijo kot privzeto vrednost za polje, so na voljo samo polja, definirana "
"v prejšnjem besedilu."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3660
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Fields can be passed as arguments to functions. The field name can be used "
"directly if it is a valid &javascript; identifier and no variable with that "
"name exists. Otherwise use the <userinput>fields</userinput> object: "
"<userinput>${func(field)}</userinput>, <userinput>${func(fields.document)}</"
"userinput>, <userinput>${func(fields[\"my field\"])}</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Polja so lahko posredovana kot argumenti funkcijam. Ime polja se lahko "
"uporabi neposredno, če je veljaven identifikator &javascript; in če že ne "
"obstaja spremenljivka s tem imenom. Sicer uporabite objekt "
"<userinput>fields</userinput>: <userinput>${func(field)}</userinput>, "
"<userinput>${func(fields.document)}</userinput>, <userinput>"
"${func(fields[\"my field\"])}</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3664
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Function fields (e.g. <userinput>${func()}</userinput>) are re-evaluated "
"every time any field's contents are changed. However, this does not apply to "
"function calls in default values: they are only evaluated once when the "
"snippet is inserted into the document."
msgstr ""
"Funkcijska polja (npr. <userinput>${func()}</userinput>) se ponovno "
"ovrednotijo vsakič, ko se spremeni vsebina katerega koli polja. Vendar to ne "
"velja za klice funkcij v privzetih vrednostih: ovrednotijo se le enkrat, ko "
"je delček kode vstavljen v dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3667
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For more complex scripts it may be important to understand that "
"<emphasis>first</emphasis>, the raw snippet is inserted into the document, "
"and <emphasis>then</emphasis> functions are being evaluated. E.g., if a "
"function retrieves the text on the line where the snippet is being inserted, "
"that text will also contain <userinput>${functionCall()}</userinput>. Where "
"this causes complications, consider using a <userinput>Script</userinput>-"
"type snippet, instead."
msgstr ""
"Pri bolj zapletenih skriptih je morda pomembno razumeti, da se "
"<emphasis>najprej</emphasis> v dokument vstavi surovi delček kode, "
"<emphasis>nato</emphasis> pa se ovrednotijo ​​funkcije. Če npr. funkcija "
"pridobi besedilo v vrstici, kamor se vstavlja delček kode, bo to besedilo "
"vsebovalo tudi <userinput>${functionCall()}</userinput>. Kjer to povzroča "
"zaplete, razmislite o uporabi delčka kode vrste <userinput>Skript</"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3673
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To simply wrap the currently selected text into tags, use: <userinput>&lt;"
"strong&gt;${view.selectedText()}&lt;/strong&gt;</userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Če želite trenutno izbrano besedilo preprosto zaviti v oznake, uporabite: "
"<userinput>&lt;strong&gt;${view.selectedText()}&lt;/strong&gt;</userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3674
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Remember that only the <emphasis>return value</emphasis> of a function is "
"inserted in a field."
msgstr ""
"Ne pozabite, da se v polje vstavi samo <emphasis>vrnjena vrednost</emphasis> "
"funkcije."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:3682
#, no-c-format
msgid "Description"
msgstr "Opis"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3683
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"An optional description of what this snippet does. This will be shown in "
"tooltips. The description may contain basic HTML formatting."
msgstr ""
"Neobvezen opis delovanja tega delčka kode. Prikazan bo v opisih orodij. Opis "
"lahko vsebuje osnovno oblikovanje HTML."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:3688
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage example"
msgstr "Primer uporabe"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3689
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following example invokes a script that wraps the selected text, or - if "
"there is no selection - a default text, into tags (Snippet type "
"<userinput>Script</userinput>):"
msgstr ""
"Naslednji primer pokliče skript, ki izbrano besedilo ali – če ni izbora – "
"privzeto besedilo ovije v oznake (tip delčka kode <userinput>Skript</"
"userinput>):"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: plugins.docbook:3692
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"let range = view.hasSelection() ? view.selection() : new Range(view."
"cursorPosition(), view.cursorPosition());\n"
"let innertext = range.isEmpty() ? \"Bold\" : document.text(range);\n"
"document.removeText(range);\n"
"document.insertText(range.start, \"&lt;strong&gt;\" + innertext + \"&lt;/"
"strong&gt;\");"
msgstr ""
"let range = view.hasSelection() ? view.selection() : new Range(view."
"cursorPosition(), view.cursorPosition());\n"
"let innertext = range.isEmpty() ? \"Bold\" : document.text(range);\n"
"document.removeText(range);\n"
"document.insertText(range.start, \"&lt;strong&gt;\" + innertext + \"&lt;/"
"strong&gt;\");"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3703
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using Snippets"
msgstr "Uporaba koškov kode"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:3706
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; Snippets in Action"
msgstr "&kate; Koščki kode v akciji"

#. Tag: phrase
#: plugins.docbook:3709
#, no-c-format
msgid "Accessing &kate; Snippets from a tool view and a drop down menu."
msgstr "Dostop do &kate; Koščki kode iz pogleda orodja in spustnega menija."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3710
#, no-c-format
msgid "Selecting from a list of snippets."
msgstr "Izbira s seznama koščkov kode."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3714
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can call snippets in several ways:"
msgstr "Koščke kode lahko pokličete na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3717
#, no-c-format
msgid "By clicking on the snippet from the tool view."
msgstr "Z izbiro koščka kode v orodnem pogledu."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3718
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using a keyboard shortcut, if you have assigned one."
msgstr "Uporaba bližnjice na tipkovnici, če ste jo dodelili."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3719
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"While writing, you can press <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Space;</"
"keycombo>, which will display all the snippets in a convenient window from "
"which you can choose. This key combination provides functionality similar to "
"code completion."
msgstr ""
"Med pisanjem lahko pritisnete <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl; &Space;</"
"keycombo>, ki prikaže vse izrezke v priročnem oknu, med katerim lahko "
"izbirate. Ta kombinacija tipk zagotavlja funkcionalnost, podobno dokončanju "
"kode."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3725
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the snippet contains variables (besides <literal>${cursor}</literal>) the "
"cursor will automatically go to the first occurrence of a variable and will "
"wait for you to write something. When you are done, you can press &Tab; to "
"move to the next variable, and so on."
msgstr ""
"Če delček vsebuje spremenljivke (poleg <literal>${cursor}</literal>), se bo "
"kazalec samodejno premaknil na prvo pojavitev spremenljivke in počakal, da "
"nekaj napišete. Ko končate, lahko pritisnete &Tab; za pomik na naslednjo "
"spremenljivko itd."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3734
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kate; Snippets was written by Joseph Wenninger."
msgstr "&kate; Izrezke je napisal Joseph Wenninger."

#. Tag: author
#: plugins.docbook:3745
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstname>Pablo</firstname> <surname>Rauzy</surname> <email>r .at. uzy.me</"
"email>"
msgstr ""
"<firstname>Pablo</firstname> <surname>Rauzy</surname> <email>r .at. uzy.me</"
"email>"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3748
#, no-c-format
msgid "Keyboard Macros Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za makre tipkovnice"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3752
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record and play keyboard macros (i.e., keyboard action sequences)."
msgstr ""
"Snemajte in predvajajte makre tipkovnice (tj. zaporedja dejanj tipkovnice)."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3756
#, no-c-format
msgid "Basic usage"
msgstr "Osnovna uporaba"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3759
#, no-c-format
msgid "To start recording a keyboard macro:"
msgstr "Za začetek snemanja makra tipkovnice:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3760
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Record Macro...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makri tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Snemaj makro ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3764
#, no-c-format
msgid "The plugin will record every key presses until you end recording."
msgstr "Vtičnik bo beležil vse pritiske tipk, dokler ne končate snemanja."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3768
#, no-c-format
msgid "To end recording:"
msgstr "Če želite končati snemanje:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3769
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>End Macro Recording</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Končaj snemanje makra</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Shift;<keycap> K</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3773
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin will stop recording key presses and save the sequence as the "
"current macro."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik bo prenehal beležiti pritiske tipk in shranil zaporedje kot trenutni "
"makro."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3777
#, no-c-format
msgid "To cancel recording:"
msgstr "Za preklic snemanja:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3778
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Cancel Macro Recording</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Prekliči snemanje makra</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3782
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin will stop recording key presses but the current macro won't "
"change."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik bo prenehal beležiti pritiske tipk, vendar se trenutni makro ne bo "
"spremenil."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3786
#, no-c-format
msgid "To play the current macro:"
msgstr "Za predvajanje trenutnega makra:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3787
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Play Macro</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo "
"action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Predvajaj makro</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>K </keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3791
#, no-c-format
msgid "The plugin will play the current macro."
msgstr "Vtičnik bo predvajal trenutni makro."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3792
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>kmplay</userinput> command without any arguments will also "
"play the current macro."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz <userinput>kmplay</userinput> brez argumentov bo prav tako predvajal "
"trenutni makro."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3798
#, no-c-format
msgid "Named macros"
msgstr "Imenovani makro"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3800
#, no-c-format
msgid "It is possible to save keyboard macros by giving them a name."
msgstr "Makro tipkovnice lahko shranite tako, da jim daste ime."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3801
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Named macros are persistent between Kate's sessions, they're saved in the "
"<filename>keyboardmacros.json</filename> file in Kate's user data directory "
"(usually <filename>~/.local/share/kate/</filename>)."
msgstr ""
"Imenovani makri so obstojni med sejami Kate, shranjeni so v datoteki "
"<filename>keyboardmacros.json</filename> v imeniku uporabniških podatkov "
"Kate (običajno <filename>~/.local/share/kate/</filename>)."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3804
#, no-c-format
msgid "To save the current macro:"
msgstr "Če želite shraniti trenutni makro:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3805
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Save Current Macro</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap>K</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Shrani trenutni makro</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"(<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Alt;&Shift;<keycap> K</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3809
#, no-c-format
msgid "The plugin will prompt you for a name and save the macro under it."
msgstr "Vtičnik vas bo pozval k imenu in pod njim shranil makro."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3810
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>kmsave <replaceable>name</replaceable></userinput> command "
"will save the current macro under the name <userinput><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz <userinput>kmsave <replaceable>ime</replaceable></userinput> bo shranil "
"trenutni makro pod imenom <userinput><replaceable>ime</replaceable></"
"userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3814
#, no-c-format
msgid "To load a saved macro as the current one:"
msgstr "Če želite naložiti shranjeni makro kot trenutnega:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3815
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Load Named Macro...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Naloži imenovani makro ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3818
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin lists saved macros as items in this submenu, activating an item "
"will load the corresponding macro as the current one."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik navaja shranjene makre kot elemente v tem podmeniju; aktiviranje "
"elementa bo naložilo ustrezni makro kot trenutni."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3819
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>kmload <replaceable>name</replaceable></userinput> command "
"will load the macro saved under the name <userinput><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></userinput> as the current one."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz <userinput>kmload <replaceable>ime</replaceable></userinput> bo naložil "
"makro, shranjen pod imenom <userinput><replaceable>ime</replaceable></"
"userinput> kot trenutni."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3823
#, no-c-format
msgid "To play a saved macro without loading it:"
msgstr "Če želite predvajati shranjeni makro, ne da bi ga naložili:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3824
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Play Named Macro...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Predvajaj imenovani makro ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3827
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin lists saved macros as items in this submenu, activating an item "
"will play the corresponding macro without loading it."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik navaja shranjene makre kot elemente v tem podmeniju; aktiviranje "
"elementa bo predvajalo ustrezni makro brez nalaganja."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3828
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that each saved macros is an action that is part of the current action "
"collection so that a custom shortcut can be assigned to it through the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure Keyboard "
"Shortcuts...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> interface."
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da je vsak shranjeni makro dejanje, ki je del trenutne zbirke "
"dejanj, tako da mu lahko dodelite bližnjico po meri prek "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj bližnjice "
"na tipkovnici ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>vmesnik."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3829
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>kmplay <replaceable>name</replaceable></userinput> command "
"will play the macro saved under the name <userinput><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></userinput> without loading it."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz <userinput>kmplay <replaceable>ime</replaceable></userinput> bo "
"predvajal makro, shranjen pod imenom <userinput><replaceable>ime</"
"replaceable></userinput>, ne da bi ga naložil."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3833
#, no-c-format
msgid "To wipe (i.e., delete) a saved macro:"
msgstr "Za brisanje (tj. brisanje) shranjenega makra:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3834
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Keyboard Macros</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Wipe Named Macro...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Makro tipkovnice</"
"guimenuitem><guimenuitem>Izbriši imenovani makro ...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3837
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The plugin lists saved macros as items in this submenu, activating an item "
"will wipe (i.e., delete) the corresponding macro."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik navaja shranjene makre kot elemente v tem podmeniju; aktiviranje "
"elementa bo izbrisalo (tj. izbrisalo) ustrezni makro."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3838
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <userinput>kmwipe <replaceable>name</replaceable></userinput> command "
"will wipe the macro saved under the name <userinput><replaceable>name</"
"replaceable></userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Ukaz <userinput>kmwipe <replaceable>ime</replaceable></userinput> bo "
"izbrisal makro, shranjen pod imenom <userinput><replaceable>ime</"
"replaceable></userinput>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3842
#, no-c-format
msgid "Tips for commands:"
msgstr "Nasveti za ukaze:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3843
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Note that after the <userinput>km</userinput> prefix, all these commands use "
"a different letter so you can efficiently call them using tab-completion!"
msgstr ""
"Upoštevajte, da za predpono <userinput>km</userinput> vsi ti ukazi "
"uporabljajo drugo črko, tako da jih lahko učinkovito pokličete z dokončanjem "
"tabulatorjev!"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3849
#, no-c-format
msgid "Limitations"
msgstr "Omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3851
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As of now, keyboard macros fail to play properly if some types of GUI "
"widgets are used: QMenu, QuickOpenLineEdit, or TabSwitcherTreeView, for "
"example. I'm not sure why but my first guess would be that these widgets "
"work in a non-standard way regarding keyboard events."
msgstr ""
"Od zdaj se makri tipkovnice ne predvajajo pravilno, če se uporabljajo "
"nekatere vrste gradnikov GUI: QMenu, HitroOdprtoUrejanjeVrstice ali "
"DrevesniPogledPreklopnikaZavihkov, na primer. Ne vem, zakaj, ampak moja prva "
"domneva bi bila, da ti pripomočki glede dogodkov na tipkovnici delujejo na "
"nestandarden način."

#. Tag: author
#: plugins.docbook:3862
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<firstname>Ömer</firstname> <othername>Faruk</othername> <surname>ORUÇ</"
"surname>"
msgstr ""
"<firstname>Ömer</firstname> <othername>Faruk</othername> <surname>ORUÇ</"
"surname>"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3866
#, no-c-format
msgid "SQL Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik SQL"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3871
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The Structured Query Language (SQL) is a specialized language for updating, "
"deleting, and requesting information from databases."
msgstr ""
"Structured Query Language (SQL) je specializiran jezik za posodabljanje, "
"brisanje in zahtevanje informacij iz baz podatkov."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3874
#, no-c-format
msgid "The &kate; SQL Plugin allows you to:"
msgstr "&kate; Vtičnik SQL vam omogoča, da:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3877
#, no-c-format
msgid "Create a database"
msgstr "Ustvari bazo podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3878
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connect to existing databases"
msgstr "Povežite se z obstoječimi zbirkami podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3879
#, no-c-format
msgid "Insert and delete data in the database"
msgstr "Vnašanje in brisanje podatkov v bazi podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3880
#, no-c-format
msgid "Execute queries"
msgstr "Izvedite poizvedbe"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3881
#, no-c-format
msgid "Display results in a table"
msgstr "Prikaz rezultatov v tabeli"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3887
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connecting to a Database"
msgstr "Povezovanje z bazo podatkov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3889
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Select <guibutton>Add Connection</guibutton> from the <guimenu>SQL</guimenu> "
"menu or toolbar, and then select the &Qt; database driver you want to use "
"(including QSQLITE, QMYSQL3, QMYSQL, QODBC3, QODBC, QPSQL7, and QPSQL). If "
"you can't see the desired driver, you need to install it. Then, press "
"<guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"V meniju ali orodni vrstici <guimenu>SQL</guimenu> izberite <guibutton>Dodaj "
"povezavo</guibutton> in nato izberite &Qt; gonilnik baze podatkov, ki ga "
"želite uporabiti (vključno s QSQLITE, QMYSQL3, QMYSQL, QODBC3, QODBC, QPSQL7 "
"in QPSQL). Če ne vidite želenega gonilnika, ga morate namestiti. Nato "
"pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3895
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If the database you selected uses a file, simply indicate the database's "
"location and press the <guibutton>Next</guibutton> button. If it requires "
"connecting to a server, you must enter the hostname of the server, your "
"username and password, and any other information that particular driver may "
"require. Then press <guibutton>Next</guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Če zbirka podatkov, ki ste jo izbrali, uporablja datoteko, preprosto "
"označite lokacijo baze podatkov in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>. Če zahteva povezavo s strežnikom, morate vnesti ime gostitelja "
"strežnika, svoje uporabniško ime in geslo ter vse druge informacije, ki jih "
"morda zahteva določen gonilnik. Nato pritisnite <guibutton>Naprej</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3901
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Finally, give a name to your connection, and press <guibutton>Finish</"
"guibutton>."
msgstr ""
"Nazadnje poimenujte svojo povezavo in pritisnite <guibutton>Dokončaj</"
"guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3906
#, no-c-format
msgid "Running Queries"
msgstr "Izvajanje poizvedb"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3909
#, no-c-format
msgid "INSERT/DELETE/UPDATE"
msgstr "VSTAVI/IZBRIŠI/POSODOBI"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3911
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can insert, delete, and update data using the SQL plugin just as you "
"would from the command line or from within a program. Simply enter a query "
"and press the <guibutton>Run query</guibutton> button in the toolbar or use "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run query</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>)."
msgstr ""
"Podatke lahko vstavljate, brišete in posodabljate z uporabo vtičnika SQL "
"tako kot v ukazni vrstici ali znotraj programa. Preprosto vnesite poizvedbo "
"in pritisnite gumb <guibutton>Zaženi poizvedbo</guibutton> v orodni vrstici "
"ali uporabite <menuchoice><guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaženi "
"poizvedbo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> (<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;"
"<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo>)."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3918
#, no-c-format
msgid "Some Example Queries"
msgstr "Nekaj primerov poizvedb"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: plugins.docbook:3923
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"INSERT INTO <replaceable>table_name</replaceable> (\"<replaceable>feature1</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature2</replaceable>\", "
"\"<replaceable>feature3</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature4</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature5</replaceable>\")\n"
"VALUES (\"<replaceable>value1</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>value2</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>value3</replaceable>\", "
"\"<replaceable>value4</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>value5</replaceable>"
"\" )"
msgstr ""
"INSERT INTO <replaceable>table_name</replaceable> (\"<replaceable>feature1</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature2</replaceable>\", "
"\"<replaceable>feature3</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature4</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature5</replaceable>\")\n"
"VREDNOSTI (\"<replaceable>vrednost1</replaceable>\", "
"\"<replaceable>vrednost2</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>vrednost3</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>vrednost4</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable> "
"vrednost5</replaceable>\" )"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: plugins.docbook:3928
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"DELETE FROM <replaceable>table_name</replaceable> WHERE name = "
"\"<replaceable>text</replaceable>\""
msgstr ""
"ODSTRANI IZ <replaceable>table_name</replaceable> WHERE name = "
"\"<replaceable>besedilo</replaceable>\""

#. Tag: programlisting
#: plugins.docbook:3933
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"UPDATE <replaceable>table_name</replaceable> SET \"<replaceable>feature1</"
"replaceable>\" = \"<replaceable>text</replaceable>\", "
"\"<replaceable>feature2</replaceable>\" = \"<replaceable>text</replaceable>"
"\", \"<replaceable>feature3</replaceable>\" = \"<replaceable>text</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature4</replaceable>\" = "
"\"<replaceable>text</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature5</replaceable>\" "
"= \"<replaceable>text</replaceable>\""
msgstr ""
"POSODOBITE <replaceable>table_name</replaceable> SET "
"\"<replaceable>feature1</replaceable>\" = \"<replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature2</replaceable>\" = "
"\"<replaceable>besedilo</replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature3</"
"replaceable>\" = \"<replaceable>besedilo</replaceable>\", "
"\"<replaceable>feature4</replaceable>\" = \"<replaceable>besedilo</"
"replaceable>\", \"<replaceable>feature5</replaceable>\" = "
"\"<replaceable>besedilo</replaceable>\""

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3942
#, no-c-format
msgid "SELECT"
msgstr "IZBERI"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3944
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"After running a <command>SELECT</command> query, you can view the results as "
"a table that will appear in the <guilabel>SQL Data Output</guilabel> tool "
"view at the bottom of &kate;, or as text in the <guilabel>SQL Text Output</"
"guilabel>. If there is an error, you can see it in the text output."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete poizvedbo <command>IZBERI</command>, si lahko ogledate rezultate "
"kot tabelo, ki bo prikazana v pogledu orodja <guilabel>Izpis podatkov SQL</"
"guilabel> na dnu &kate;, ali kot besedilo v <guilabel>Izpis besedila SQL</"
"guilabel>. Če pride do napake, jo lahko vidite v izpisu besedila."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3950
#, no-c-format
msgid "Example <command>SELECT</command> Query"
msgstr "Primer poizvedbe <command>IZBERI</command>"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: plugins.docbook:3951
#, no-c-format
msgid "SELECT * FROM <replaceable>table_name</replaceable>"
msgstr "IZBERI * OD <replaceable>ime_tabele</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3954
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"In the <guilabel>SQL Data Output</guilabel> tool view, there are several "
"buttons:"
msgstr ""
"V pogledu orodja <guilabel>Izpis podatkov SQL</guilabel> je več gumbov:"

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3959
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize columns to contents"
msgstr "Spremenite velikost stolpcev glede na vsebino"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3960
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changes the size of columns to fit their contents."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost stolpcev, da ustreza njihovi vsebini."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3964
#, no-c-format
msgid "Resize rows to contents"
msgstr "Spremenite velikost vrstic na vsebino"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3965
#, no-c-format
msgid "Changes the size of rows to fit their contents."
msgstr "Spremeni velikost vrstic, da se prilegajo njihovi vsebini."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3969
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy"
msgstr "Kopiraj"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3970
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Selects all of the table contents and copies it to the clipboard buffer."
msgstr "Izbere celotno vsebino tabele in jo kopira v medpomnilnik odložišča."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3974
#, no-c-format
msgid "Export"
msgstr "Izvozi"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3975
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Exports all of the table contents to a file, the clipboard, or the current "
"document in the Comma Separated Values format."
msgstr ""
"Izvozi vso vsebino tabele v datoteko, odložišče ali trenutni dokument v "
"obliki zapisa vrednosti, ločenih z vejico."

#. Tag: guibutton
#: plugins.docbook:3980
#, no-c-format
msgid "Clear"
msgstr "Počisti"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3981
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes everything from the table view."
msgstr "Odstrani vse iz pogleda tabele."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3988
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can now change the colors displayed in the table in the <guilabel>SQL</"
"guilabel> section of <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Configure &kate;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Zdaj lahko spremenite prikazane barve v tabeli v razdelku <guilabel>SQL</"
"guilabel> v <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</"
"guimenu><guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kate;...</guimenuitem> </menuchoice> ."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:3996
#, no-c-format
msgid "Browsing"
msgstr "Brskanje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:3998
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can browse your database using the <guilabel>Database schema</guilabel> "
"browser tool view on the left. The information displayed varies depending on "
"which database driver you are using."
msgstr ""
"Po svoji zbirki podatkov lahko brskate s pogledom orodij brskalnika "
"<guilabel>Shema baze podatkov</guilabel> na levi strani. Prikazane "
"informacije se razlikujejo glede na gonilnik baze podatkov, ki ga "
"uporabljate."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4002
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To refresh this list, right-click anywhere in the tool view and select "
"<guimenuitem>Refresh</guimenuitem>. To generate a query on any entry in the "
"list, right-click on an entry, select <guisubmenu>Generate</guisubmenu>, and "
"select the query type (<guimenuitem>SELECT</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>UPDATE</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>INSERT</guimenuitem>, or "
"<guimenuitem>DELETE</guimenuitem>) from the submenu that appears."
msgstr ""
"Če želite osvežiti ta seznam, z desno tipko miške kliknite kjer koli v "
"orodnem pogledu in izberite <guimenuitem>Osveži</guimenuitem>. Če želite "
"ustvariti poizvedbo za kateri koli vnos na seznamu, z desno miškino tipko "
"kliknite vnos, izberite <guisubmenu>Ustvari</guisubmenu> in izberite vrsto "
"poizvedbe (<guimenuitem>IZBERI</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>POSODOBITEV</"
"guimenuitem >, <guimenuitem>VSTAVI</guimenuitem> ali <guimenuitem>IZBRIŠI</"
"guimenuitem>) v podmeniju, ki se prikaže."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4016
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Add connection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodaj povezavo ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4019
#, no-c-format
msgid "Adds a new connection using any database driver."
msgstr "Doda novo povezavo s katerim koli gonilnikom baze podatkov."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4025
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Remove connection</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Odstrani povezavo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4028
#, no-c-format
msgid "Removes the selected connection."
msgstr "Odstrani izbrano povezavo."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4034
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Edit connection...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Uredi povezavo ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4037
#, no-c-format
msgid "Edits the current connection's settings."
msgstr "Uredi nastavitve trenutne povezave."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:4043
#, no-c-format
msgid "Connections"
msgstr "Povezave"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4044
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All database connections you have created are listed between the "
"<guimenuitem>Edit connection</guimenuitem> and <guimenuitem>Run query</"
"guimenuitem> menu items. Select one to run queries or make modifications to "
"it."
msgstr ""
"Vse povezave baze podatkov, ki ste jih ustvarili, so navedene med menijskima "
"elementoma <guimenuitem>Uredi povezavo</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>Zaženi "
"poizvedbo</guimenuitem>. Izberite enega, da zaženete poizvedbe ali ga "
"spremenite."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4052
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Run query</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut><keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>E</keycap></keycombo></"
"shortcut> <guimenu>SQL</guimenu><guimenuitem>Zaženi poizvedbo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4056
#, no-c-format
msgid "Runs your query."
msgstr "Zažene vašo poizvedbo."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4067
#, no-c-format
msgid "The SQL Plugin was written by Marco Mentasti."
msgstr "Vtičnik SQL je napisal Marco Mentasti."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4068
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Special thanks to Google Code-In 2011 participant Ömer Faruk ORUÇ for "
"writing much of this section."
msgstr ""
"Posebna zahvala udeležencu Google Code-In 2011 Ömerju Faruku ORUÇ za pisanje "
"večjega dela tega razdelka."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4077
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbol Viewer Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za pregledovalnik simbolov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4082
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"It allows developers to view symbols (functions, macros and structures) from "
"source code."
msgstr ""
"Razvijalcem omogoča ogled simbolov (funkcij, makrov in struktur) iz izvorne "
"kode."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4083
#, no-c-format
msgid "By clicking the parsed information you can easily browse the code."
msgstr "S klikom na razčlenjene informacije lahko preprosto brskate po kodi."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4084
#, no-c-format
msgid "At the moment the following languages are supported:"
msgstr "Trenutno so podprti naslednji jeziki:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4085
#, no-c-format
msgid "C/C++, &Java;, Perl, PHP, Python, Ruby, XSLT, Tcl/Tk, Fortran"
msgstr "C/C++, &Java;, Perl, PHP, Python, Ruby, XSLT, Tcl/Tk, Fortran"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4087
#, no-c-format
msgid "Feature list:"
msgstr "Seznam funkcij:"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:4089
#, no-c-format
msgid "List/Tree mode"
msgstr "Način seznama/drevesa"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:4090
#, no-c-format
msgid "Enable/disable sorting"
msgstr "Omogoči/onemogoči razvrščanje"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:4091
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide/Show Functions Parameters"
msgstr "Skrij/prikaži parametre funkcij"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:4092
#, no-c-format
msgid "Expand/collapse tree mode"
msgstr "Razširi/strni drevesni način"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:4093
#, no-c-format
msgid "Auto-update on document change"
msgstr "Samodejno posodabljanje ob spremembi dokumenta"

#. Tag: member
#: plugins.docbook:4094
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Code parsing is based on the Syntax-Highlighting framework from &kde-"
"frameworks;"
msgstr ""
"Razčlenjevanje kode temelji na ogrodju Označevanje sintakse iz &kde-"
"frameworks;"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4104
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>\\</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>View</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Symbol List</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>\\</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Pogled</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži Seznam simbolov</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Toggle the display of &kate;'s Symbol List displaying Functions, Macros and "
"Structures of the source code in the active document."
msgstr ""
"Preklopi prikaz seznama simbolov &kate;, ki prikazuje funkcije, makre in "
"strukture izvorne kode v aktivnem dokumentu."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:4126
#, no-c-format
msgid "Symbol Viewer"
msgstr "Pregledovalnik simbolov"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4129
#, no-c-format
msgid "Choose the default parser options"
msgstr "Izberite privzete možnosti razčlenjevalnika"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4139
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal Tool View Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za ogled terminalskega orodja"

#. Tag: primary
#: plugins.docbook:4141
#, no-c-format
msgid "Terminal emulator"
msgstr "Terminalski emulator"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4141
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The built in Terminal Emulator is a copy of the &kde; &konsole; terminal "
"application, for your convenience. It is available from the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Show Terminal Panel</guimenuitem></menuchoice> menu item and "
"will get the focus whenever displayed. Additionally, if the <link linkend="
"\"konsole-config\">Automatically synchronize the terminal with the current "
"document when possible</link> option is enabled, it will change to the "
"directory of the current document if possible when it is displayed, or when "
"the current document changes."
msgstr ""
"Vgrajeni terminalski emulator je kopija &kde; &konsole; terminalsko "
"aplikacijo, za vaše udobje. Na voljo je v meniju "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodij</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži terminalsko ploščo</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in bo "
"vedno, ko bo prikazan, dobil fokus. Poleg tega, če je omogočena možnost "
"<link linkend=\"konsole-config\">Samodejno sinhroniziraj terminal s "
"trenutnim dokumentom, ko je to mogoče</link>, se bo po možnosti spremenil v "
"imenik trenutnega dokumenta, ko bo prikazan, ali ko se trenutni dokument "
"spremeni."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The default location in the &kate; window is at the bottom, below the "
"editing area."
msgstr ""
"Privzeta lokacija v datoteki &kate; okno je na dnu, pod območjem za urejanje."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4156
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the &konsole; using its &RMB; menu, for more information, "
"see the <ulink url=\"help:/konsole/index.html\">&konsole; manual</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Konfigurirate lahko &konsole; z uporabo &RMB; za več informacij glejte "
"<ulink url=\"help:/konsole/index.html\">&konsole; priročnik</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4159
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The built-in terminal emulator is provided by the Terminal Tool View plugin."
msgstr ""
"Vgrajen terminalski emulator zagotavlja vtičnik Pogled terminalskega orodja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4167
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>View</guimenu><guisubmenu>Tool Views</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Show "
"Terminal Panel</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Pogled</guimenu><guisubmenu>Pogledi orodja</guisubmenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Pokaži terminalsko ploščo</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4172
#, no-c-format
msgid "Toggles the display of the built-in terminal emulator."
msgstr "Preklopi prikaz vgrajenega terminalskega emulatorja."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4173
#, no-c-format
msgid "When activated for the first time, the terminal will be created."
msgstr "Ob prvi aktivaciji bo terminal ustvarjen."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4174
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When the terminal emulator is displayed, it will get the focus, so that you "
"can start typing in commands immediately. If the <link linkend=\"konsole-"
"config\">Automatically synchronize the terminal with the current document "
"when possible</link> option is enabled in the <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> "
"page of the <link linkend=\"config-dialog\">Main configuration dialog</link> "
"the shell session will change to the directory of the active document, if it "
"is a local file."
msgstr ""
"Ko se prikaže terminalski emulator, bo dobil fokus, tako da lahko takoj "
"začnete vnašati ukaze. Če je možnost <link linkend=\"konsole-config"
"\">Samodejno sinhroniziraj terminal s trenutnim dokumentom, ko je to mogoče</"
"link> omogočena na strani <guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> v <link linkend="
"\"config-dialog\">Glavno konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno</link> se bo "
"lupinska seja spremenila v imenik aktivnega dokumenta, če gre za lokalno "
"datoteko."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4185
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>Tools</guimenu><guimenuitem>Pipe to Terminal</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu><guimenuitem>Cev do terminala</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4187
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Feed the currently selected text into the built-in terminal emulator. No "
"newline is added after the text."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite trenutno izbrano besedilo v vgrajen terminalski emulator. Za "
"besedilom se ne doda nova vrstica."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Synchronize Terminal with Current "
"Document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Sinhroniziraj terminal s trenutnim "
"dokumentom</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4196
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will cause the built-in Terminal to <command>cd</command> into the "
"directory of the active document."
msgstr ""
"To bo povzročilo, da bo vgrajeni terminal <command>cd</command> v imenik "
"aktivnega dokumenta."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4199
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Alternatively, you can configure &kate; to always keep the terminal in sync "
"with the current document. See <xref linkend=\"konsole-config\"/> for more "
"information."
msgstr ""
"Lahko pa konfigurirate &kate; da bo terminal vedno sinhroniziran s trenutnim "
"dokumentom. Za več informacij glejte <xref linkend=\"konsole-config\"/>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4206
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Run Current Document</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zaženi trenutni dokument</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4210
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Run the current document in &konsole;. Only the local documents can be run. "
"&kate; will show a warning before running document because this action can "
"be a serious security threat."
msgstr ""
"Zaženi trenutni dokument v &konsole;. Izvajati je mogoče samo lokalne "
"dokumente. &kate; bo pred zagonom dokumenta prikazal opozorilo, ker je to "
"dejanje lahko resna varnostna grožnja."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4217
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Focus/Defocus Terminal Panel</"
"guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Izostritev/defokusiranje terminalske "
"plošče</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4222
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Switch the focus from the current document to the terminal and vice versa."
msgstr "Preklopite fokus s trenutnega dokumenta na terminal in obratno."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4233
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can configure the Terminal Tool View plugin on the <guilabel>Terminal</"
"guilabel> page of the <link linkend=\"configuring-kate\">configuration "
"dialog</link>."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik Pogled terminalskega orodja lahko konfigurirate na strani "
"<guilabel>Terminal</guilabel> v <link linkend=\"configuring-kate"
"\">konfiguracijskem pogovornem oknu</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4237
#, no-c-format
msgid "The following options are available:"
msgstr "Na voljo so naslednje možnosti:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:4242
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Automatically synchronize the terminal with the current document when "
"possible"
msgstr ""
"Samodejno sinhronizirajte terminal s trenutnim dokumentom, ko je to mogoče"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4243
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will cause the built-in terminal to <command>cd</command> into the "
"directory of the active document when launched and when a new document gets "
"the focus. If not enabled, you have to do all your navigation in the "
"terminal on your own."
msgstr ""
"To bo povzročilo, da bo vgrajeni terminal <command>cd</command> v imenik "
"aktivnega dokumenta, ko ga zaženete in ko nov dokument dobi fokus. Če ni "
"omogočeno, morate vso svojo navigacijo v terminalu izvajati sami."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:4251
#, no-c-format
msgid "Set EDITOR environment variable to 'kate -b'"
msgstr "Spremenljivko okolja UREJEVALNIK nastavite na 'kate -b'"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4252
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This sets the <envar>EDITOR</envar> environment variable so programs run in "
"the built-in terminal that automatically open a file in an editor will open "
"them in &kate; instead of the default editor configured in your shell. You "
"will not be able to continue using the terminal until you have closed the "
"file in &kate;, so the calling program is aware you have finished editing "
"the file."
msgstr ""
"To nastavi spremenljivko okolja <envar>UREJEVALNIK</envar>, tako da se bodo "
"programi, ki se izvajajo v vgrajenem terminalu in samodejno odprejo datoteko "
"v urejevalniku, odprli v &kate; namesto privzetega urejevalnika, "
"konfiguriranega v lupini. Ne boste mogli nadaljevati z uporabo terminala, "
"dokler ne zaprete datoteke v &kate;, tako da klicni program ve, da ste "
"končali z urejanjem datoteke."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:4260
#, no-c-format
msgid "Hide &konsole; on pressing 'Esc'"
msgstr "Skrij &konsole; ob pritisku na 'Esc'"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4261
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This allows closing the built-in terminal by pressing the &Esc; key. May "
"cause issues with terminal applications that use &Esc; key, &eg; "
"<application>vim</application>. Add such applications in the text input box "
"below. The items in the list should be separated with comma."
msgstr ""
"To omogoča zapiranje vgrajenega terminala s pritiskom na &Esc; ključ. Lahko "
"povzroči težave s terminalskimi aplikacijami, ki uporabljajo &Esc; ključ, "
"&eg; <application>vim</application>. Dodajte takšne aplikacije v spodnje "
"polje za vnos besedila. Postavke na seznamu naj bodo ločene z vejico."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4273
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Filter Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za filter besedila"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4276
#, no-c-format
msgid "Using the Text Filter Plugin"
msgstr "Uporaba vtičnika Text Filter"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4278
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can use this plugin to process selected text using terminal commands. "
"The selection will be used as input for the command, and the output will "
"either replace the selection or be copied to the clipboard, depending on the "
"user's preference."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik lahko uporabite za obdelavo izbranega besedila s terminalskimi "
"ukazi. Izbor bo uporabljen kot vhod za ukaz, rezultat pa bo zamenjal izbor "
"ali kopiral v odložišče, odvisno od uporabnikovih preferenc."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4284
#, no-c-format
msgid "Examples:"
msgstr "Primeri:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>less /etc/fstab</command> - paste the contents of this file or copy "
"it to the clipboard"
msgstr ""
"<command>less /etc/fstab</command> - prilepite vsebino te datoteke ali jo "
"kopirajte v odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4288
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>wc</command> - count lines, words and characters of the selection "
"and paste this into the document or copy it to the clipboard"
msgstr ""
"<command>wc</command> - preštejte vrstice, besede in znake izbora in to "
"prilepite v dokument ali kopirajte v odložišče"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4292
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<command>sort</command> - sort lines of the selection and paste the result "
"into the document or copy it to the clipboard"
msgstr ""
"<command>razvrsti</command> - razvrsti vrstice izbora in prilepi rezultat v "
"dokument ali ga kopiraj v odložišče"

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4306
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>\\</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Tools</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filter Text</guisubmenu>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>\\</keycap></keycombo> </"
"shortcut> <guimenu>Orodja</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Filtriraj besedilo</"
"guisubmenu>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4315
#, no-c-format
msgid "<action>Opens</action> the Text Filter dialog:"
msgstr "<action>Odpre</action> pogovorno okno besedilnega filtra:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: plugins.docbook:4318
#, no-c-format
msgid "Text Filter dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno filtra besedila"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4324
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Enter the shell command into the combobox or select a previous command from "
"the history."
msgstr ""
"Vnesite ukaz lupine v kombinirano polje ali izberite prejšnji ukaz iz "
"zgodovine."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:4329
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy the result instead of pasting it"
msgstr "Kopirajte rezultat, namesto da ga prilepite"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4331
#, no-c-format
msgid "Copy the result to clipboard leaving a document unchanged."
msgstr "Kopirajte rezultat v odložišče, tako da ostane dokument nespremenjen."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: plugins.docbook:4336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Merge STDOUT and STDERR"
msgstr "Združi STDOUT in STDERR"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4338
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If checked, an output from STDOUT and STDERR will be merged and no errors "
"will be reported. Otherwise, STDERR will be displayed as a passive message."
msgstr ""
"Če je označeno, bo izhod iz STDOUT in STDERR združen in napake ne bodo "
"sporočene. V nasprotnem primeru bo STDERR prikazan kot pasivno sporočilo."

#. Tag: author
#: plugins.docbook:4358 plugins.docbook:4420
#, no-c-format
msgid "&Daniel.Naber; &Daniel.Naber.mail;"
msgstr "&Daniel.Naber; &Daniel.Naber.mail;"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4363
#, no-c-format
msgid "&XML; Validation"
msgstr "&XML; Validacija"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4365
#, no-c-format
msgid "This plugin checks &XML; files for validity and being well-formed."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik preverja &XML; datoteke za veljavnost in dobro oblikovanost."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin checks the current file. A list of warnings and errors will "
"appear at the bottom of &kate;'s main window. You can click on an error "
"message to jump to the corresponding place in the file. If the file has a "
"<quote>DOCTYPE</quote> the DTD given with this doctype will be used to check "
"the file for validity. The DTD is expected at a position relative to the "
"current file, &eg; if the doctype refers to <quote>DTD/xhtml1-transitional."
"dtd</quote> and the file is <filename>/home/peter/test.xml</filename> the "
"DTD is expected to be located at <filename>/home/peter/DTD/xhtml1-"
"transitional.dtd</filename>. However, remote DTDs specified via http are "
"supported."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik preveri trenutno datoteko. Na dnu glavnega okna &kate; se bo "
"pojavil seznam opozoril in napak. Lahko kliknete na sporočilo o napaki, da "
"skočite na ustrezno mesto v datoteki. Če ima datoteka <quote>DOCTYPE</"
"quote>, bo DTD, podan s tem tipom dokumenta, uporabljen za preverjanje "
"veljavnosti datoteke. DTD se pričakuje na položaju glede na trenutno "
"datoteko, &eg; če se doctype nanaša na <quote>DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd</"
"quote> in je datoteka <filename>/home/peter/test.xml</filename>, naj bi se "
"DTD nahajal na <filename>/ home/peter/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd</"
"filename>. Vendar pa so podprti oddaljeni DTD-ji, določeni prek http."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4375
#, no-c-format
msgid "If the file has no doctype it will be checked for being well-formed."
msgstr ""
"Če datoteka nima tipa dokumenta, bo preverjeno, ali je pravilno oblikovana."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4377
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To learn more about &XML; check out the <ulink url=\"https://www.w3.org/XML/"
"\"> official W3C &XML; pages</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Če želite izvedeti več o &XML; preverite <ulink url=\"https://www.w3.org/XML/"
"\"> uradni W3C &XML; strani</ulink>."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4379
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Internally this plugin calls the external command <command>xmllint</"
"command>, which is part of libxml2. If this command is not correctly "
"installed on your system, the plugin will not work."
msgstr ""
"Interno ta vtičnik kliče zunanji ukaz <command>xmllint</command>, ki je del "
"libxml2. Če ta ukaz ni pravilno nameščen v vašem sistemu, vtičnik ne bo "
"deloval."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4383
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To load this plugin open &kate;'s configuration dialog under "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kate;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then select <guilabel>&XML; Validation</guilabel> "
"which will appear in the <guilabel>Application</guilabel> / "
"<guilabel>Plugins</guilabel> section and close the dialog."
msgstr ""
"Če želite naložiti ta vtičnik, odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno &kate; "
"pod <menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj "
"&kate;...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Nato izberite <guilabel>&XML; "
"Preverjanje</guilabel>, ki se prikaže v razdelku <guilabel>Aplikacija</"
"guilabel> / <guilabel>Vtičniki</guilabel> in zapre pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4395
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Validate &XML;</guimenuitem>"
msgstr "<guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Potrdi &XML;</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4400
#, no-c-format
msgid "This will start the check, as described above."
msgstr "S tem se bo začelo preverjanje, kot je opisano zgoraj."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4408
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; Plugin <quote>&XML; Validation</quote> copyright 2002 &Daniel.Naber; "
"&Daniel.Naber.mail;."
msgstr ""
"&kate; Vtičnik <quote>&XML; Preverjanje</quote> avtorske pravice 2002 "
"&Daniel.Naber; &Daniel.Naber.mail;."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4412
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation copyright 2002 &Daniel.Naber;"
msgstr "Avtorske pravice za dokumentacijo 2002 &Daniel.Naber;"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4424
#, no-c-format
msgid "&XML; Completion"
msgstr "&XML; Dokončanje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4426
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This plugin gives hints about what is allowed at a certain position in an "
"&XML; file, according to the file's DTD. It will list possible elements, "
"attributes, attribute values or entities, depending on the cursor position "
"(&eg; all entities are listed if the character on the left of the cursor is "
"<quote>&amp;</quote>). It's also possible to close the nearest open tag on "
"the left."
msgstr ""
"Ta vtičnik daje namige o tem, kaj je dovoljeno na določenem mestu v &XML; "
"glede na DTD datoteke. Navede možne elemente, atribute, vrednosti atributov "
"ali entitete, odvisno od položaja kazalca (&eg; vse entitete so navedene, če "
"je znak na levi strani kazalca <quote>&amp;</quote>). Možno je tudi zapreti "
"najbližjo odprto oznako na levi."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4433
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The <acronym>DTD</acronym> must exist in &XML; format, as produced by the "
"Perl program <command>dtdparse</command>. We will call a DTD in this format "
"<quote>meta DTD</quote>. Some meta DTDs are supplied. They are installed in "
"<filename class=\"directory\">katexmltools/</filename> in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation </"
"option></userinput>, which is also the default folder when you choose "
"<guimenuitem>Assign Meta DTD...</guimenuitem>. To produce your own meta "
"DTDs, get <command>dtdparse</command> from <ulink url=\"http://dtdparse."
"sourceforge.net\">http://dtdparse.sourceforge.net</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"<acronym>DTD</acronym> mora obstajati v &XML; obliki, kot jo ustvari program "
"Perl <command>dtdparse</command>. DTD v tej obliki bomo imenovali "
"<quote>meta DTD</quote>. Priloženih je nekaj meta DTD. Nameščeni so v "
"<filename class=\"directory\">katexmltools/</filename> v "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation </"
"option></userinput>, ki je tudi privzeta mapa, ko izberete "
"<guimenuitem>Dodeli meta DTD ...</guimenuitem>. Če želite ustvariti lastne "
"meta DTD-je, pridobite <command>dtdparse</command> iz <ulink url=\"http://"
"dtdparse.sourceforge.net\">http://dtdparse.sourceforge.net</ulink>."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4444
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Use"
msgstr "Kako uporabiti"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4446
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Start &kate; and open the configuration dialog under "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Configure &kate;...</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Then select <guilabel>&XML; Completion</guilabel> "
"which will appear in the <menuchoice><guimenu>Application</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Plugins</guimenuitem></menuchoice> page and close the dialog. "
"After that, select <menuchoice><guimenu>&XML;</guimenu><guimenuitem>Assign "
"Meta DTD...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. If your document contains no "
"<quote>DOCTYPE</quote> or the doctype is unknown, you will have to select a "
"meta DTD from the file system. Otherwise the meta DTD that matches the "
"current document's DOCTYPE will be loaded automatically."
msgstr ""
"Zaženi &kate; in odprite konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno pod "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj &kate;..."
"</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Nato izberite <guilabel>&XML; Dokončanje</"
"guilabel>, ki se prikaže na strani <menuchoice><guimenu>Aplikacija</guimenu> "
"<guimenuitem>Vtičniki</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in zapre pogovorno okno. Po "
"tem izberite <menuchoice><guimenu>&XML;</guimenu><guimenuitem>Dodeli meta "
"DTD ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>. Če vaš dokument ne vsebuje "
"<quote>DOCTYPE</quote> ali je tip dokumenta neznan, boste morali izbrati "
"meta DTD iz datotečnega sistema. V nasprotnem primeru se bo meta DTD, ki se "
"ujema z DOCTYPE trenutnega dokumenta, samodejno naložil."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4456
#, no-c-format
msgid "You can now use the plugin while typing your text:"
msgstr "Zdaj lahko uporabljate vtičnik med vnašanjem besedila:"

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:4461
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>&lt;</keycap> (less than key)"
msgstr "<keycap>&lt;</keycap> (manj kot tipka)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4462
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will trigger a list of possible elements unless the cursor is inside a "
"tag already. Note that you currently cannot use this to insert the top level "
"element (&eg; <quote>&lt;html&gt;</quote>)."
msgstr ""
"To bo sprožilo seznam možnih elementov, razen če je kazalec že znotraj "
"oznake. Upoštevajte, da tega trenutno ne morete uporabiti za vstavljanje "
"elementa najvišje ravni (&eg; <quote>&lt;html&gt;</quote>)."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:4468
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>&lt;</keycap><keycap>/</keycap>(less than key + slash)"
msgstr "<keycap>&lt;</keycap><keycap>/</keycap>(manj kot tipka + poševnica)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4469
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Entering these characters will offer to close the current element (nearest "
"open one to the left of the cursor). Press &Enter; to accept the suggestion. "
"Unlike the <guimenuitem>Close Element</guimenuitem> menu item, this works "
"only with a DTD assigned."
msgstr ""
"Vnos teh znakov bo ponudil zapiranje trenutnega elementa (najbližji odprt "
"levo od kazalca). Pritisnite &Enter; sprejeti predlog. Za razliko od "
"menijske postavke <guimenuitem>Zapri element</guimenuitem>, ta deluje samo z "
"dodeljenim DTD."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:4476
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>\"</keycap> (quote key)"
msgstr "<keycap>\"</keycap> (ključ narekovaja)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4477
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The quote key will trigger a list of possible attribute values (if there are "
"any) if you are inside a tag."
msgstr ""
"Ključ narekovaja bo sprožil seznam možnih vrednosti atributov (če "
"obstajajo), če ste znotraj oznake."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:4482
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>&nbsp;</keycap> (space key)"
msgstr "<keycap>&nbsp;</keycap> (preslednica)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4483
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This key will trigger a list of possible attributes for the current element "
"if you are inside a tag."
msgstr ""
"Ta ključ bo sprožil seznam možnih atributov za trenutni element, če ste "
"znotraj oznake."

#. Tag: term
#: plugins.docbook:4489
#, no-c-format
msgid "<keycap>&amp;</keycap> (ampersand key)"
msgstr "<keycap>&amp;</keycap> (tipka ampersand)"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4490
#, no-c-format
msgid "This key will trigger a list of named entities."
msgstr "Ta ključ bo sprožil seznam poimenovanih entitet."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4497
#, no-c-format
msgid "Features and Limitations"
msgstr "Lastnosti in omejitve"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4499
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can test all functions and limitations by loading <filename>katexmltools/"
"testcases.xml</filename> in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--"
"paths GenericDataLocation </option></userinput> into &kate; and following "
"the instructions."
msgstr ""
"Vse funkcije in omejitve lahko preizkusite tako, da naložite "
"<filename>katexmltools/testcases.xml</filename> v "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation </"
"option></userinput> v &kate; in po navodilih."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4512
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Insert Element...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Enter;</keycombo> </shortcut> "
"<guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Vstavi element ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4519
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will open a dialog that lets you insert an &XML; element. The &lt;, "
"&gt; characters and the closing tag will be inserted automatically. If you "
"have selected text when this menu item is selected, the selected text will "
"be surrounded by the opening and the closing tag. The dialog also offers "
"completion of all elements that may be inserted at the current cursor "
"position if you have assigned a meta DTD by using <guimenuitem>Assign Meta "
"DTD...</guimenuitem>."
msgstr ""
"To bo odprlo pogovorno okno, v katerem lahko vstavite &XML; element. &lt;, "
"&gt; znakov in končna oznaka bosta samodejno vstavljena. Če ste ob izbiri "
"tega elementa menija izbrali besedilo, bo izbrano besedilo obdano z začetno "
"in končno oznako. Pogovorno okno ponuja tudi dokončanje vseh elementov, ki "
"jih je mogoče vstaviti na trenutni položaj kazalke, če ste dodelili meta DTD "
"z uporabo <guimenuitem>Dodeli meta DTD ...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4530
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>&lt;</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Close Element</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<shortcut> <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;<keycap>&lt;</keycap></keycombo> "
"</shortcut> <guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Zapri element</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4537
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will search your text for a tag that is not yet closed and will close "
"it by inserting the corresponding closing tag. The search starts at the "
"cursor position and goes left. If it cannot find an open tag nothing will "
"happen."
msgstr ""
"To bo v vašem besedilu poiskalo oznako, ki še ni zaprta, in jo zaprlo z "
"vstavljanjem ustrezne zaključne oznake. Iskanje se začne na položaju kazalke "
"in gre levo. Če ne najde odprte oznake, se ne bo zgodilo nič."

#. Tag: menuchoice
#: plugins.docbook:4544
#, no-c-format
msgid "<guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Assign Meta DTD...</guimenuitem>"
msgstr ""
"<guimenu>&XML;</guimenu> <guimenuitem>Dodeli meta DTD ...</guimenuitem>"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4548
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This will tell the plugin which meta DTD to use for the current document. "
"Note that this assignment will not be saved. You will have to repeat it when "
"you start &kate; the next time."
msgstr ""
"To bo vtičniku povedalo, kateri meta DTD naj uporabi za trenutni dokument. "
"Upoštevajte, da ta dodelitev ne bo shranjena. Ko boste zagnali &kate;, ga "
"boste morali ponoviti. naslednjič."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4558
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kate; Plugin <quote>&XML; Completion</quote> copyright 2001,2002 &Daniel."
"Naber; &Daniel.Naber.mail;."
msgstr ""
"&kate; Vtičnik <quote>&XML; Dokončanje</quote> avtorske pravice 2001,2002 "
"&Daniel.Naber; &Daniel.Naber.mail;."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4562
#, no-c-format
msgid "&kde; SC 4 version copyright 2010 Tomáš Trnka"
msgstr "&kde; Različica SC 4 avtorske pravice 2010 Tomáš Trnka"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4563
#, no-c-format
msgid "Documentation copyright 2001,2002 &Daniel.Naber;"
msgstr "Avtorske pravice za dokumentacijo 2001,2002 &Daniel.Naber;"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4568
#, no-c-format
msgid "Compiler Explorer Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik Compiler Explorer"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4570
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The compiler explorer plugin allows you to use compiler explorer from within "
"Kate. Compiler explorer is usually limited to 1 file only and it is "
"difficult to use it to see the codegen of a file in your project. This "
"plugin aims to simplify this process by automatically detecting compile "
"commands for your file."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik compiler explorer vam omogoča uporabo orodja compiler explorer "
"znotraj Kate. Compiler explorer je običajno omejen samo na eno datoteko in "
"ga je težko uporabiti za ogled generacije kode datoteke v vašem projektu. "
"Namen tega vtičnika je poenostaviti ta postopek s samodejnim zaznavanjem "
"ukazov prevajanja za vašo datoteko."

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4573 plugins.docbook:4601
#, no-c-format
msgid "Usage"
msgstr "Raba"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4575
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first thing you need to do is to open a compiler explorer tab. Hit "
"<keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></keycombo> to open "
"the command bar and search for \"Open Current File in Compiler Explorer\" "
"and hit enter. You can add this action to the toolbar or assign a shortcut "
"to it for easier access."
msgstr ""
"Prva stvar, ki jo morate storiti, je, da odprete zavihek compiler explorer. "
"Pritisnite <keycombo action=\"simul\">&Ctrl;&Alt;<keycap>I</keycap></"
"keycombo>, da odprete ukazno vrstico in poiščete \"Odpri trenutno datoteko v "
"orodju compiler explorer\" in pritisnite enter. To dejanje lahko dodate v "
"orodno vrstico ali mu dodelite bližnjico za lažji dostop."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4579
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next you need to setup a local instance of compiler explorer or use the "
"public <ulink url=\"https://godbolt.org/\">https://godbolt.org/</ulink> "
"instance. See <ulink url=\"https://github.com/compiler-explorer/compiler-"
"explorer\">https://github.com/compiler-explorer/compiler-explorer</ulink>. "
"Once you have an instance, click on <guilabel>Option</guilabel> combobox in "
"the compiler explorer tab you opened earlier and select <guilabel>Change "
"Url...</guilabel> and then enter the url of the compiler explorer server."
msgstr ""
"Nato morate nastaviti lokalni pojavek orodja compiler explorer ali uporabiti "
"javni pojavek <ulink url=\"https://godbolt.org/\">https://godbolt.org/</"
"ulink>. Glejte <ulink url=\"https://github.com/compiler-explorer/compiler-"
"explorer\">https://github.com/compiler-explorer/compiler-explorer</ulink>. "
"Ko imate pojavek, kliknite kombinirano polje <guilabel>Možnost</guilabel> v "
"zavihku compiler explorer, ki ste ga odprli prej, in izberite "
"<guilabel>Spremeni URL ...</guilabel> ter nato vnesite naslov strežnika "
"compiler explorer."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4581
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Next you need a compile_commands.json if you need to see codegen for a file "
"in your project. Otherwise you can skip this part. This can easily be "
"obtained if you are using a modern build system like CMake or Meson. For "
"CMake it is enough to pass <code>-DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=ON</code> "
"when invoking cmake. The <code>compile_commands.json</code> should be placed "
"at the root of your project. Close and reopen the compiler explorer tab in "
"Kate. After reopening the tab it should show the compile commands need to "
"compile the file"
msgstr ""
"Nato potrebujete compile_commands.json, če želite videti generiranje kode za "
"datoteko v vašem projektu. V nasprotnem primeru lahko ta del preskočite. To "
"lahko enostavno dobite, če uporabljate sodoben sistem izgradnje, kot sta "
"CMake ali Meson. Za CMake je dovolj, da podate <code>-"
"DCMAKE_EXPORT_COMPILE_COMMANDS=ON</code>, ko prikličete cmake. Datoteka "
"<code>compile_commands.json</code> mora biti postavljena v koren vašega "
"projekta. Zaprite in znova odprite zavihek compiler explorer v Kate. Ko "
"znova odprete zavihek, bi morali biti prikazani ukazi za prevajanje, "
"potrebni za prevod datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4583
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are just using compiler explorer to see the codegen for something "
"temporary, you can just write down the compile commands for your file and "
"click the <guilabel>Compile</guilabel>. Note that auto recompilation on "
"editing is not supported. You need to click Compile every time you want to "
"recompile the file"
msgstr ""
"Če samo uporabljate orodje compiler explorer, da si ogledate generiranje "
"kode za nekajzačasnega, lahko samo zapišete ukaze za prevajanje za svojo "
"datoteko inkliknite <guilabel>Prevedi</guilabel>. Upoštevajte, da je "
"samodejno ponovno prevajanje pri urejanju ni podprto. Vsakič morate klikniti "
"Prevedi, kadar želite znova prevesti datoteko"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4585
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Once the file is compiled you should see the codegen on the right hand side. "
"You can right-click and select <guilabel>Reveal linked code</guilabel> to "
"see the codegen for a particular line. Similarly on the right hand side, you "
"can right click and select <guilabel>Scroll to source</guilabel> to show the "
"source code for a given codegen line"
msgstr ""
"Ko je datoteka prevedena, bi morali videti generirano kodo na desni strani."
"Lahko kliknete z desno tipko miške in izberete <guilabel>Razkrij povezano "
"kodo</guilabel> dasi ogledate generirano kodo za določeno vrstico. Podobno "
"lahko na desni strani z desnim klikom izberete <guilabel>Pomakni se do vira</"
"guilabel>, da prikažete izvorno kodo za dano generirano vrstico"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4594
#, no-c-format
msgid "Formatting Plugin"
msgstr "Vtičnik za formatiranje"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4596
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The formatting plugin allows one to format code easily. The plugin aims to "
"preserve the document's undo history and user's cursor position when "
"formatting the code so that the formatting of code doesn't disrupt user's "
"work. This is especially important for automatic formatting on save."
msgstr ""
"Vtičnik za formatiranje omogoča preprosto oblikovanje kode. Vtičnik je "
"namenjen, da ohranja zgodovino razveljavitev dokumenta in položaj kazalca "
"uporabnika, koformatira kodo, tako da oblikovanje kode ne moti "
"uporabnikovega dela. To je še posebej pomembno za samodejno formatiranje ob "
"shranjevanju."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4603
#, no-c-format
msgid "It allows the user to format code in two ways:"
msgstr "Uporabniku omogoča oblikovanje kode na dva načina:"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4606
#, no-c-format
msgid "Manually using the \"Format Document\" action."
msgstr "Ročno z dejanjem \"Formatiraj dokument."

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4607
#, no-c-format
msgid "Automatically on save"
msgstr "Samodejno ob shranjevanju"

#. Tag: para
#: plugins.docbook:4611
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You can search for this action in the command bar and bind a shortcut to it "
"for easier access"
msgstr ""
"To dejanje lahko poiščete v ukazni vrstici in nanj povežete bližnjico za "
"lažji dostop"

#. Tag: title
#: plugins.docbook:4616
#, no-c-format
msgid "Supported languages and formatters"
msgstr "Podprti jeziki in oblikovalniki"

#. Tag: para
